NK132(no)004:1: // snga 'gyur bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam gyi 'grel
NK132(no)004:2: pa phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan zhes
NK132(no)004:4: na mo gu ru pad+ma many+dzu sh+r+ai ye /
NK132(no)004:5: dpal ldan yon tan bye bas yongs gang phul byung mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer gyis //
NK132(no)004:6: sa gsum nyes pa'i mun pa kun sel phan bde'i 'dab stong bzhad pa'i gnyen //
NK132(no)004:7: dus gsum rgyal ba'i ye shes gcig bsdams dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK132(no)004:8: kun mkhyen ye shes gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin rgyal ba rig 'dzin brgyud bcas rgyal //
NK132(no)004:9: rgyal bstan ljongs 'dir 'dren mkhas mes dbon gsum //
NK132(no)004:10: mdo sngags bstan pa gsal mdzad mkhan slob chos //
NK132(no)004:11: skad gnyis smra ba thon mi bee ro sogs //
NK132(no)004:12: gangs can 'gro la bka' drin zla bral nyid //
NK132(no)004:13: sde gsum snying po'i bka' babs gnyags gnubs zur //
NK132(no)004:14: lung rigs smra ba'i khyu mchog rong klong gnyis //
NK132(no)004:15: bka' gter bstan pa'i srog mthud smin gling pa //
NK132(no)004:16: 'di dag snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyi ma yin //
NK132(no)004:17: ngo mtshar bka' babs bdun ldan mdo sngags gling //
NK132(no)004:18: rgyal basngagasa mdzod lnga'i shing rta gu na'i zhabs //
NK132(no)004:19: theg mchog seng ge'i dbyangs sgrogs a dzi ta //
NK132(no)004:20: rtsod pa'i dus kyi rgyal ba gnyis pa yin //
NK132(no)004:21: gang gi ring lugs ngo mtshar bye ba'i gter //
NK132(no)004:22: rtsod 'chad rtsom pa'i dpung pas legs bzung nas //
NK132(no)004:23: dus kyi mthar yang mi nyams gsal byed pa //
NK132(no)004:24: de kun lhar bcas skye bos basngagasa 'os nyid //
NK132(no)004:25: de phyir bdag blo sher brtson dman na yang //
NK132(no)004:26: bstan la gus dang dam pa'i gsung bskul ngor //
NK132(no)004:27: tshul 'dir brtson na dbyings nas rtsa gsum lhas //
NK132(no)004:28: rjes dgongs byin rlobs bka' yi gnang ba rtsol //
NK132(no)004:29: de la 'dir rje btsun smra ba'i seng ge gu
NK132(no)004:30: ru blo ldan mchog sred nyid bsam bzhin srid par
NK132(no)004:31: rjes su chags pa'i rang gzugs nges pa don gyi
NK132(no)004:32: thams cad mkhyen pa chen po mi pham 'jam dbyangs
NK132(no)004:33: rnam rgyal rgya matsho'am 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rang mdangs
NK132(no)004:34: mtsho byung bzhad pa'i ge sar zhes nyi zla ltar
NK132(no)004:35: yongs su grags pa de nyid kyi zhal snga nas
NK132(no)004:36: stsal ba'i snga 'gyur bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam
NK132(no)004:37: chos rgyal dgyes pa'i zhal lung zhes bya ba dgos
NK132(no)004:38: pa dang che yon rmad du byung ba'i gzhung bzang
NK132(no)004:39: lha'i rnga bo che'i dbyangs lta bu 'di nyid 'chad
NK132(no)004:40: pa la gnyis / spyi don rnam par bzhag pa rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK132(no)004:41: tshig gi 'bru 'grel snying por dril nas bshad pa'o //
NK132(no)004:43: yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir du
NK132(no)004:44: mchog gsum gyi rnam dbye bstan pa sngon du 'gro
NK132(no)004:45: bas brgyud pa rin po che gang las byung ba'i
NK132(no)004:47: de la gzhan gyis log par rtog pa'i skyon bsal ba /
NK132(no)004:48: rang lugs rnam par dag pa gser zhun lta bu
NK132(no)004:49: nyid rig pas sgrub cing che ba drug ldan gyi
NK132(no)004:52: spyir dkon mchog gi rnam dbye bshad pa /
NK132(no)004:53: bye brag brgyud pa gsum gyi lo rgyus dang byung tshul mdo tsam smos pa'o //
NK132(no)004:56: rnam grangs so sor bshad pa /
NK132(no)004:57: don ngos bzung ba gsum las /
NK132(no)004:59: gang gi tshe dpal kun tu bzang po nyid gdod ma'i grol gzhir mngon par byang chub nas /
NK132(no)004:64: kun tu brtags pa'i chos la mngon par zhen pa'i rang bzhin gzigs nas //
NK132(no)004:65: srid pa'i sdug bsngal yongs su skyob pa dang /
NK132(no)004:66: thar pa dam pa yongs su thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:67: ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das longs spyod chen po //
NK132(no)004:68: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK132(no)004:71: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa'i chos thams
NK132(no)004:72: cad kyi rang bzhin gcig dang du ma med pa'i
NK132(no)004:73: bdag nyid chen po'i ngang las g.yo ba'i rtsol ba
NK132(no)004:74: dang rnam par rtog pa mi mnga' bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:75: sngon gyi smon lam dang thugs rje chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i shugs dang /
NK132(no)004:76: shes rab chen po'i stobs kyis chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag par gyur pa'i dbang dang /
NK132(no)004:77: gdul bya rnams kyi dkar po'i las kyi rgyu las /
NK132(no)004:78: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu kun tu /
NK132(no)004:79: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi sprul pa sna tshogs
NK132(no)004:80: pa gdul bya so so'i ngor so sor gang la
NK132(no)004:82: dper na lha'i dbang po dbang bsgyur gyi gnas man chad nas /
NK132(no)004:84: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi rkyen so sor char 'bab pa yang /
NK132(no)004:86: gnas so so'i nam mkha'i dbang dang /
NK132(no)004:87: 'gro ba so so'i las kyi rgyu las char so sor 'bab par grub pa yin yang /
NK132(no)004:88: rgya mtsho'i lha yang 'di snyam du /
NK132(no)004:89: bdag gis ni gnas 'di rnams su so so'i las
NK132(no)004:90: skal dang 'tshams par spriin 'di lta bu bsdu bar
NK132(no)004:91: bya'o // glog 'di lta bu dbyung bar bya'o //
NK132(no)004:93: char 'di lta bu dbab par bya'o snyam du mi rtog /
NK132(no)004:97: 'gro ba 'di dag gi 'dod pa'i yon tan 'byung
NK132(no)004:98: ba'i char dbab pa'i go skabs dabye'o snyam du mi
NK132(no)004:101: 'gro ba so so'i las kyi bag chags kyang 'di snyam du /
NK132(no)004:102: bdag cag gi las kyi skal ba dang 'tshams pa'i char dbyung bar bya'o snyam du mi rtog /
NK132(no)004:104: mngon par mi rtsol bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:105: rgyu dang rkyen tshogs pa'i dbang gis gnas de rnams su /
NK132(no)004:106: so so'i las kyi skal ba dang 'tshams pa'i sprin
NK132(no)004:107: 'du ba nas char 'bab pa'i bar du so sor
NK132(no)004:108: 'byung ba ni / lha'i rgyal po dbang sgyur gyi
NK132(no)004:109: gnas su gser gyi snying po lta bu'i sprin 'du
NK132(no)004:110: 'byung ba ni / ba dang / de bzhin du glog dang /
NK132(no)004:111: 'brug rnams kyang tha dad du byung zhing /
NK132(no)004:112: char yang rang bzhin tha dad du 'bab pa ni 'dzam bu'i gling gi bar yang de bzhin ti /
NK132(no)004:113: sprin rnams kyang mu tig dmar po lta bu las /
NK132(no)004:114: ri nag po brtsegs pa lta bu'i ba dang /
NK132(no)004:115: glog kyang gser kha sbyang ba lta bu nas /
NK132(no)004:116: rin po che in+d+ra snyil 'od 'phro ba lta bu'i bar dang /
NK132(no)004:117: 'brug kyang bya ka la ping ka'i dbyangs lta bu dang /
NK132(no)004:118: rol mo'i sgra dbyangs lta bu nas /
NK132(no)004:119: rgya mtsho 'khrugs pa lta bu'i sgra yi bar dang /
NK132(no)004:120: char yang rin po che sna tshogs kyi char nas /
NK132(no)004:122: chu dwangs pa'i char gyi bar du /
NK132(no)004:123: so so'i las kyi skal ba dang 'tshams par so sor tha dad du 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:124: gdul bya so so'i ngo la /
NK132(no)004:125: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin tha dad du mthong ba ni 'di lta bu ste /
NK132(no)004:126: 'gro ba mchog tu gyur pa rnams la ni /
NK132(no)004:128: longs spyod chen po mtshan dang dpe byad /
NK132(no)004:130: theg pa chen po thun mong ma yin pa'i chos dang /
NK132(no)004:131: sa chen po la rab tu bzhugs pa'i dge 'dun nam /
NK132(no)004:132: de bzhin du so so'i skye bo dang /
NK132(no)004:134: so so'i bsod nams mthun pa rnams la ni /
NK132(no)004:135: sangs rgyas mchog gi sprul pa'i sku dga' ldan nas
NK132(no)004:136: 'pho ba la sogs pa mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi
NK132(no)004:137: rnam pa dang / theg pa sna tshogs pa'i chos dang /
NK132(no)004:138: 'phags pa dang so so'i skye bo'i dge 'dun /
NK132(no)004:139: dge sbyong gi cha byad can 'khor rnam bzhi dang bcas par kun tu snang ngo //
NK132(no)004:141: ngan song du gyur pa la sogs bsod nams cung
NK132(no)004:142: zad dman pa rnams la ni so so'i snang ba
NK132(no)004:143: dang mthun par / lha dang mi dang klu dang
NK132(no)004:144: dud 'gro la sogs pa'i ston pa tha dad pa
NK132(no)004:145: dang mthun par / dang / mi rtag pa dang /
NK132(no)004:149: 'jig rten gyi gtsug lag khang dang /
NK132(no)004:150: glu dang bzhad gad la sogs pa so sor mngon par dad par gyur pa de dang /
NK132(no)004:152: rang rang gi bsod nams kyi zhing du gyur pa'i dge 'dun yang tha dad du snang ngo //
NK132(no)004:153: de bzhin du 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon
NK132(no)004:154: tan dang ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yul
NK132(no)004:158: dper na zla ba yar gyi ngo'i dkyil nam phyed kyi dus na /
NK132(no)004:159: 'dzam gling gi sems can thams cad kyi so so'i
NK132(no)004:160: mdun na zla ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dug par shes kyang
NK132(no)004:161: / zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ni sems can de dag
NK132(no)004:162: gis bdag ci nas kyang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK132(no)004:163: shes par 'gyur bar bdag gis sems can de dag
NK132(no)004:164: gi mdun du 'dug par bya'o snyam du mi rtog
NK132(no)004:165: rnam par mi rtog mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:167: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ni ma 'dres pa'i chos dang ldan pas /
NK132(no)004:168: lhun gyis grub cing rnam par mi rtog pa de lta bu'i bya ba 'di byung ngo //
NK132(no)004:169: 'jam dpal de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK132(no)004:170: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang
NK132(no)004:172: tshad med mtshungs pa med pa gzhal du med pa
NK132(no)004:173: de dag gi dbus na de bzhin gshegs pa bzhugs
NK132(no)004:175: de bzhin gshegs pa ni de dag gi mdun du bzhugs par bya'o snyam du mi rtog /
NK132(no)004:177: 'on kyang sems can gyis mthong ba de bzhin du
NK132(no)004:178: de bzhin gshegs pa mdun na bzhugs shing chos ston
NK132(no)004:179: to // 'jam dpal de bzhin du gser gyi kha dog gis 'dul bar bya ba yin na /
NK132(no)004:184: mu tig dmar po'i kha dog gis 'dul ba yin na /
NK132(no)004:185: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i kha dog tu snang ngo //
NK132(no)004:192: byol song gi gzugs su snang bas gdul bar bya ba yin na'ang /
NK132(no)004:195: gnyis pa rnam grangs so sor bshad pa la gsum las /
NK132(no)004:196: theg pa thun mong la grags pa'i sangs rgyas dkon mchog ni /
NK132(no)004:197: mchog gi sprul pa'i sku rab tu byung ba'i cha
NK132(no)004:198: byad can skyes bu'i gzugs su bzhugs pa mtshan dang
NK132(no)004:199: dpe byad du 'bar ba sh+aakya thub pa lta bu'o
NK132(no)004:202: gnyen po'i dbye bas theg pa sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK132(no)004:203: chos kyi sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:207: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pa'o //
NK132(no)004:210: dge slong la sogs pa rab tu byung ba dag la dge 'dun du brjod kyi /
NK132(no)004:211: dge 'dun dkon mchog zhes mi brjod de 'phags pa slob pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:212: gnyis pa theg pa chen po thun mong ma yin pa ltar na /
NK132(no)004:213: sangs rgyas dkon mchog ni chos kyi sku dang /
NK132(no)004:214: 'og min na bzhugs pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK132(no)004:215: de las phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na sprul pa'i sku ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK132(no)004:216: chos dkon mchog ni thun mong du grags pa de dag dang /
NK132(no)004:217: theg pa chen po 'ba' zhig pa ste /
NK132(no)004:218: thar pa chen po'i grong du gzhol ba'i lam du gyur pa'o //
NK132(no)004:219: dge 'dun dkon mchog kyang byang chub sems dpa' so
NK132(no)004:220: so'i skye bo dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun te snga
NK132(no)004:221: ma bzhin no // gsum pa gsang ba bla na med pa'i lugs la'ang gsum las /
NK132(no)004:222: dang po thun mong du grags pa bya ba dang spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:225: sku gsum mam bzhi'i bdag nyid dag pa dang /
NK132(no)004:227: byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha dang bcas pa /
NK132(no)004:230: rdo rje'i rigs gsum gyis bsdus pa /
NK132(no)004:232: sprul pa'i sku zhi ba dang /
NK132(no)004:234: rigs sngags dang gsang sngags kyi gzugs su bzhugs pa /
NK132(no)004:238: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang snying po'i dkyil 'khor la
NK132(no)004:239: sogs pa'i bye brag gis dkyil 'khor che chung gi
NK132(no)004:240: lha rnams ni sangs rgyas so //
NK132(no)004:242: sngar smos pa rnams dang khyad par du rang rang gi gzhung du grags pa'o //
NK132(no)004:246: rig pa 'dzin pa'i dge 'dun te gsum du 'dod do //
NK132(no)004:247: gnyis pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:250: sku gsum mam bzhi'i chos nyid dag pa dang /
NK132(no)004:251: dkyil 'khor dang rgyud du gtogs pa /
NK132(no)004:252: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs thams cad kyi bdag po dang /
NK132(no)004:256: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs lngas bsdus pa'i sku gsum zhi ba dang /
NK132(no)004:263: chos dang las kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK132(no)004:265: gcig pa la sogs pa'i rim pas dkyil 'khor che
NK132(no)004:266: chung du gtogs pa'i lha rnams ni sangs rgyas so
NK132(no)004:267: // chos dang dge 'dun ni bshad ma thag pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:268: gsum pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:269: sangs rgyas dkon mchog bcom ldan 'das longs spyod chen po /
NK132(no)004:270: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid /
NK132(no)004:271: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad /
NK132(no)004:275: gcig dang du ma med pa'i bdag nyid chen po /
NK132(no)004:276: sku lnga ye shes drug gi bdag nyid zag pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK132(no)004:277: zag pa med pa'i chos thams cad dbyer med par
NK132(no)004:278: sku gsung thugs rdo rje lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du
NK132(no)004:279: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i lha dang bcas pa
NK132(no)004:280: / sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las byang chub kyi sems kyi rigs te drug gis bsdus pa /
NK132(no)004:281: zhi ba dang khro bo'i cha byad can /
NK132(no)004:283: sprul pa'i sku thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK132(no)004:284: pa'i rgyan chen po la rol pa chen po'i gzugs
NK132(no)004:285: su bzhugs pa / gtso bo dang /
NK132(no)004:291: spyod yul lta bu chos thams cad ye nas mngon
NK132(no)004:292: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du dbyer
NK132(no)004:293: med cing / gcig dang du ma med pa'i bdag nyid /
NK132(no)004:294: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings sku gsung thugs
NK132(no)004:295: lhun stug po bkod pa'i rgyan du bzhugs pa ni
NK132(no)004:296: sangs rgyas dkon mchog zhes par 'dod /
NK132(no)004:298: thun mong ba gsang ba spyi dang 'dra la /
NK132(no)004:299: thun mong ma yin pa ni dkon mchog gsum dbyer
NK132(no)004:300: med pa'i rang bzhin de nyid kun tu bzang po
NK132(no)004:301: byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)004:302: chos kyi sku nyag gcig gdod ma nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK132(no)004:303: tshul de dang mthun par rgyu bla ma las kyang /
NK132(no)004:304: skyabs ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig ste //
NK132(no)004:305: skyob pa chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK132(no)004:306: tshogs kyang de yi mthar thug phyir //
NK132(no)004:308: gsum pa don ngos bzung ba la gsum las /
NK132(no)004:309: dang po theg pa chung ngu nyan thos bye brag pa ltar na /
NK132(no)004:310: so so'i skye bo dbang po rnon po srid pa
NK132(no)004:311: tha ma pa zhig brtson pa chen pos sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:312: nas / bdag gi smon lam dang gdul bya'i skal bas mi mjed 'dir don mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:313: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor nas mya ngan las 'das
NK132(no)004:314: te zhi ba'i dbyings su gtan du bzhugs nas phyis
NK132(no)004:317: byang chub sems dpa' srid pa tha ma pa'i lus ni smon lam gyis bsgrubs te /
NK132(no)004:318: rgyu'ang bdag tu lta ba'i bag chags dang gnas kyi
NK132(no)004:319: sa'i ma rig pas bskyed pa yin par 'dod pas
NK132(no)004:320: sangs rgyas te mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK132(no)004:321: gdul bya'i don du 'gyur na zhi ba'i dbyings las
NK132(no)004:322: sprul pa 'bad rtsol med par ston par 'dod do
NK132(no)004:323: // 'di nyid gzhung lugs phal cher nyan thos las /
NK132(no)004:324: tshul theg pa chen po'i mdo sde'i rjes su 'brang bas mdo sde pa zhes grags so //
NK132(no)004:325: theg pa chen po la'ang gnyis te /
NK132(no)004:326: pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK132(no)004:329: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK132(no)004:330: grags sde spyod pa'i dbu ma'o //
NK132(no)004:336: phyi rol gyi don du snang ba sems las gud na med la /
NK132(no)004:339: longs spyod lta bu snang ba ste /
NK132(no)004:340: sangs rgyas nas kyang nyon mongs pa mtha' dag dang bral ba'i ye shes gzugs kyi sku /
NK132(no)004:342: de'i rgyan la sogs pa'i longs spyod du snang bas 'gro ba'i don byed par 'dod la /
NK132(no)004:343: de'ang ma dag pa la sprul pa dang /
NK132(no)004:344: dag pa'i 'gro ba la longs skur snang bas dus rgyun mi chad par 'dod do //
NK132(no)004:346: khams gsum pa'i sems kyang don ltar snang ba'i rnam pa dang bral ba yin la /
NK132(no)004:348: de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med pa'i bag chags te /
NK132(no)004:349: sangs rgyas pa'i dus na bag chags yongs su dag
NK132(no)004:350: nas ye shes rnam pa dang bral ba skad cig
NK132(no)004:351: ma'i mtshan nyid rgyun 'brel bar skye zhing /
NK132(no)004:352: smon lam dang thugs rje dang ye shes chen po'i dbang gis /
NK132(no)004:353: gzugs kyi sku mngon du snang ba nor bu dang
NK132(no)004:354: dpag bsam gyi shing ltar 'gro ba'i don 'byung bar
NK132(no)004:355: 'dod de / de las ni skad cig ma'i rgyun
NK132(no)004:356: dang 'brel ba'i ye shes nyid don dam par yod
NK132(no)004:357: pa nyid du khas len to //
NK132(no)004:358: gnyis pa rang rgyud gong ma ltar na /
NK132(no)004:359: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs las grub pa'i ngang du sangs rgyas pa na /
NK132(no)004:360: don dam par gang gi'ang rang bzhin du ma grub pas don bya ba dang byed pa med kyang /
NK132(no)004:361: kun rdzob tu smon lam dang thugs rje chen pos /
NK132(no)004:362: sar gnas kyi sems dpa' la longs sku /
NK132(no)004:363: so so'i skye bo dang nyan rang la sprul pa'i skus don mdzad par 'dod do //
NK132(no)004:364: gnyis pa grags sde spyod pa'i dbu ma pa ltar na /
NK132(no)004:365: sangs rgyas pa'i tshe rang bzhin mkha' la sprin dengs pa ltar /
NK132(no)004:366: sems dang sems byung gi 'jug pa dbyings su zhi bas ye shes su grub pa med kyang /
NK132(no)004:367: sngon gyi smon lam gyis gdul bya gzhan snang du
NK132(no)004:368: gzugs sku gnyis su snang bas don mdzad par 'dod
NK132(no)004:369: do // gnyis pa gsang sngags la'ang gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:370: dang po phyi pa ltar na /
NK132(no)004:371: sangs rgyas ni bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs tshad med pa las grub pa /
NK132(no)004:372: ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK132(no)004:373: yongs su dag pa'i zhing na longs spyod chen po'i sku dag pa'i sems dpas bskor ba /
NK132(no)004:374: ji ltar 'dul ba'i dbang dang bcas pas don mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:375: btsun mo'i tshogs la mi spyod de smad pa'i gnas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:376: 'on kyang 'ga' zhig gi ngor sprul pa'i yum du
NK132(no)004:377: snang yang lhan cig sbyor ba ni ma yin no
NK132(no)004:378: // de las sprul pa'i sku sna tshogs su snang bas don mdzad pa'o //
NK132(no)004:380: gnyis pa nang pa la'ang gsum las /
NK132(no)004:381: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ltar na /
NK132(no)004:382: ye nas sangs rgyas su gnas pa /
NK132(no)004:383: thabs dang she rab kyis mngon du byas pa na /
NK132(no)004:385: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku gsal la rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngang las /
NK132(no)004:386: sprul pa'i sku rtag tu lhun gyi sa grub pa'o zhes bshad /
NK132(no)004:387: lung a nu yo ga ltar na /
NK132(no)004:388: kun tu bzang po byang chub kyi sems rdo rje
NK132(no)004:389: 'chang chen po rtag tu da ltar byung ba lta
NK132(no)004:392: sprul pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK132(no)004:393: rtag tu yongs su dag pa'i zhing khams na btsun mo'i tshogs dpag tu med pa'i dkyil 'khor na /
NK132(no)004:394: bde ba thams cad dang mi 'bral bar bzhugs te /
NK132(no)004:395: bde ba de yang chos kyi dbyings de kho na
NK132(no)004:396: nyid kyi don la ting nge 'dzin gyi mnga' brnyes
NK132(no)004:397: pa'i bde ba dang ldan pa /
NK132(no)004:398: yid bde ba dang ldan pa /
NK132(no)004:399: gzugs la sogs pa phyi rol gyi 'dod pa'i bde ba dang /
NK132(no)004:400: yum dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i bde ba la sogs te /
NK132(no)004:401: bde ba mchog dang ldan pa /
NK132(no)004:402: bde ba zag pa med pa dang /
NK132(no)004:403: bde ba tshad med pa dang /
NK132(no)004:406: gdul bya thams cad la bde ba bskyed pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK132(no)004:408: rdzogs pa chen po ltar na /
NK132(no)004:409: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa nyid /
NK132(no)004:410: lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing na 'od gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha'i dbyings khyab pa las /
NK132(no)004:411: bde ba dang gsal ba zhes tha dad pa'am gcig
NK132(no)004:412: pa la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid med cing spros pa
NK132(no)004:413: dang bral ba / rang byung gi thugs rje dang
NK132(no)004:414: mdzad pas sprul pa'i sku gsum gdul bya'i 'jig rten
NK132(no)004:415: du phyogs mthas gtugs par snang zhing /
NK132(no)004:416: so so'i mos pa dang mthun par don mdzad pa'o zhes 'dod do //
NK132(no)004:417: zhes smra ba'i seng ge rong klong rnam gnyis kyis gsungs so //
NK132(no)004:420: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK132(no)004:421: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK132(no)004:423: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK132(no)004:425: gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa dang gsum /
NK132(no)004:427: ston pa sku gsum gyis ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul /
NK132(no)004:428: de re re la phun sum tshogs pa lnga lngas 'chad pa las /
NK132(no)004:429: dang po chos sku'i phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK132(no)004:430: gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min chos dbyings kyi zhing khams spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang /
NK132(no)004:432: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gang du'ang rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa na /
NK132(no)004:433: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dpal kun bzang po
NK132(no)004:434: gdod nas mngon par byang chub pa'i rang bzhin nyid
NK132(no)004:435: / dus phun sum tshogs pa chos nyid 'gyur ba
NK132(no)004:436: med pa dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin
NK132(no)004:437: / na / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs la /
NK132(no)004:438: chos phun sum tshogs pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK132(no)004:439: po ma gsungs mi gsung gsung ba med pa'i tshul
NK132(no)004:440: gyis so // gnyis pa longs sku'i phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK132(no)004:441: chos sku spros dang bral ba'i ngang las ma g.yos
NK132(no)004:442: bzhin du ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid longs
NK132(no)004:444: gnas phun sum tshogs pa rang snang lhun stug po bkod pa gsal dag bde ba'i zhing na /
NK132(no)004:445: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad dang rdo rje mi bskyod pa sogs la /
NK132(no)004:446: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)004:447: dkyil 'khor nam mkha'i dbyings khyab pa zhi ba dang
NK132(no)004:448: khro bo'i rang bzhin mngon par snang bas bskor te
NK132(no)004:449: / dus phun sum tshogs pa thog ma dang tha
NK132(no)004:450: ma med pa'i chos nyid 'du 'bral med pa'i ngo
NK132(no)004:451: bo bsam gyis mi khyab pa na /
NK132(no)004:452: chos phun sum tshogs pa bstan pa dang theg pa
NK132(no)004:453: thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am rtsa bar gyur pa rang
NK132(no)004:454: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po la sogs pa'i zab mo
NK132(no)004:455: nang rgyud sde gsum rang byung rang shar chen por
NK132(no)004:456: rang snang ba'o // gsum pa sprul sku'i phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK132(no)004:457: de lta bu'i lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing nas
NK132(no)004:458: rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho'i sku las sprul pa'i dang
NK132(no)004:459: po yi ge sprin gyi 'od zer bye ba khrag
NK132(no)004:460: khrig dpag tu med pa 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK132(no)004:461: bcu kun tu 'phro ba'i rtse mo las /
NK132(no)004:462: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug grangs med brjod du med pa thon te /
NK132(no)004:463: lha dang lha ma yin la sogs pa 'gro ba so so'i don mdzad pa las /
NK132(no)004:464: khyad par du stong gsum gyi stong chen po mi
NK132(no)004:465: mjed kyi 'jig rten gzhi dang snying po me tog
NK132(no)004:466: gis brgyan pa 'di nyid du thub pa drug gis
NK132(no)004:468: mi yi thub pa sangs rgyas stong mngon par snang ba 'gro ba'i kha lo gyen du bsgyur zhing /
NK132(no)004:469: de dag las kyang rtsod ldan tshe lo brgya pa'i dus 'dir /
NK132(no)004:470: sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya ba'i mtshan dang sku'i rnam
NK132(no)004:471: pas gdul bar dgongs nas 'dzam bu'i gling bye ba
NK132(no)004:472: phrag brgyar sku mnyam du snang nas sems can gyi
NK132(no)004:474: nam mkha'i zla ba ma 'phos bzhin du chu snod
NK132(no)004:475: bye ba phrag brgyar snang ba bzhin longs sku'i ngang
NK132(no)004:476: las sprul pa'i sku mngon par snang bas mdzad pa
NK132(no)004:477: bcu gnyis kyis don mdzad pa na /
NK132(no)004:478: sku dngos kyi gdul byar gyur pa'i rigs can gsum
NK132(no)004:479: gyi gdul bya la chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa
NK132(no)004:481: de yang bka' 'khor lo dang po /
NK132(no)004:482: gnas phun sum tshogs pa w+aa r+aa na s+ai'i drang
NK132(no)004:483: srong lhung ba ri dwags mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i
NK132(no)004:484: nags na / ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK132(no)004:485: chos phun sum tshogs pa bden pa bzhi /
NK132(no)004:486: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa lnga sde bzang po lha brgyad khri dang bcas pa la /
NK132(no)004:487: dus phun sum tshogs pa sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun lon pa'i dus na gsungs /
NK132(no)004:489: gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyal po'i khab bya rgod kyi phung po'i ri la /
NK132(no)004:490: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK132(no)004:491: chos phun sum tshogs pa bka' rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum sogs mtshan ma med pa /
NK132(no)004:492: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa thun mong ba sh+aa ri'i bu sogs 'khor rnam bzhi dang /
NK132(no)004:493: thun mong ma yin pa bzang skyong dang /
NK132(no)004:494: rin chen 'byung gnas sogs byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig rab tu mang po rnams la /
NK132(no)004:495: dus phun sum tshogs pa lo bcu gnyis su zla ba gnyis kyis ma chog pa'i bar du gsungs /
NK132(no)004:497: gnas phun sum tshogs pa lha klu mi yi gnas
NK132(no)004:498: rgyal po'i khab dang grong khyer pad+mo can la sogs
NK132(no)004:499: par / ston pa phun sum tshogs pa mnyam med sh+aakya'i rgyal pos /
NK132(no)004:500: chos phun sum tshogs pa nges pa don gyi rnam
NK132(no)004:501: grangs de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po bstan pa la
NK132(no)004:502: sogs pa / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa thun mong
NK132(no)004:503: dang thun mong ma yin pa'i tshogs rab tu mang
NK132(no)004:504: sogs pa / po rnams la / dus phun sum
NK132(no)004:505: tshogs pa lo sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi bar du
NK132(no)004:506: sogs pa / po rnams la / gsungs so //
NK132(no)004:507: de ltar rigs can gsum gyi gdul bya rnams byang
NK132(no)004:509: gdul bya rtag 'dzin shas che ba rnams gdul ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)004:510: sku dngos su snang bas 'dul ba'i 'gro ba'i bsod
NK132(no)004:511: nams kyi chu snod kyang de tsam du zad pas
NK132(no)004:512: tha ma'i mdzad pa ston par bzhed nas /
NK132(no)004:513: gyad yul r+ts+wa can du shing sa la zung gi drung du seng ge'i khri la gzims te /
NK132(no)004:514: 'khor gyi nang nas rdzu 'phrul cher spyod la /
NK132(no)004:515: khyod song la nga'i slob ma bstan pa 'dir zhugs
NK132(no)004:516: pa gang ji snyed pa sdus shig ces bskul ba
NK132(no)004:517: dang / rdzu 'phrul can des ri rab kyi rtser song nas rdzu 'phrul gyi skad chen pos /
NK132(no)004:518: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur rigs drug gang su dag /'di par nges shing phyogs pa kun nyon cig /
NK132(no)004:519: der 'dir ston pas bdud rtsi gsum 'jog gis //
NK132(no)004:520: dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus shig /
NK132(no)004:521: ces sogs phyogs kun tu khyab cing go bar mdzad pas /
NK132(no)004:522: blo gros dad grol la sogs pa gang zag dam pa'i rigs can lnga ni /
NK132(no)004:523: ston pa rdo rje'i sku la skye 'chi med kyis /
NK132(no)004:524: sprul pa dbyings su zhi ba tsam las mya ngan
NK132(no)004:525: las mi 'da' bar khong du chud nas nang du
NK132(no)004:527: de las gzhan thams cad ston pa'i spyan sngar 'dus te smre sngags 'don pa na /
NK132(no)004:529: grogs po dag shes par gyis shig /
NK132(no)004:530: chos thams cad ni mi rtag pa /
NK132(no)004:531: 'byor pa thams cad ni mthar rgud pa /
NK132(no)004:532: dngos po thams cad ni nges par 'jig pa /
NK132(no)004:533: gang zag gi srog gi dbang po la nges par
NK132(no)004:534: skye shi yod pa'i phyir nga yongs su mya ngan
NK132(no)004:535: las 'da' bas / gang su dag the tshom dang spros pa yod na dris shig gsungs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:536: 'khor gyi nang nas rig 'dzin chen po kuny+dzara stan nas langs te gsol pa /
NK132(no)004:537: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK132(no)004:542: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum la //
NK132(no)004:543: gang dag rim par bkod lags na //
NK132(no)004:544: mnyam pas blang dor mi spyod cing //
NK132(no)004:545: byang chub gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK132(no)004:546: thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang ba //
NK132(no)004:547: mnyam pa'i theg mchog yongs ma gsungs //
NK132(no)004:549: rgyu la mos pa rgyu chos kyi //
NK132(no)004:550: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK132(no)004:551: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK132(no)004:554: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK132(no)004:555: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK132(no)004:556: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK132(no)004:557: mi las skal ldan d+r+wa ma che //
NK132(no)004:558: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba dang //
NK132(no)004:559: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK132(no)004:560: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK132(no)004:561: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK132(no)004:562: phyag na rdo rjes ston par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:564: sprul skus tshig sdeb sbyor legs pa'i sgo nas gsungs so //
NK132(no)004:565: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa la /
NK132(no)004:566: rig 'dzin mi ma yin las brgyud pa dang /
NK132(no)004:567: mi la brgyud pa gnyis kyi /
NK132(no)004:569: lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing du /
NK132(no)004:570: ston pa longs sku bla na med pa'i gsang ba
NK132(no)004:571: rang gi ngo bos bstan pa nyid kyi sku gsung
NK132(no)004:572: thugs kyi sems dpa' gsum gyis mi mjed kyi zhing
NK132(no)004:573: 'dir gnas ris gsum so sor sku mnyam du bstan
NK132(no)004:575: sku yi sprul ba 'jam dpal ni /
NK132(no)004:576: mkhyen rab mchog tu gyur pas gtso bor lta ba'i chos ston cing /
NK132(no)004:577: mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar bas lha yi gnas su lha rnams kyi don mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:578: gsang ba dam pa lha grags ldan mchog skyong la gsungs /
NK132(no)004:579: de nas rim pa bzhin du lha rin chen 'od 'bar dang /
NK132(no)004:580: tshangs pa skye dgu'i bdag po dang /
NK132(no)004:582: dbang po brgya byin gyi bar du gsungs shing /
NK132(no)004:583: des lha'i 'khor tshom bu 'bum sde la bstan pas /
NK132(no)004:584: lha rnams kyang sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'tshob cing gsang sngags kyi rig pa 'dzin par gyur to //
NK132(no)004:585: gsung gi sprul pa spyan ras gzigs ni /
NK132(no)004:586: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag tu gyur pas gtso bor spyod pa'i chos ston cing /
NK132(no)004:587: bdud rtsi sman gyi sku mnga' bas klu'i nad gso
NK132(no)004:588: zhing klu'i gnas su gsang ba 'di nyid klu dung
NK132(no)004:589: mgrin nag po la gsungs shing /
NK132(no)004:595: des klu'i 'khor tshom bu 'bum sde la gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:596: klu rnams kyang sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'tshob cing rig pa 'dzin par gyur to //
NK132(no)004:597: thugs kyi sprul pa gsang bdag ni /
NK132(no)004:598: mthu stobs kyi bdag por gyur pas gtso bor 'bras bu'i chos ston cing /
NK132(no)004:599: 'jigs gzugs rngams pa'i sku mnga' bas gnod sbyin gyi
NK132(no)004:600: yul lcang lo can gyi gnas su gnod sbyin rnams
NK132(no)004:601: la gsungs shing / gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la gdams par mdzad /
NK132(no)004:602: de nas rim bzhin gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje /
NK132(no)004:604: skar mda' gdong gi bar brgyud cing /
NK132(no)004:605: des gnod sbyin gyi 'khor tshom bu 'bum sde la
NK132(no)004:606: bstan pas sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'tshob cing rig pa
NK132(no)004:609: sngar lung bstan pa dang mthun par sangs rgyas mchog
NK132(no)004:610: gi sprul pa'i sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul
NK132(no)004:611: bstan nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis te nyer brgyad
NK132(no)004:612: song ba na / dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma
NK132(no)004:613: lnga nang du yang dag 'jog las langs nas ri
NK132(no)004:614: ma la ya'i rtse mor lhags so //
NK132(no)004:615: ri de ni rdo rje gdan gyi shar lho'i mtshams za hor gyi yul na yod de /
NK132(no)004:616: tsan+dana la sogs pa'i nags 'khrigs shing sman dang me tog gi tshogs rgyas pa /
NK132(no)004:619: lce spyang la sogs pa rgyu zhing /
NK132(no)004:620: mkha' 'gro dang grub pa du mas bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)004:621: dus dus su lha yi me tog dang tsan+dana sna tshogs kyi phye ma'i char 'bab pa /
NK132(no)004:622: shar phyogs na a su ra gsang ba'i brag phug yod pa /
NK132(no)004:623: de'ang sgo zla gam la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung ba /
NK132(no)004:626: lha'i bya ka lan ta kas theg pa chen po'i chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa /
NK132(no)004:628: 'phags pa las gang zag gzhan phal pas bgrod mi nus so //
NK132(no)004:629: de'i tshe lha grags ldan mchog skyong /
NK132(no)004:632: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK132(no)004:633: mi li tsa b+ai'i dri med grags pa ste dam pa'i rigs can lnga pos mgrin gcig tu /
NK132(no)004:634: kye ma kye hud kye ma'o klong //
NK132(no)004:635: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK132(no)004:636: 'jig rten mun pa gang gi sel //
NK132(no)004:637: zhes sogs gdung tshig nyer gsum bton pas /
NK132(no)004:638: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsan nas kun kyang lcang lo can gyi gnas su 'dus te /
NK132(no)004:639: gsang ba'i bdag po la bskul ba /
NK132(no)004:640: gsang ba dam pa'i bdag po khyod //
NK132(no)004:641: sngon gyi go cha yal lam ci //
NK132(no)004:642: snying rjes sa la bab nas kyang //
NK132(no)004:643: 'jig rten gdung ba bsal bar rigs //
NK132(no)004:646: las dang skal bar rab ldan zhing //
NK132(no)004:647: rgyal bas 'byung bar lung bstan pa //
NK132(no)004:648: bsod nams chen po'i skal ldan rnams //
NK132(no)004:649: sprul pas ji ltar lung bstan zhing //
NK132(no)004:650: da lta'i dus la 'dir babs kyis //
NK132(no)004:651: 'khor ba snying por lung bstan bzhin //
NK132(no)004:652: cho 'phrul rnams kyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK132(no)004:653: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK132(no)004:654: ji ltar bshad cing lung bstan bzhin //
NK132(no)004:655: skal ldan rnams la bsgro bar bya'o //
NK132(no)004:657: rigs can lnga sogs rig 'dzin 'dus pa phal mo cher /
NK132(no)004:658: sngar 'og min sogs su bstan pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams slar bzlas te gsungs pa /
NK132(no)004:659: srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis gser gyi shog
NK132(no)004:660: bu la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas bris te glegs bam
NK132(no)004:661: rnams dgongs pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la sbas
NK132(no)004:662: so // de'i tshe za hor gyis yul na skal
NK132(no)004:663: ldan rgyal po dzahzhesa theg pa chen po'i rigs dang
NK132(no)004:664: ldan pa don la gsang bdag rang gi rnam par
NK132(no)004:666: rmis ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun byung ste /
NK132(no)004:668: ma la ya'i rtse mor phyag na rdo rje'i pho
NK132(no)004:669: brang bcas nas sku las 'od zer sngon po 'phros
NK132(no)004:670: pas / 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad bsreg sbyang mi snang bar byas /
NK132(no)004:671: gsung gi sgra 'brug stong ldir ba lta bu ni grags /
NK132(no)004:672: thugs ka nas rdo rje mthing ka 'od 'bar ba
NK132(no)004:673: gcig byung nas rgyal po nyid kyi thugs kar thim
NK132(no)004:674: / nyi ma 'od 'bar ba gcig shar nas spyi bor thim /
NK132(no)004:675: zla ba 'od 'bar ba zhi ga shar nas zhabs mthil du thim /
NK132(no)004:676: snang srid thams cad rgyal po nyid kyi lto na 'phyo ba rmis so //
NK132(no)004:678: sangs rgyas thams cad nyi ma la zhon nas gser
NK132(no)004:679: gyi 'khor lo bskor zhing chos kyi bsgro ba mdzad
NK132(no)004:680: pas srid pa gsum gyi kha lo bsgyur ba rmis
NK132(no)004:682: nam mkha'i ngos la sprin gser gyi kha dog can ni 'thib /
NK132(no)004:683: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug sgra go bar sla zhing snyan pas tshim par ni grags /
NK132(no)004:684: rin po che sna tshogs kyi na bun ni 'thul //
NK132(no)004:687: rin po che sna tshogs kyi char chen po 'bab pa zhig rmis so //
NK132(no)004:689: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad ni dag pa'i zhing du gyur /
NK132(no)004:690: rin po che'i sgron me 'bar bas snang srid kyi mun pa mun nag thams cad ni bsal /
NK132(no)004:691: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'bab pas sems can gyi las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad ni sbyangs /
NK132(no)004:692: 'gro ba thams cad rdo rje rnal 'byor che ge
NK132(no)004:693: mo zhes bya ba'i sgra di ri ri sgrogs pa
NK132(no)004:695: sprin gyi nang nas nyi ma rim pa sna tshogs kyi 'od zer shar ba'i dkyil nas /
NK132(no)004:696: rin po che smug po'i dpal be'u'i sgrom bu 'od 'bar zhing phyi nang gsal ba'i ngang nas /
NK132(no)004:697: gser gyi glegs bam bee d+aur+ya'i zhun mas bris pa
NK132(no)004:698: mang po skar mda' thang la lhung ba bzhin du
NK132(no)004:701: glegs bam de dag la sangs rgyas dang /
NK132(no)004:702: byang sems dang rig 'dzin lha dang lha mo dpag
NK132(no)004:703: tu med pas yon tan gyi sgra sgrogs shing mchod
NK132(no)004:704: pa dang bskor ba byed pa rmis so //
NK132(no)004:706: nam mkha' las lung ston gyi sgra grags pa /
NK132(no)004:707: las dang skal bar rab ldan cing //
NK132(no)004:708: rgyal bas 'byung bar lung bstan pa //
NK132(no)004:709: bsod nams chen po'i d+r+wa ma khyod //
NK132(no)004:710: sprul pas ji ltar lung bstan bzhin //
NK132(no)004:711: da lta'i dus la 'dir bab kyis //
NK132(no)004:712: 'khor ba snying por bya ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:713: nga yi cho 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK132(no)004:714: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK132(no)004:715: skal ldan khyod la bsgro bar bya'o //
NK132(no)004:717: de nas mnal sad de rab tu dgyes te /
NK132(no)004:718: nang par 'khor rnams la mdangs gi don de tshigs
NK132(no)004:719: su bcad nas bka' stsal pas kun kyang ngo mtshar
NK132(no)004:720: du gyur to // de nas pho brang gi rtser
NK132(no)004:721: byon nas nyin re bzhin mchod pa chen po byas
NK132(no)004:722: te phyag na rdo rje zla ba drug sgrub pas
NK132(no)004:723: du gyur to // / tsan+dana rat+na smug po'ang /
NK132(no)004:725: las grub pa'i phyag na rdo rje'i sku gzugs gcig nam mkha' las rang byon te /
NK132(no)004:726: rgyal po'i phyag tu babs pas dgyes te /
NK132(no)004:727: sngon tshe gong nas bsgrubs pa yis //
NK132(no)004:728: las kyis mjal ba'i lha mchog 'di //
NK132(no)004:729: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK132(no)004:730: mos pa'i stobs kyis lha mchog 'dzin //
NK132(no)004:732: rmi lam dang mthun par pho brang gi rtser glegs
NK132(no)004:733: bam mang po babs te de dag la mchod cing
NK132(no)004:734: brtags pas / sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa le'u brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa nas /
NK132(no)004:735: rdo rje sems dpa' sgrub pa'i le'u rtogs par gyur te /
NK132(no)004:736: de la brten nas sgrub tshul mdzad pas /
NK132(no)004:737: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal gzigs te /
NK132(no)004:738: dngos grub ci 'dod bka' stsal bas /
NK132(no)004:739: glegs bam 'di rnams kyi don rtogs par 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)004:741: rigs kyi bu khyod kyi stoon pa phyag na rdo
NK132(no)004:742: rje byon nas 'di dag gi don mngon du 'byin
NK132(no)004:743: par 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan nas mi snang bar
NK132(no)004:744: gyur to // de nas ma la ya'i rtser phyag na rdo rje dngos su byon nas /
NK132(no)004:745: rol pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa mdzad do //
NK132(no)004:746: de'i 'khor dam pa'i rigs can rnams kyis gsol ba /
NK132(no)004:747: e ma ngo mtshar rmad re che //
NK132(no)004:748: skyes bu chen po khyod su zhig /
NK132(no)004:749: gang nas byon te gang ltar byung //
NK132(no)004:750: gang la brten nas gang du byon //
NK132(no)004:751: don dang ched ka ji zhig mchis //
NK132(no)004:753: nga ni cis kyang mi bskyod de //
NK132(no)004:754: mi 'khrugs rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK132(no)004:755: snying rje g.yo zhing bskyod pas na //
NK132(no)004:756: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gcig pu //
NK132(no)004:757: zhes sogs gsungs nas 'khor rnams yi rang bar mdzad do //
NK132(no)004:759: mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum na //
NK132(no)004:760: glog 'gyu bar snang ston pa ltar //
NK132(no)004:761: thog ma tha ma med pa yi //
NK132(no)004:762: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas //
NK132(no)004:763: rnam dag lam chen 'di nyid du //
NK132(no)004:764: byung ba'i skyes bu don grub khyod //
NK132(no)004:765: dam pa rnams kyi gsang 'dzin cing //
NK132(no)004:766: gsang ba dam pa'i bdag por grags //
NK132(no)004:768: dam pa'i sgron me ji ltar nub //
NK132(no)004:769: dam pa'i gsang lung ji ltar byung //
NK132(no)004:770: ces sogs dris pa'i lan du /
NK132(no)004:771: rmongs pas gdung ba sel ba dang /
NK132(no)004:772: 'jig rten du sgron ma bkod pa dang /
NK132(no)004:774: snying po byang chub tu nges pa dang /
NK132(no)004:775: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba dang /
NK132(no)004:776: gdul bya dus la babs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:778: brgyud pa thabs kyis grags pa dang /
NK132(no)004:780: lung chen nges par bstan pa dang /
NK132(no)004:781: las rgyun yongs su gcod pa dang /
NK132(no)004:782: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba ste /
NK132(no)004:783: gsang sngags byung tshul bcu gnyis kyis gtan la phab nas /
NK132(no)004:784: rgyud sde nam mkha' dang mnyam pa rnams gsungs shing dbang bskur bar mdzad do //
NK132(no)004:785: de dag gi bka' bsdu ba'i grogs kyang lang+ka'i bdag pos byas so //
NK132(no)004:786: 'di la 'chad tshul 'ga' zhig mchis pa las 'dir
NK132(no)004:787: bshad pa ni kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos snying
NK132(no)004:788: po'i spyi don du gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:789: de nas rim par rig 'dzin rgyal po dzahs /
NK132(no)004:790: o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi /
NK132(no)004:791: dza hor gyi rgyal po u pa r+aa dza /
NK132(no)004:792: yul dbus kyi dge slong ku ku r+aa dza gsum la bshad de /
NK132(no)004:793: de thams cad sku tshe de nyid la lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK132(no)004:794: in+d+ra b+hu tis sras sh+aakya b+hu ti dang /
NK132(no)004:795: sras mo go ma de w+ai la bshad de /
NK132(no)004:796: de gnyis kyang rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gyi gral la 'khod do //
NK132(no)004:797: ku ku r+aa dzas rgyud sde bco brgyad du phyes nas /
NK132(no)004:799: drang srong b+ha shi ta la bshad de /
NK132(no)004:800: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK132(no)004:802: 'di la ngos 'dzin gyi bzhed pa mi 'dra ba 'dug kyang /
NK132(no)004:803: kun mkhyen chen po'i bzhed pa ltar na /
NK132(no)004:804: sku'i sku rgyud glang po rab 'bog /
NK132(no)004:805: sku'i gsung rgyud glang po chur 'jug /
NK132(no)004:806: sku'i thugs rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor te sku rgyud gsum /
NK132(no)004:807: gsung gi sku rgyud ri bo brtsegs pa /
NK132(no)004:808: gsung gi gsung rgyud pad+ma dbang chen /
NK132(no)004:809: gsung gi thugs rgyud zla gsang thig le ste gsung rgyud gsum /
NK132(no)004:810: thugs kyi sku rgyud rtse mo 'dus pa /
NK132(no)004:811: thugs kyi gsung rgyud gcig las 'phros pa /
NK132(no)004:812: thugs kyi thugs rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa ste thugs rgyud gsum /
NK132(no)004:813: yon tan gyi sku rgyud sgron me 'bar ba /
NK132(no)004:814: yon tan gyi gsung rgyud bdud rtsi sa ma ya 'bum sde /
NK132(no)004:815: yon tan gyi thugs rgyud dpal mchog dang po ste yon tan gyi rgyud gsum /
NK132(no)004:816: phrin las kyi sku rgyud dpal phreng dkar po /
NK132(no)004:817: phrin las kyi gsung rgyud ma mo rgyud lung /
NK132(no)004:818: phrin las kyi thugs rgyud bi to ta ma la 'bum sde ste phrin las kyi rgyud gsum /
NK132(no)004:820: spyi'i gsung rgyud sa ma ya bkod pa /
NK132(no)004:821: spyi'i thugs rgyud gsang ba sgyu 'phrul te spyi rgyud gsum bcas bco brgyad la bzhed cing /
NK132(no)004:822: 'di rnams thog ma nas gsang bdag gis phyes te /
NK132(no)004:823: rgyal po dzahl bshad par yang sngags kyi spyi don
NK132(no)004:824: tshangs sgra las gsungs te 'chad tshul gnyis snang ngo
NK132(no)004:826: n+aa gardzu nas pad+ma sam b+ha wa /
NK132(no)004:827: des bi ma mi tra la bshad de /
NK132(no)004:828: 'di gnyis kyang gdul bya'i don du pan+di tar snang yang /
NK132(no)004:829: ngo bo lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos yin no //
NK132(no)004:830: yang sras mo go mas mee tri ka ma la /
NK132(no)004:831: des sangs rgyas gsang ba la gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:832: 'di gnyis kyang tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin du gnas so //
NK132(no)004:833: yang drang srong b+ha shi tas pra b+ha hasti la bshad /
NK132(no)004:834: 'dis kyang phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin brnyes so //
NK132(no)004:835: des kyang o rgyan chen po la gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:836: 'di dag la kha cig gang zag snyan brgyud du 'dod pa mi 'thad de /
NK132(no)004:837: la la ni rgyu'i rig 'dzin yin la /
NK132(no)004:838: phal cher phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin mang zhing /
NK132(no)004:839: pad+ma dang bi ma la ni lhun grub kyi sa
NK132(no)004:840: la bzhugs nas sems can gyi don du pan+di tar
NK132(no)004:841: snang ba ste 'pho ba chen po'i skur bzhengs pa
NK132(no)004:842: yin no // zhes kun mkhyen chen pos gsang snying gi spyi don du gsungs /
NK132(no)004:843: zab pa sgrub sde'i phyogs la bka' gter gnyis kyi
NK132(no)004:844: snga ma'i phyogs ni phal cher gong bshad dang mthun
NK132(no)004:845: la / gter ma'i phyogs rnams ni /
NK132(no)004:846: gnas 'og min gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor chos 'byung dbyings kyi zhing me ri 'bar bar /
NK132(no)004:847: ston pa dpal chen kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' zhi ba dang /
NK132(no)004:848: rang byung che mchog he ru ka khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs nas /
NK132(no)004:849: 'khor rang rig gi tshom bur snang ba rnams la /
NK132(no)004:850: dus thog tha med pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang
NK132(no)004:851: du chos nyid rdo rje'i rang sgras theg pa spyi
NK132(no)004:852: dang / bye brag bde gshegs 'dus pa'i spyi rgyud lnga /
NK132(no)004:854: yan lag so so'i sgrub lugs dpag tu med pa gsungs pa rnams /
NK132(no)004:855: gsang bdag rdo rje chos kyis rang nyid tshom bu
NK132(no)004:856: dgu yi dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor snang bar mdzad
NK132(no)004:857: nas thog mar ngag tu bsdus /
NK132(no)004:858: de nas glegs bam la bkod de dgongs 'grel lung lnga yang mdzad nas /
NK132(no)004:859: mkha' 'gro ma las kyi dbang mo che la gtad /
NK132(no)004:860: des spyi bye brag gi rgyud rnams phyes te dur
NK132(no)004:861: khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal du mchod rten bde
NK132(no)004:862: byed brtsegs par gter du sbas so //
NK132(no)004:863: de nas dus phyis slob dpon brgyad kyi 'don par 'dod de /
NK132(no)004:864: der tshogs nas mkha' 'gro ma la gtor ma phul
NK132(no)004:865: nas gsol ba btab pa'i tshe mkha' 'gro ma rnams
NK132(no)004:868: sku ni lhar gsal gsung ni sngags sgra sgrogs //
NK132(no)004:869: thugs ni mnyam nyid rdo rje lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:870: sprul pa sna tshogs 'phro ba'i slob dpon brgyad //
NK132(no)004:871: bka' ni ci stsal gsung ni gang gsungs nyan //
NK132(no)004:874: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs ma mo d+aa ki dang //
NK132(no)004:875: bdud dang gshin rje la sogs bdag la nyon //
NK132(no)004:876: bka' bzhin byed pa khyed rnams mchod byed pa //
NK132(no)004:877: sgrom bu dgu po de rnams khur la shog /
NK132(no)004:879: slob dpon h'u ka ra la he ru ka gal
NK132(no)004:880: po la sogs pa yang dag thugs kyi rgyud rnams
NK132(no)004:881: gtad / 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la 'jam dpal gsang rgyud la sogs gshin rje'i rgyud rnams gtad /
NK132(no)004:882: klu sgrub la rta mchog rol pa sogs pad+ma gsung gi rgyud rnams gtad /
NK132(no)004:883: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas pra b+ha hasti la'ang mchan /
NK132(no)004:884: la bi to ta ma la sogs phur pa phrin las kyi rgyud rnams gtad /
NK132(no)004:885: bi ma mi tra la bdud rtsi rol pa'i rgyud sogs bdud rtsi yon tan gyi rgyud rnams gtad /
NK132(no)004:886: d+h+aa na sam kri ta la rgyud lung 'bum tig la sogs ma mo'i rgyud rnams gtad /
NK132(no)004:887: rom bu gu h+ya d+ae wa tsan+d+ra la sku'i rgyud
NK132(no)004:888: dreg pa 'dul ba sogs 'jig rten dregs pa can
NK132(no)004:890: phung byed sh+ain+tam gar+b+ha la drag sngags shel phreng dkar
NK132(no)004:891: po'i rgyud sogs dmod pa drag sngags kyi rgyud rnams
NK132(no)004:892: gtad / bde gshegs 'dus pa'i rgyud rnams slob dpon
NK132(no)004:893: thun mong du gtad nas slar mchod rten du bcug
NK132(no)004:894: gtad / / so sor gtad pa'i rgyud rnams slob
NK132(no)004:895: dpon so sos zhal phyes nas yongs su rgyas par
NK132(no)004:896: gtad / / mdzad do // de nas slob dpon
NK132(no)004:897: pad+mas mchod rten de nyid nas bde gshegs 'dus pa'i
NK132(no)004:898: skor rnams bton te yang le shod kyi brag phug
NK132(no)004:899: tu bder 'dus kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes nas bsgrub
NK132(no)004:900: pas phyag rgya chen po mchog grub /
NK132(no)004:901: rig 'dzin brgyad la'ang bde 'dus kyi dbang bskur te chos kyi skyes 'bul bar mdzad do //
NK132(no)004:902: lung a nu yo ga'i mdo rnams ni ri ma
NK132(no)004:903: la ya'i rtser gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can
NK132(no)004:904: lnga la tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad gsungs pa dang dus
NK132(no)004:905: mtshungs par / kri ya rnams w+aa r+aa na sir babs /
NK132(no)004:906: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar bar babs /
NK132(no)004:907: ma h+aa yo ga rnams rgyal po dzah'i khang thog tu babs /
NK132(no)004:908: a nu yo ga rnams ri ma la ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse la babs /
NK132(no)004:909: a ti yo ga rnams d+ha na ko sha'i gling du babs pa las /
NK132(no)004:910: rgyud sde gzhan rnams ni pusti dngos su babs pa yin zhing de las rim par brgyud la /
NK132(no)004:911: a ti yo ga ni de ltar ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:912: rdo rje sems dpa'i slob ma lha'i bu kun dga' snying po zhes bya ba /
NK132(no)004:913: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza snang gsal 'od ldan
NK132(no)004:914: gnyis kyi sras mo su d+harma'i sras su 'khrungs shing
NK132(no)004:915: / 'og min du dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i dbang dang /
NK132(no)004:916: yang gsang bla na med pa'i gdams pa dang bcas
NK132(no)004:917: pa yongs su rdzogs par zhus te gnas pa las
NK132(no)004:918: / sngar gyi sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i sde snod dang /
NK132(no)004:919: khyad par du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud
NK132(no)004:920: 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi thugs la bzhugs pa
NK132(no)004:921: rnams / ri ma la ya rin po che rnams par sprul pa'i rtse mor /
NK132(no)004:922: rdo rje dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro ma bde ba'i ro ldan ma dang /
NK132(no)004:923: bde byed ser mo yon tan mtha' yas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma gnyis kyis zhus te /
NK132(no)004:924: lo gsum du yi ger bkod nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams 'du ba'i phug tu bzhugs so //
NK132(no)004:925: de lta bu'i sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje nas /
NK132(no)004:926: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang /
NK132(no)004:927: sh+r+ai sing ha sogs brgyud nas /
NK132(no)004:930: bee ro gsum la bka' babs te dar bar mdzad do //
NK132(no)004:931: gsum pa gang zag snyan khung du brgyud pa ni /
NK132(no)004:932: bod kyi rim pas brgyud pa rnams te /
NK132(no)004:933: de yang lha mo dri ma med pa lung bstan pa las /
NK132(no)004:934: nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyis
NK132(no)004:935: stong lnga brgya na gdong dmar bod kyi yul du
NK132(no)004:938: sh+aakya li tsa b+ai'i rigs las byung ba'i rgyal po
NK132(no)004:939: gnya' khri btsan po nas rgyal rabs nyer bdun pa
NK132(no)004:940: / byang sems kun tu bzang po'i rnam 'phrul lha tho ri snyan btsan gyi sku ring la /
NK132(no)004:941: pho brang yum bu bla mkhar gyi rtser mdo sde za ma tog /
NK132(no)004:943: tsin+ta ma ni'i gzungs kyi brkos phor rnams dngos su babs te dam pa'i chos kyi dbu brnyes /
NK132(no)004:944: de nas gdung rabs lnga pa na 'phags pa spyan
NK132(no)004:945: ras gzigs kyi rnam 'phrul chos rgyal srong btsan sgam
NK132(no)004:946: pos / rgya bal nas ston pa'i rgyal tshab snang brnyan rnam gnyis spyan drangs /
NK132(no)004:947: ra sa 'phrul snang sogs mtha' 'dul yang 'dul gyi gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa bzhengs /
NK132(no)004:948: chos blon thon mi sam b+ho tas bod yi ge med pa la yi ge'i srol gtod /
NK132(no)004:949: spyan ras gzigs kyi mdo rgyud nyi shu rtsa gcig bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:950: rgyal khams la dge bcu'i khrims bcas te dam pa chos kyi srol gtod /
NK132(no)004:951: de nas rgyal rabs lnga pa 'jam dpal rnam 'phrul chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan gyis /
NK132(no)004:952: za hor me tog gling nas mkhan chen bo d+hi sat+wa dang /
NK132(no)004:953: o rgyan gyi yul nas slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha wa spyan drangs nas /
NK132(no)004:954: nag phyogs kyi mi dang mi ma yin pa thams cad tshar bcad /
NK132(no)004:955: dkar phyogs kyi lha 'dre rnams bran du bkol te /
NK132(no)004:956: lugs gsum mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag khang rten dang brten par bcas pa bzhengs /
NK132(no)004:957: mkhan pos rba rat+na dang ba ro tsa na sogs
NK132(no)004:958: sad mi mi bdun dang dge slong mi lnga sogs
NK132(no)004:959: rab tu byung ste bstan rtsa 'dul ba'i bstan pa
NK132(no)004:960: spel te gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde
NK132(no)004:961: btsugs / o rgyan chen pos bka' babs las can
NK132(no)004:962: snying gi bu dgu sogs bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK132(no)004:964: de'i tshe rigs kyi me tog dor ba na /
NK132(no)004:965: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i me tog dbus che mchog la babs /
NK132(no)004:966: gnubs nam mkha'i snying po'i me tog shar yang dag la babs /
NK132(no)004:967: de bzhin du gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis lho gshin rje la /
NK132(no)004:968: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis nub dbang chen la /
NK132(no)004:969: jo mo mkhar chen bzas byang rdo rje gzhon nu la /
NK132(no)004:970: 'brog ban dpal gyi ye shes kyis shar lhor ma mo la /
NK132(no)004:971: rlangs dpal gyi seng ges nub byang dregs pa kun 'dus la /
NK132(no)004:972: pa gor bee ro tsa nas byang shar dmod pa drag sngags la babs pas /
NK132(no)004:973: so so'i rgyud dang sgrub thabs rnams stsal ba nyams
NK132(no)004:974: su blangs pas grub ba thob nas so so'i rigs
NK132(no)004:975: kyi gtso bo dang dbyer med du gyur /
NK132(no)004:977: slob dpon bi ma mi tra /
NK132(no)004:979: d+harma k+airti sogs pan+di ta brgya rtsa brgyad spyan drangs /
NK132(no)004:980: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro dang nam snying sogs rgya gar du byon pa dang /
NK132(no)004:981: gzhan ska cog sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen
NK132(no)004:982: po rnams dang pan+di ta rnams bsdebs nas mdo rgyud
NK132(no)004:983: bstan bcos man ngag gi tshogs dpag tu med pa
NK132(no)004:984: bsgyur bshad sgom gsum gyis gtan la phabs te sangs
NK132(no)004:985: rgyas kyi bstan pa nyi ma shar ba lta bur
NK132(no)004:986: mdzad / de las gsang ba sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs la /
NK132(no)004:990: de yang sangs rgyas gsang ba gangs ti ser bzhugs dus /
NK132(no)004:993: bee ro gsum la bshad de /
NK132(no)004:994: de las brgyud pa ni snga 'gyur /
NK132(no)004:995: pad+mas gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK132(no)004:996: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs la mchims phur dbang
NK132(no)004:997: bskur te sgra bsgyur rgya gar gling du bsgyur nas
NK132(no)004:999: bi mas gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK132(no)004:1000: rma rin chen mchog la bsam yas lhun gyis grub
NK132(no)004:1001: pa'i bar khang du gsungs pa ni phyi 'gyur du
NK132(no)004:1002: bzhed / de gsum ka'i brgyud pa kun 'dus /
NK132(no)004:1003: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes nas rim par zur mes dban sogs su brgyud pa zur lugs dang /
NK132(no)004:1005: pa gor blon chen 'phags sogs brgyud /
NK132(no)004:1006: rim par kun mkhyen rong klong rnam gnyis las brgyud
NK132(no)004:1007: pa sogs brgyud pa'i bka' srol mang du byung ngo
NK132(no)004:1008: // lung a nu yo ga 'dus pa mdo'i skor rnams ni /
NK132(no)004:1009: rgya bal bru sha'i mkhas pa bzhi las gnubs sangs
NK132(no)004:1010: rgyas ye shes rin po ches gsan nas dar bar
NK132(no)004:1011: mdzad / rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga las /
NK132(no)004:1012: phyi sems klong gi skor rnams ni /
NK132(no)004:1013: gtso bor lo chen bee ro tsa nas slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+ha sogs la zhus nas dar bar mdzad /
NK132(no)004:1017: bi ma'i bka' srol dang gsum byon pa'i snga ma gnyis gter nas byon pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1018: phyi ma la bka' gter gyi brgyud pa gnyis su yod do //
NK132(no)004:1019: de la kun mkhyen rong zom pa chen pos gsang sngags kyi babs bdun du bzhed de /
NK132(no)004:1020: babs dang po o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pas thugs
NK132(no)004:1021: sras rje 'bangs las can snying gi bu dgu sogs
NK132(no)004:1023: gnyis pa grub chen nam mkha'i snying po rgya gar
NK132(no)004:1024: du byon nas slob dpon h'u ka ra sogs las
NK132(no)004:1025: gsan pa dang / gsum pa slob dpon sh+ain+tam gar+b+ha
NK132(no)004:1026: bsam yas rab gnas su phebs skabs gsungs pa dang
NK132(no)004:1027: gsan pa dang / / bzhi pa slob dpon sangs
NK132(no)004:1028: rgyas gsang bas gangs ti se nas sbas many+dzu sh+r+ai
NK132(no)004:1029: sogs la bstan nas rgyal po la skyes su bskur
NK132(no)004:1030: gsan pa dang / / ba dang / lnga pa
NK132(no)004:1031: lo chen bee ros 'phags yul gyi slob dpon sh+r+ai
NK132(no)004:1032: seng ha sogs mkhas pa nyer gcig gi dgongs mdzod
NK132(no)004:1033: phyung ba rdzogs chen gtsor gyur /
NK132(no)004:1034: drug pa pan chen bi ma las ska cog rma gsum sogs la sngar gsungs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1035: bdun pa lha sras mu ne btsad po'i dgongs rdzogs
NK132(no)004:1036: su slar rgya nag nas gshegs pa'i skabs su gnyags
NK132(no)004:1037: chen dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra sogs la gsungs pa
NK132(no)004:1038: rnams so gsungs / gzhan yang o rgyan dus gsum
NK132(no)004:1039: mkhyen pas ma 'ongs phyi rabs kyi gdul bya rnams
NK132(no)004:1040: la dgongs nas zab gter rgya mtsho lta bu sbas
NK132(no)004:1041: rnams so gsungs / pa rnams / phyis dus la
NK132(no)004:1042: babs pa'i tshe sngon gyi rje blon sa chen po
NK132(no)004:1043: la bzhugs pa'i 'phags pa rnams kyi rnam par 'phrul
NK132(no)004:1044: ba sprul pa'i gter chen mchog gnyis gling pa brgyad
NK132(no)004:1045: sogs rim par byon pa rnams kyis spyan drangs nas
NK132(no)004:1046: bod khams mtha' dbus kyi skye rgu yongs la 'phral
NK132(no)004:1047: yun gyi phan bde bla na med pa ster bzhin
NK132(no)004:1048: rnams so gsungs / pa rnams / pa ste /
NK132(no)004:1049: mdor na rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa dang po
NK132(no)004:1050: rnams so gsungs / pa rnams / pa ste / gnyags la babs / bar du gnubs la babs /
NK132(no)004:1051: tha ma zur la babs zhes grags pa ltar de dag gi chos brgyud mtha' yas pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1052: khyad par bstan pa phyi dar gyi dus su /
NK132(no)004:1053: lha rje 'ug bya lung pa'am bde gshegs zur po
NK132(no)004:1054: che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa'i
NK132(no)004:1055: rtsa ba btsugs / bde gshegs rgya bo pa'am zur chung shes rab grags pas yal ga brkyang /
NK132(no)004:1056: gsang bdag sgro phug pa'am sh+aakya seng+gesa lo 'bras rgyas
NK132(no)004:1057: par mdzad pas zur mes dbon rnam gsum zhes grags
NK132(no)004:1058: shing / 'di'i skabs su bod la gsang sngags kyi
NK132(no)004:1059: bstan pa dar tshul oo di ya na dang mtshungs
NK132(no)004:1060: shing / par grags / gzhan yang gsang bdag sgro
NK132(no)004:1061: phug pa'i slob ma 'dzom ston 'gro ba'i mgon po
NK132(no)004:1062: shing / par grags / nas / kahdama pa bde gshegs sogs la brgyud pa khams lugs dang /
NK132(no)004:1063: gsar rnying gnyis ka'i nang nas 'gran zla dang bral
NK132(no)004:1064: ba'i mkhas pa chen po dpal rong zom pan+di ta
NK132(no)004:1065: dang / 'od gsal theg mchog lta ba'i shing rta
NK132(no)004:1066: pa chen po kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams sogs
NK132(no)004:1067: mkhas pa dang grub pa'i skyes chen bsam gyis mi
NK132(no)004:1068: dang / khyab pa / de re re la'ang brgyud
NK132(no)004:1069: pa'i bka' srol dang brgyud 'dzin skyes chen bgrang gis
NK132(no)004:1071: bar skabs dus dbang gis cung zad rgud par phyogs pa na /
NK132(no)004:1072: lo chen bee ro tsa na dang rgyal mo g.yu
NK132(no)004:1073: sgra snying po gnyis bsam bzhin srid par skye ba
NK132(no)004:1074: bzhes pa / rje rig 'dzin gter bdag gling pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1075: mkhan chen d+harma sh+r+ai gnyis kyi thugs bskyed brtson pa
NK132(no)004:1076: chen pos bstan pa rmangs nas gsos te gzhir bzhengs
NK132(no)004:1077: su mdzad / g.yo ru rdzogs chen pa rig 'dzin
NK132(no)004:1078: 'jigs med gling pa la kun mkhyen chen po'i ye
NK132(no)004:1079: shes kyi skus byin gyis brlabs pas mkhyen rtogs dgongs
NK132(no)004:1080: pa'i rtsal rdzogs nas thugs gter gyi phrin las mkha'
NK132(no)004:1081: su mdzad / khyab tu brdal / khyad par snga 'gyur kalpa dum bu'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:1082: 'jig rten kha ba can zhes su pad+ma'i snying po
NK132(no)004:1083: kun dga' dang blo gros mtha' yas la sogs pas
NK132(no)004:1084: 'dzin pas bstan pa rgyas par 'gyur zhes sogs mdo
NK132(no)004:1085: rgyud du ma nas rdo rje'i lung gis basngagasa shing
NK132(no)004:1086: rig pas grub pa tshad mar gyur pa'i skyes chen
NK132(no)004:1087: sa gsum na 'gran zla dang bral ba /
NK132(no)004:1088: pan chen bi ma'i rnam 'phrul ngo mtshar bka' babs
NK132(no)004:1089: bdun ldan pad+ma 'od gsal mdo sngags gling pa dang
NK132(no)004:1090: / bee ro'i rnam 'phrul rgyal basngagasa mdzod lnga'i shing
NK132(no)004:1091: rta pa chen po kun mkhyen pad+ma gar dbang blo
NK132(no)004:1093: rje bla ma rdo rje 'chang rnam gnyis kyi thugs bskyed brtson pa chen pos /
NK132(no)004:1094: bod gangs can na yongs su grags pa'i snga 'gyur rnying ma /
NK132(no)004:1101: rdo rje gsum gyi bsnyen sgrub sogs sgrub brgyud shing
NK132(no)004:1102: rta chen po brgyad rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa'i ring
NK132(no)004:1103: lugs spyi dang / khyad par snga 'gyur bka' gter
NK132(no)004:1104: gyi bstan pa'i me ro rmangs nas gsos te phyi
NK132(no)004:1105: ma'i mthar yang mi nyams pa'i btsas su bka' gtsigs
NK132(no)004:1106: phyag rgyas btab ste sngon med mdzod chen lnga yi
NK132(no)004:1107: shing rta'i ring lugs gsal bar mdzad pa yin la
NK132(no)004:1108: lugs spyi dang / / dam pa de gnyis kyi
NK132(no)004:1109: thugs sras slob tshogs rgyu skar phreng ba'i dbus na
NK132(no)004:1110: mtshan mo'i mgon po bzhin mngon par 'phags pa /
NK132(no)004:1111: rje btsun 'jam pa'i rdo rje ngur smrig gar gyi bardzu la bzhugs pa /
NK132(no)004:1112: so so yang dag rig pa bzhi dang /
NK132(no)004:1113: spobs pa'i gter chen po brgyad la mnga' dbang 'byor
NK132(no)004:1114: ba'i kun mkhyen bla ma mi pham 'jam dbyangs rnam
NK132(no)004:1115: rgyal rgya mtshos / rang lugs grub matha'i rkang blangs te /
NK132(no)004:1116: gzhan gyi zer sgros nya dang nyung ma bsres pa lta bu ma yin par /
NK132(no)004:1117: dpyad gsum rnam par dag pa gser zhun lta bu'i
NK132(no)004:1118: legs bshad bsam mi khyab pa mdzad de mtha' dbus
NK132(no)004:1119: kun tu 'jigs med seng+ge'i sgra dbyangs sgrogs par mdzad
NK132(no)004:1121: khyad par thun min nang rgyud sde gsum gyi bstan
NK132(no)004:1122: pa'i rgyal mtshan dus mthar yang nub pa med par
NK132(no)004:1123: bsgreng ba'i bka' drin ni rang lugs rnying bstan 'dzin
NK132(no)004:1124: pa rnams kyis bskal pa rgya mtshor gzhal daka'i gnas
NK132(no)004:1125: su gyur pas / zol med kyi bstan la dgongs pa'i skyes chen rnams kyis /
NK132(no)004:1126: 'jam mgon rdo rje 'chang rnam gsum gyi ring lugs
NK132(no)004:1127: dri ma med pa nyid sgo du ma nas 'phel
NK132(no)004:1128: zhing rgyas par 'gyur pa'i thabs la brtson par cis
NK132(no)004:1129: kyang gsol ba 'debs pa lags shing /
NK132(no)004:1130: gong smos rnams kyi brgyud pa'i rnam thar dang lo rgyus rgyas pa ni /
NK132(no)004:1131: chos 'byung pad dkar rdzing bu dang /
NK132(no)004:1132: gter mdzod las 'phros pa'i gtam lha yi rnga sgra
NK132(no)004:1133: gnyis su gsal bar bshad zin pas 'dir ma spros
NK132(no)004:1134: so // gnyis pa de la gzhan gyis log par rtog pa bsal ba la gsum /
NK132(no)004:1135: pusti 'chang rdzun du 'dod pa bsal ba /
NK132(no)004:1136: rgyud rnams bod kyis brtsam par 'dod pa bsal ba /
NK132(no)004:1137: gzhi rgyud rang gi ngo bo la 'gal ba brjod pa bsal ba'o //
NK132(no)004:1139: kun mkhyen chen pos snying po'i spyi don du 'di skad ces gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:1140: 'dir gsar ma kha cig na re /
NK132(no)004:1141: slob dpon la ma ltos par glegs bam la brten
NK132(no)004:1142: nas lha sgrub pas lha'i zhal mthong zer ba mi
NK132(no)004:1143: 'thad de / bka' la ras chod 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)004:1144: bla ma las ma thos pas chos la khungs med pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1145: dbang ma bskur bas lam la gzhi med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)004:1146: lung bstan pa 'di yang khyod kyi mdo sgyu 'phrul la sogs 'byung ba'i lung bstan ma yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:1147: rgya gar shar phyogs kri ti ka ra'i grong khyer du /
NK132(no)004:1148: rgyal po rab gsal zla ba la phyag na rdo
NK132(no)004:1149: rjes rnal 'byor gyi rgyud bstan pa'i lung bstan yin
NK132(no)004:1150: te khungs ni sdom pa phyi ma'i rgyud na yod
NK132(no)004:1151: ces zer ro // de yang khyed cag ni phyin
NK132(no)004:1152: ci log gi ling thog gis blo gros kyi mig
NK132(no)004:1154: tshul 'di la brgal du rung ba ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:1155: rgyal sras chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs pa'i grub chen rnams byon cing /
NK132(no)004:1156: sngon gyi lo pan rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi yid ches pa'i gnas su bzung na /
NK132(no)004:1157: khyod kyi log rtog 'dis ji zhig dkrug tu yod /
NK132(no)004:1158: 'on kyang lan mdo tsam zhig brjod na /
NK132(no)004:1159: slob dpon la ma ltos par glegs bam la brten
NK132(no)004:1160: nas lha bsgrub pas zhal mi mthong ba'ang mi 'thad
NK132(no)004:1161: de / sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa ni gang la
NK132(no)004:1162: gang 'dul du snang bas glegs bam gyis 'dul na
NK132(no)004:1164: glegs bam nyid slob dpon du gyur pa'ang mi 'gal mod /
NK132(no)004:1165: rgyal po nyid de la dbang ba'i rigs ldan du bshad cing /
NK132(no)004:1166: phyag na rdo rje'i sprul par grags te /
NK132(no)004:1167: des mi dbang na nam yang chos la dbang ba'i gang zag rgyun chad pa'i skyon yod cing /
NK132(no)004:1168: bla ma las ma thos pas chos la khungs med ces zer ba ni /
NK132(no)004:1169: mi'i bla ma las ma thos kyang /
NK132(no)004:1170: phyag na rdo rje dngos su rol pa brtul zhugs
NK132(no)004:1171: kyis byon nas chos bstan dbang bskur bas lam la
NK132(no)004:1172: gzhi med pa ga la srid /
NK132(no)004:1173: gal te mi'i bla ma med pas yid mi ches na /
NK132(no)004:1175: te lo bas rdo rje 'chang la thos pa de la su zhig yid brtan du rung /
NK132(no)004:1176: de bzhin rdo rje dril bu pas bde mchog las dngos su brgyud pa bsnyegs pa la'ang mtshungs so //
NK132(no)004:1177: de dag grub pa chen po la yin no zhe na /
NK132(no)004:1178: 'dir yang mtshungs pa kho na ste /
NK132(no)004:1179: rgyal po nyid grub pa chen po dngos yin pa kho na'o //
NK132(no)004:1180: lung bstan pa la'ang nged kyi mdo sgyu 'phrul la
NK132(no)004:1181: ma yin zhes rnam par bcad pa'i lung ci zhig
NK132(no)004:1182: yod / gal te rnal 'byor gyi rgyud byung ba yin du chug mod /
NK132(no)004:1183: de tshe gsang bdag gis mdo sgyu 'phrul la sogs ma gsungs pa'i tshad ma ci zhig yod /
NK132(no)004:1184: chos la khungs kyang shin tu yod do //
NK132(no)004:1185: rgyal bas lung bstan cing gsang bdag gis dngos su
NK132(no)004:1186: byin gyis brlabs te grub chen du ma rim gyis
NK132(no)004:1188: gal te de ltar gyur pa la'ang yid mi ches na /
NK132(no)004:1189: mkha' 'gro ma'i gling nas glegs bam brkus nas 'dzam bu gling du dar bar byas pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1190: byang sham+b+ha lar chos 'tshol ba la /
NK132(no)004:1191: lho phyogs kyi rgya mtshor zhugs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1192: sngon du bdag med ma la brtags gnyis gsan nas /
NK132(no)004:1193: phyis dmo b+hi he ru kas o rgyan nas btsal
NK132(no)004:1194: ba sogs rang rang gi lo rgyus 'gal ba can
NK132(no)004:1195: de dag khyod la yod pas su zhig yid ches
NK132(no)004:1196: su rung / gal te khyod kyi rtsod pas nged kyi chos la skyon yod na /
NK132(no)004:1197: mu stegs pas nang pa'i chos la rtsod nas sangs
NK132(no)004:1198: rgyas kyi chos rnams skyon can du 'gyur ba dang
NK132(no)004:1199: / khyed rang gi chos su rlom pa'i gur brtags
NK132(no)004:1200: sam b+hu tra la sogs pa la'ang nged kyis rtsod
NK132(no)004:1201: pa byas na chos ma yin par 'gyur zhing /
NK132(no)004:1202: phan tshun rtsod cing mthun snang du ma grub pas
NK132(no)004:1203: chos ma yin na nyan thos kyi sde pa bco
NK132(no)004:1204: brgyad kyang / nged kyi 'di yin gyis gzhan gyi
NK132(no)004:1205: ltar ma yin zhes rtsod pas chos ma yin par
NK132(no)004:1206: brgyad kyang / 'gyur te / de ltar ma yin
NK132(no)004:1207: par sangs rgyas kyi chos su gcig pa bzhin no
NK132(no)004:1208: brgyad kyang / 'gyur te / // des na chos
NK132(no)004:1209: dang gang zag la skur pa gdab par mi bya
NK132(no)004:1210: brgyad kyang / 'gyur te / // ste / dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK132(no)004:1211: dge slong dag nga'am nga 'dra bas gang zag dang chos kyi tshod gzung bar bya yi /
NK132(no)004:1212: gzhan gyis ni ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:1213: sgrib pa rnams kyi nang nas shin tu lci ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)004:1214: rnam par ltung ba chen po nyams su myong bar 'gyur du 'ong ba'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:1215: ces sogs lung drangs te rgyas par gsungs so //
NK132(no)004:1217: kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal dgyes pas 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:1218: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba zhes pa'i mtshan gzhi 'dzin pa /
NK132(no)004:1219: chos rgyal srong btsan gyi dus nas bzung /
NK132(no)004:1220: khri srong lde btsan gyis dar zhing rgyas par mdzad pa nas /
NK132(no)004:1221: jo bo rje ma byon yan chad du bsgyur ba'i chos dang /
NK132(no)004:1222: de phyin chad bsgyur ba'i chos la gsar mar grags pa las /
NK132(no)004:1223: snga 'gyur gyi chos zhes bya ba /
NK132(no)004:1225: sngags rgyud sde drug gis bsdus pa rnams yin /
NK132(no)004:1226: de la sde snod kyi chos rnams bka' yin min du sus kyang rtsod pa med /
NK132(no)004:1227: sngags thun mong ba gsang 'dus sogs ni gsar rgyud du 'dod kyang thun mong yin /
NK132(no)004:1228: thun min nang rgyud sde gsum ni rnying chos zhes the tshom bya ba'i gzhi yin no //
NK132(no)004:1229: de la log rtog skye ba'i sa bon gang las
NK132(no)004:1230: byung na bstan pa phyi dar gyi thog mar glang
NK132(no)004:1231: dar gyis bstan pa bsnubs rjes /
NK132(no)004:1232: klu mes sogs kyis dge 'dun gyi sde btsugs /
NK132(no)004:1233: so thar sdom pa'i bka' ma chad kyang /
NK132(no)004:1234: dge 'dun rnams rang rang gi rtog chos 'chad /
NK132(no)004:1235: lta ba tha dad mi mthun par gyur /
NK132(no)004:1236: sham thabs sngon po can dang /
NK132(no)004:1237: +aa tsar+ya dmar po'i zhabs kyis chags lam bsgyur bas
NK132(no)004:1238: mnga' ris stod kyi dge 'dun rnams la chags lam
NK132(no)004:1239: dar / sngags pa rnams kyang slob dpon med par rang blos gzhal ba'i rtog chos 'chad /
NK132(no)004:1240: sbyor sgrol sogs sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa'i sngags
NK132(no)004:1241: 'chal mang po byung bas bod phal cher yid sun
NK132(no)004:1242: / skabs der lha bla ma ye shes 'od kyis
NK132(no)004:1243: sngags pa rnams la bka' shog bardzanga bar mdzad de
NK132(no)004:1244: / / de'i nang na thun mong mdo yi lam rim bshad nas /
NK132(no)004:1245: de dang mi ldan pa'i sngags su khas blangs nas
NK132(no)004:1246: sbyor sgrol sogs bag med byed pa bkag 'dug /'di
NK132(no)004:1247: lan 'debs pa'i gnas ma yin gdams pa yin /
NK132(no)004:1248: lo chen rin chen bzang po'i sngags log sun 'byin
NK132(no)004:1249: yang 'di dang 'dra ste rnying ma bkag pa med
NK132(no)004:1250: mod / skabs 'di tsam nas gsar ma rnams rim par byung ste /
NK132(no)004:1251: de rnams rgya gar du song chos ci rigs bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:1252: der rgya gar nang yongs su grags pa rnams bzung /
NK132(no)004:1253: ma grags pa gsang rgya can rnams ma thob pas sa lan byas /
NK132(no)004:1254: gsar rnying phan tshun chags sdang gis nga bzang nga che'i skabs shig /
NK132(no)004:1255: chos dang gang zag bar du bdud kyis dkrugs pa'i
NK132(no)004:1256: blo gros kyis nang rgyud phal cher bod rtsom yin
NK132(no)004:1257: zhes bsgrags / de bsgrags mi 'gos lhas btsas kyis mdzad do zer ba'i 'byams yig btang /
NK132(no)004:1259: lo ts+aa tshos brtsam chos yin /
NK132(no)004:1261: pan+di ta la dris kyang bu mi bden zer zhes
NK132(no)004:1262: pa tsam phrag dog gi bslu tshig 'di las gzhan
NK132(no)004:1263: rgyu mtshan til 'bru tsam mi snang /
NK132(no)004:1264: de nas zhi ba 'od kyi bka' shog sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:1265: dpal 'dzin sogs kyi dgag pa rtsom pa sa bon yin /
NK132(no)004:1266: de las 'phros te chags sdang can rnams kyis snga chos la kha zer zhing /
NK132(no)004:1267: mi shes pa dag g.yom rgyug gis chos yang dag
NK132(no)004:1268: pa ma yin snyam du 'dzin pa 'di byung ba
NK132(no)004:1269: yin / smra ba 'di don gnas yin min kho bos cung zad dpyad kyi /
NK132(no)004:1270: blo ldan gzu bor gnas pa rnams kyis su bden legs par dpyod cig /
NK132(no)004:1271: gal te chos min zhig yin na ni de shes na los dgag /
NK132(no)004:1272: min na chos spang gi las gsog par mi rung bas /
NK132(no)004:1273: de la rgya gar du med ces pa /
NK132(no)004:1274: bod lam thag ring rkang thang zhig gis rgya gar sa rgya thams cad ji ltar nyul te /
NK132(no)004:1275: bod sa rgya chung ngu'i yul thams cad kyang rkang thang re zung gis e chod soms /
NK132(no)004:1276: n+aa len+d+ra sogs chos sde che ba rnams su rgyal
NK132(no)004:1277: bka' mtha' dag phyogs gcig yod pa'i nges pa med
NK132(no)004:1278: de / spyir sangs rgyas kyi bka' mdo rgyud la tshad med /
NK132(no)004:1279: bye brag phal chen dkon brtsegs sogs kyi ma dpe
NK132(no)004:1280: chos mngon pa la dgra lan gsum byung ba na
NK132(no)004:1281: nub tshul dang / 'bum rgyas pa klu sgrub kyis klu yul nas gdan drangs pa yin na /
NK132(no)004:1282: bod la sleb pa'i gtsug lag khang gcig na med
NK132(no)004:1283: na sangs rgyas kyi bka' min nges 'di blo rgya
NK132(no)004:1284: shin tu chung ba byis pa'i ca co ste /
NK132(no)004:1285: rgya gar na yod pa 'di tsam zhes bod kyi
NK132(no)004:1286: bka' bstan ltar dkar chag ni yod par ma bshad
NK132(no)004:1287: / spar 'khod de phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa'ang yod pa ma grags /
NK132(no)004:1288: gal te ci rigs bsdus kyang mtha' dag bsdu ga la nus te /
NK132(no)004:1289: bram ze rgyal po rgyal bshes kyis bstan pa nyams dmas par byas rjes /
NK132(no)004:1290: dge slong rnams kyis yul dang gnas sna tshogs pa nas sde snod gsum gyi glegs bam bsdus nas /
NK132(no)004:1291: yul bcom brlag tu yang dag par bsdu bar byas pa'i tshe /
NK132(no)004:1292: gzhung bla ma'i gzhung ma rnyed nas bsdu ba'i gzhi nyams par bshad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1293: gsang sngags la'ang bde mchog 'bum pa sogs mi yul du ma dar ba sogs /
NK132(no)004:1294: bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi tshad /
NK132(no)004:1295: bde mchog sdom 'byung dang ye shes snying po kun
NK132(no)004:1296: las btus sogs las bshad pa de rnams rgya gar
NK132(no)004:1297: na'ang dper 'khod pa'ang dka' zhing med na /
NK132(no)004:1298: de thams cad rgya gar nas mthong ba'i lo ts+aa ba su yang mi snang zhing /
NK132(no)004:1299: snga 'gyur du bsgyur ba'i sde snod kyi chos la'ang
NK132(no)004:1300: rgya dpe bltas nas 'dra bsdur nus mkhan su yang
NK132(no)004:1301: ma byung / rgya dpe klog nus mkhan kyang dkon
NK132(no)004:1302: na gsang sngags kyi bka' thams cad yod med ga
NK132(no)004:1303: ma byung / la shes / sngags thams cad sangs
NK132(no)004:1304: rgyas kyi sku dus nas pusti byas nas gtsug lag
NK132(no)004:1305: khang re na brtsigs yod pa ma red /
NK132(no)004:1306: gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa ltar /
NK132(no)004:1307: sdud pa po phyag na rdo rje dang dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro'i bka' rgya dus su khrol ba'i tshe /
NK132(no)004:1308: grub pa'i dbang phyug rnams kyis rim par spyan drangs pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:1309: gsang 'dus rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti las brgyud de
NK132(no)004:1310: o rgyan gyi yul nas 'phags yul du dar tshar
NK132(no)004:1311: rjes / rdo rje 'jigs byed la li tas btsal ba'i lo rgyus dang /
NK132(no)004:1312: de'i phyis zhig na dus zhabs pas dus 'khor drangs pa sogs kyis shes nus la /
NK132(no)004:1313: des na gtsigs ka che ba thams cad de dus
NK132(no)004:1314: yod kyang mi ston pa'i bka' rgya yod pas mi
NK132(no)004:1316: de'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi gsungs la lo ts+aa rkang
NK132(no)004:1317: 'khyams tshos gtsug lag khang gcig na gang mthong ba
NK132(no)004:1318: de las gzhan rnams sangs rgyas kyi bka' min par
NK132(no)004:1319: thag bcad pa ni khron pa'i rus sbal gyi rnam
NK132(no)004:1321: 'di mtha' 'di tsam kho nar gnas so zhes //
NK132(no)004:1322: de mtha' de tsam kho nar rjes dpag nas //
NK132(no)004:1323: 'gro ba'i bla ma'i gsung las brgal ba ste //
NK132(no)004:1324: des na mtha' min dgongs pa dpyad par bya //
NK132(no)004:1326: legs par brtags na phyogs re'i mig can yin //
NK132(no)004:1328: gzhan yang lo ts+aa ba re zung gis ma mthong
NK132(no)004:1329: zhes pa'i tshig gis chos min par bya nus na
NK132(no)004:1330: / sngon gyi pan grub chen po 'phags yul na'ang
NK132(no)004:1331: 'gran zla dang bral ba'i pad 'byung bi ma sogs
NK132(no)004:1332: kyis gzigs nas bstan pa'i chos des ci'i phyir go
NK132(no)004:1333: / mi chod / 'o na rnying rgyud rnams ci ltar yin byas tshe /
NK132(no)004:1335: gshed skor rnams gnubs kyi rtsom chos yin /
NK132(no)004:1336: rdzogs chen nam mkha' che sogs bee ros brtsams sogs
NK132(no)004:1337: byas pa mi gzo ba'i steng du 'phags chen rnams
NK132(no)004:1338: la skur 'debs mi bzad pas rang log lam du
NK132(no)004:1339: song nas / gzhan byis pa 'brid pa'i sa mkhan byed pa 'di kye ma hud /
NK132(no)004:1340: bod phal cher skal ba chung bas na /
NK132(no)004:1341: lo ts+aas bsgyur tshad des rtsom mo zer na /
NK132(no)004:1342: mdo phyogs ska cog sogs kyis ma bsgyur ba med /
NK132(no)004:1343: thar lo'i 'gyur phran bcu gsum tsam min pa gsar 'gyur med la /
NK132(no)004:1344: mdo phyogs dka' chag tu btab cing ma sbas pas
NK132(no)004:1345: so so'i gshams su yongs grags la 'gyur byang yang
NK132(no)004:1346: sngar ltar 'dug pa 'di tsho lo ts+aa ba de
NK132(no)004:1347: rnams kyi rtsom pa e red /
NK132(no)004:1348: 'di 'dra'i blun gtam mkhas pa'i tshogs par dbyung rung ba yin min dpyod cig /
NK132(no)004:1349: da ni de dag gi mtshang brtol nas bshad kyis nyon cig /
NK132(no)004:1350: snga 'gyur ba'i sngags rgyud rnams lo ts+aa ba de
NK132(no)004:1351: dag gis brtsam mo zhes pa'i tshig 'di la khyod
NK132(no)004:1353: rgyu mtshan med pa'i tshig ni skur 'debs mi bzad par 'agro'o //
NK132(no)004:1354: yod na rgyud de rtsom gyin yod par khyod kyis
NK132(no)004:1355: mngon sum du mthong nas de ltar brjod pa yin
NK132(no)004:1356: nam / gzhan las thos nas sam /
NK132(no)004:1357: rang gis dpyad nas bye brag phyed pa'am /
NK132(no)004:1358: yang na mngon shes kyis shes nas de ltar brjod pa'i tha snyad byas pa las mi 'da' na /
NK132(no)004:1359: khyod kyis mthong ba ni mi srid de /
NK132(no)004:1360: khyod yod dus lo ts+aa de dag mi bzhugs pas so //
NK132(no)004:1361: gal te rna brgyud las thos so zhe na /
NK132(no)004:1362: khyod kyi sngon du byung ba'i rin bzang sogs lo
NK132(no)004:1363: ts+aa ba rnams la ni de ltar ma grags na
NK132(no)004:1365: phyis kyi pan+di ta'i nang na grags che zhing tshad mar gyur pa /
NK132(no)004:1366: bod yongs kyi mgon po bka' drin mtshungs med jo
NK132(no)004:1367: bo rje lta bu'i zhal nas snga 'gyur gyi rgyud
NK132(no)004:1368: sde rnams la basngagasa pa brjod kyis /
NK132(no)004:1369: bod kyi rdzun rgyud ma gsungs na khyod kyis yid
NK132(no)004:1370: ches pa'i ngag gang las thos brjod dang rigs mi
NK132(no)004:1372: de 'dra'i khungs sus kyang bshad rgyu ma rnyed na /
NK132(no)004:1373: rgyu mtshan med par khyod kyis lo ts+aa ba'i rtsom
NK132(no)004:1374: chos zhes phrag dog gi tshig tsam ni de bden
NK132(no)004:1376: khyod kyis rigs pas dpyad nas rgya chos dang bod chos 'byed ga la nus te /
NK132(no)004:1377: gzhal bya lkog gyur la sus rtsom ma rtsom gyi
NK132(no)004:1378: gang zag gi rtags bstan bcos la bkod pa mi
NK132(no)004:1379: srid do // des na rtsom chos yin par bdag gi mngon shes kyis shes so smras na /
NK132(no)004:1380: khyod de 'dra'i mngon shes bslu med can yin na /
NK132(no)004:1382: pra khog snang gnubs kyis rtsom mo zhes pa'i ngan smras 'di /
NK132(no)004:1383: phyis lo ts+aa ba dang pan+di ta'i phyag tu rgya
NK132(no)004:1384: dpe dngos su byung nas bsgyur bas sa steng 'dir
NK132(no)004:1386: sngar skur 'debs byas pa thams cad cig car bsal ba 'dis /
NK132(no)004:1387: khyod kyi dam bca' de'i mtshang bud pa 'di 'dra gang las byung /
NK132(no)004:1388: des na mu stegs pa rnams kyis /
NK132(no)004:1389: ston pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po la sgyu ma shes pa /
NK132(no)004:1390: 'khor sgyu mas kha 'brid pa sogs skur pa 'debs pa dang 'dra ste /
NK132(no)004:1391: skye bo skal dman blo zhan rnams log lam du
NK132(no)004:1392: bsgyur ba'i bdud kyi gsang tshig brtag na dben pa'i
NK132(no)004:1393: blun gtam ngo tsha ba 'di 'dra sor bzhag gis
NK132(no)004:1394: rjes brjod byed pa rnams ngo mi tsha'am /
NK132(no)004:1395: mkhas pa'i tshig la rigs pa'i rgyu mtshan yod na /
NK132(no)004:1396: rgyu mtshan med pa'i ca co ni brtag na bzhad gad kyi gnas so //
NK132(no)004:1397: des na de 'dra'i brjod pa la sgrub byed gtan
NK132(no)004:1398: tshigs med pas ci yang 'grub par mi nus so
NK132(no)004:1399: // de la gnod byed kyi rigs pa yod de /
NK132(no)004:1400: sngar gyi lo ts+aa 'phags chen sar bzhugs de dag
NK132(no)004:1401: gis rdzun rgyud ci'i phyir rtsom pa'i rgyu mtshan brjod
NK132(no)004:1402: dgos na rgyu mtshan smros shig /
NK132(no)004:1403: de yang rgyal bstan la tho brtsam pa'i bdud kyi las spel ba ni ma yin te /
