NK132(no)004:1404: de dus rdzun lung rtsom pa'i dus ma yin /
NK132(no)004:1405: yin na mdo phyogs thams cad kyang cis mi rtsom ste /
NK132(no)004:1406: sngags rgyud kho na rtsom pa'i dgos pa dang rgyu mtshan khyed la brjod rgyu med do //
NK132(no)004:1407: rnyed pa'i phyir ni ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:1408: de dus rdzun lung rtsom pas rnyed pa phar zhog /
NK132(no)004:1410: rgya chos rnams bam po'i grangs sogs bcad de tshig
NK132(no)004:1411: lhad phra mo tsam mi 'jug pa'i zhib cha yod
NK132(no)004:1412: pa dang / 'phags yul pan chen grub pa'i dbang
NK132(no)004:1413: phyug du ma dpang por bzhugs bzhin pa yin pa
NK132(no)004:1414: pa dang / dang / chos kyi rgyal po 'jam
NK132(no)004:1415: dpal dbyangs nyid bzhugs nas chos kyi 'chad nyan byed
NK132(no)004:1416: pa'i skabs yin pas rdzun lung gis rnyed pa 'byung
NK132(no)004:1418: rmas gsang snying rtsom pas rgyal po'i chad pas mi
NK132(no)004:1419: lo bcu gnyis gab dgos byung zhes dpal 'dzin gyis
NK132(no)004:1421: de dus rdzun chos spel ba'i dbang med pa'i dan
NK132(no)004:1422: rtags su song gis sun 'byin du ma song ste
NK132(no)004:1423: rang tshig dngos shugs 'gal ba shes par zad /
NK132(no)004:1424: spyir yang rgyal po bka' btsan pas rma rin lo bcu gnyis gab dgos byung na /
NK132(no)004:1425: gnubs dang bee ro sogs kyis de bas mang ba'i rgyud rtsom pa chos rgyal gyis ma dgongs /
NK132(no)004:1427: gsan nas shes kyang rdzun rgyud mi 'gog na rma rin la chad pa ci ste 'ong /
NK132(no)004:1428: rang tshig dngos 'gal 'di 'dra ma smras thabs med ci 'dug /
NK132(no)004:1429: pan grub chos rgyal de rnams kyi dus su ma
NK132(no)004:1430: dgongs pa rjes su khyod kyis shes so smras pa'i
NK132(no)004:1431: tshig der brtag dpyad mi shes pa'i byis pa dag
NK132(no)004:1432: las / brtag dpyad cung zad yod pa su zhig yid ches par 'gyur /
NK132(no)004:1433: khyod kyi rgyud rnams kyang lo ts+aa so sos byas so zhes brjod na'ang mtshungs pas /
NK132(no)004:1434: 'di 'dra'i tshig tsam gyis phan tshun sum 'byin ci yang mi nus pas don ci yang med do //
NK132(no)004:1435: sems can la phan pa'i phyir ni bka' min la
NK132(no)004:1436: bkar btags te sangs rgyas la rdzun gyis skur zhing
NK132(no)004:1437: chos la dbang za ba'i dmyal ba'i rgyu de 'dra
NK132(no)004:1438: mkhas shing grub pa'i bdag nyid chen po dag gis
NK132(no)004:1439: ga la mdzad de skur 'debs 'ba' zhig tu nges
NK132(no)004:1440: nus so // de dus kyi gang zag dam pa de dag gis de ltar rdzun chos spel na /
NK132(no)004:1441: phyis su khyod rgya gar du phyin nas ngas bsgyur
NK132(no)004:1442: zer ba tsho la dan dpang mkhas pa su yod
NK132(no)004:1443: / chos kyi rgyal pos chos gral bzhag pa'i bka' them mi snang /
NK132(no)004:1444: lo ts+aa ba de tshos rdzun chos mi rtsom pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yang med pas /
NK132(no)004:1445: snga 'gyur bas kyang gsar 'gyur la the tshom cis mi za /
NK132(no)004:1446: des na de 'dra'i tshig phrag dog gis bslang yang mthar rang sma 'bebs byed du 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:1447: des na khyed cag gi smra ngan de la sgrub
NK132(no)004:1448: byed mi srid pas smra bcad byin pa yin no
NK132(no)004:1450: sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams kyi legs bshad kyi bcud bsdus te /
NK132(no)004:1451: ze chen ma h+aa pan+di ta 'jam mgon bstan 'dzin
NK132(no)004:1452: 'phel rgyas sam mthu stobs zhabs kyis 'di ltar gsungs
NK132(no)004:1453: te / mdor na rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs ni /
NK132(no)004:1459: spros ma spros kyi mthar ma lhung /
NK132(no)004:1464: brjod pa thams cad tshig dang tha snyad kyi spun pa /
NK132(no)004:1465: bsam tshad dpyad tshad thams cad rtog pas btags pa
NK132(no)004:1466: kho nar song bas rang ngo khas len gyi mthar
NK132(no)004:1467: mi gnas pa'i ngang du la bzla ba zhig ste
NK132(no)004:1468: / rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long las /
NK132(no)004:1469: rig pa'i chos thams cad bdag rtog gi blo dang bral bar shes par gyis shig /
NK132(no)004:1471: 'on kyang snga phyi ci rigs pa rnams su chos
NK132(no)004:1472: nyid zab mo blos byas kyis sgrub par rlom pa
NK132(no)004:1473: rnams ni chos nyid blo bral gyi gtam zab mos
NK132(no)004:1475: 'dis lam gyi rim pa thog ma rnams sun phyung
NK132(no)004:1476: ba ltar snang ba la zab mo'i phyogs dang rgya
NK132(no)004:1477: che ba'i gnas la shin tu mdza' ba ma yin
NK132(no)004:1478: pa'i rtog ge'i blo gros ltar snang dang lhan cig
NK132(no)004:1479: tu dus snga phyi tsam la'ang phrag pa dog pa'i
NK132(no)004:1480: dka' thub res 'ga' ma yin par lhur len pa
NK132(no)004:1483: bya ba rnams la rnal 'byor pa //
NK132(no)004:1484: lam chen dag tu yongs 'dzin pa //
NK132(no)004:1485: ri dwags smig rgyu bsnyegs pa ltar //
NK132(no)004:1486: rtag tu snang yang mi zin no //
NK132(no)004:1487: de bas de dag thams cad kyang //
NK132(no)004:1488: yang dag min pa'i blo dang bcas //
NK132(no)004:1490: gong ma gong ma khyad par 'phags //
NK132(no)004:1491: 'og ma'i blo na gong ma yi //
NK132(no)004:1492: shes rab kyis ni sun 'byin no //
NK132(no)004:1493: zhes gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya zhing /
NK132(no)004:1494: rtsod pa'i kun slong chos nyid bsam mi khyab pa'i ngang du zhi ba la mkhas par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:1495: de yang rdzogs pa chen po'i gshis la bya ba
NK132(no)004:1496: dang bral ba'i grub mtha' rgyu rkyen 'dus byas kyi
NK132(no)004:1497: khams su mi gnas pa'i ye shes nges don mthar
NK132(no)004:1498: thug pa drang thad du ston pa'i skabs /
NK132(no)004:1499: dkar nag rgyu 'bras la 'bad rtsol gyis byas chos la ltos 'cha' mi dgos par bshad pa la /
NK132(no)004:1500: bod 'ga' zhig gis spyod phyogs spangs pa'i ha shang
NK132(no)004:1501: dang mthun par thal lo zhes smre ngag 'don pa
NK132(no)004:1502: byung mod / lar bde bar gshegs pa'i chos kyi
NK132(no)004:1503: 'khor lo gsum bskor ba'i rim pa dang po dge
NK132(no)004:1504: mi dge'i rgyu 'bras mi bslu bar ston pa de
NK132(no)004:1505: byung mod / yang / 'jig rten gyi ngo la
NK132(no)004:1506: ltos nas bstan pa'i phyir drang don du bzhag pa
NK132(no)004:1507: byung mod / yang / yin / bar tha gnyis
NK132(no)004:1508: rnam thar sgo gsum gyi mtshan nyid du don gyis
NK132(no)004:1510: nges don zab mo'i gnas lugs ston pa zab pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1511: ches zab pa'i khyad par tsam yod /
NK132(no)004:1512: drang nges kyi don de yang 'dus byas dang /
NK132(no)004:1513: 'dus ma byas kyi sgo nas 'byed cing /
NK132(no)004:1514: brjod bya de dag shas che chung gi sgo nas
NK132(no)004:1515: dbye ba yin par mkhas pa kun la grags shing
NK132(no)004:1516: grub mod / de lta nyid kyis re zhig bka'
NK132(no)004:1517: bar pa rnam shes kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK132(no)004:1518: rang gi ngo bos stong par khas blangs nas /
NK132(no)004:1519: de nges don du 'chad pa'i skabs /
NK132(no)004:1520: gang la dmigs par bya ba thams cad dang bral ba /
NK132(no)004:1521: rtog pa dang rnam par rtog pa thams cad spangs pa /
NK132(no)004:1522: gang la blang ba dang dor bar bya pa'i chos dmigs su med pa ste /
NK132(no)004:1523: mdor na gzung 'dzin gyi chos rnams las yang dag
NK132(no)004:1524: par 'das pa'i 'dus ma byas kyi gnas lugs gang
NK132(no)004:1526: rnam thar sgo gsum gyi mtshan nyid kyang gnas pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:1527: rdzogs chen pas gzhi'i dus su /
NK132(no)004:1528: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du blta bas rgyu 'bras tha dad du mi 'byed /
NK132(no)004:1529: lam gyi dus su ci la'ang rnam par mi rtog pas blang ba dang dor ba'i mtha' mi dpyod /
NK132(no)004:1530: 'bras bu'i dus su thob bya re dogs dang bral
NK132(no)004:1531: ba'i gding chos kun zad sar 'khyol ba la grub
NK132(no)004:1534: yo ga shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs chen la //
NK132(no)004:1535: rgyu dang 'bras bu yod ces smra byed na //
NK132(no)004:1536: de ni rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i don mi ldan //
NK132(no)004:1537: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su smra byed na //
NK132(no)004:1538: sgro dang skur pa 'debs pa'i tshig yin te //
NK132(no)004:1539: de yis gnyis su med par rtogs pa med //
NK132(no)004:1540: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyis rtogs pa yang //
NK132(no)004:1541: gnyis su ma mthong rnam bzhag gcig tu rtogs //
NK132(no)004:1543: de lta bu'i grub matha'i 'cha' lugs chen po 'di ni /
NK132(no)004:1544: gnyis su mi gsungs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das
NK132(no)004:1545: kyi nges don zab mo'i mdo sde rnams kyi dgongs
NK132(no)004:1546: pa'ang de kho na nyid du gnas pa yin te
NK132(no)004:1547: / tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:1548: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin de gang zhe na /
NK132(no)004:1549: chos thams cad ni stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin can te dmigs pa dang bral ba'o //
NK132(no)004:1550: chos thams cad ni mtshan ma med pa'i rang bzhin
NK132(no)004:1551: can te rtog pa dang rnam par rtog pa dang
NK132(no)004:1552: bral ba'o // chos thams cad ni smon pa med pa'i rang bzhin can te /
NK132(no)004:1557: shin tu ngo bo nyid dang bral ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:1558: de ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK132(no)004:1559: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin gang yin pa de mya ngan las 'das pa'i rang bzhin yin no //
NK132(no)004:1560: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rang bzhin gang yin pa de chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin te /
NK132(no)004:1561: de'i phyir sems rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba zhes bya'o //
NK132(no)004:1563: de'i phyir lta ba khas len dang bral ba /
NK132(no)004:1564: sgom pa yid byed dang bral ba /
NK132(no)004:1565: spyod pa blang dor dang bral ba /
NK132(no)004:1566: 'bras bu re dogs dang bral ba bzhi po des
NK132(no)004:1567: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum gyi mtshan nyid nyams
NK132(no)004:1568: len rjen par de las gtan du ci zhig phab
NK132(no)004:1569: / khyed nyid kyis tshad mar khas len sor bzhag
NK132(no)004:1570: gi rgyud sde du ma'i rdzogs rim man ngag gis
NK132(no)004:1571: / 'chad pa na / grub mtha' 'khor 'das dbyer med ces pa 'di la ris ma byung /
NK132(no)004:1572: rtog ge'i blos bzhag pa'i grub mtha' dang ni 'di gnyis gcig tu mdza' ba'i skabs mi 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)004:1573: 'on te lta ba'i ldog pa nas de ltar yin kyang spyod pa'i phyogs dor bas so zer na /
NK132(no)004:1574: lta ba don dam pa'i bden pa ma 'khrul ba'i gnas lugs mthong ba la ltos te bzhag na /
NK132(no)004:1575: sems dang sems byung gi ngo na gnas pa'i bslab
NK132(no)004:1576: pa sogs 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa sogs byas chos
NK132(no)004:1577: dkar nag gi 'ching grol las 'das pa'i phyir blang
NK132(no)004:1579: de smon pa med pa'i mtshan nyid du gnas pa dkon brtsegs 'od srung gis zhus mdor /
NK132(no)004:1580: gang 'dus ma byas pa de ni 'phags pa rnams kyi rigs so //
NK132(no)004:1581: 'phags pa'i rigs gang yin pa de la bslab pa yang med /
NK132(no)004:1582: bslab pa las 'das pa yang med do //
NK132(no)004:1583: gang la bslab pa yang med /
NK132(no)004:1584: bslab pa las 'das pa yang med pa de la rgyu ba yang med /
NK132(no)004:1587: gang la rgyu ba yang med /
NK132(no)004:1589: rab tu rgyu ba yang med pa de la sems kyang med /
NK132(no)004:1590: sems las byung ba'i chos rnams kyang med /
NK132(no)004:1592: sems las byung ba'i chos rnams kyang med pa de la las kyang med /
NK132(no)004:1593: las kyi rnam par smin pa yang med do //
NK132(no)004:1595: las kyi rnam par smin pa yang med pa de la bde ba yang med /
NK132(no)004:1596: sdug bsngal ba yang med do //
NK132(no)004:1597: gang la bde ba yang med /
NK132(no)004:1598: sdug bsngal ba yang med pa de ni 'phags pa rnams kyi rigs so //
NK132(no)004:1599: 'phags pa rnams kyi rigs gang yin pa de la ni /
NK132(no)004:1601: las mngon par 'du bya ba yang med do //
NK132(no)004:1603: de la dge ba yang stong la /
NK132(no)004:1605: dge ba yang rnam par dben la /
NK132(no)004:1606: mi dge ba yang rnam par dben /
NK132(no)004:1607: dge ba yang mi dge ba dang mi 'drel /
NK132(no)004:1608: mi dge ba yang dge ba dang mi 'dre zhing /
NK132(no)004:1609: dge ba dang mi dge bar mngon par zhen pa'i rgyu dang rkyen med do //
NK132(no)004:1612: bsgom med sgom pa po yang med //
NK132(no)004:1613: lha med sngags kyang yod ma yin //
NK132(no)004:1614: zhes pa la sogs pa'i bstan pa rmad du byung
NK132(no)004:1615: ba'i sgra bsgrags pa 'di yang ha shang gi lugs
NK132(no)004:1617: spyir yang shes rab phyin ci ma log par rtogs pas /
NK132(no)004:1618: thabs de'i yan lag tsam du 'gyur ba ni sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ma nor ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:1620: tshul khrims las ni nyams sla yi //
NK132(no)004:1621: lta las de lta ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:1622: zhes bshad pa ltar lta ba ji bzhin par rtogs na /
NK132(no)004:1623: spyod pa ci la spyad kyang mi 'ching bar ma
NK132(no)004:1624: zad grol ba'i 'bras bu thob pa rgyal ba'i sras
NK132(no)004:1625: kyi gzhung lam nyid du gnas mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:1626: rdzogs pa chen po'i lam 'dir ni /
NK132(no)004:1627: chos nyid mnyam pa chen po'i klong du blang dor med par bzhag pas don 'grub pa las /
NK132(no)004:1628: spyod pa la ched 'dzin gyi bcos mas ma bsgrib pa ni khyad par gyi chos te /
NK132(no)004:1629: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa bstan pa las /
NK132(no)004:1630: rin chen byin gyis smras pa /
NK132(no)004:1634: rang gi lus las gyen du ma bskyod cig /
NK132(no)004:1636: lta ba tshar ma gcod cig /
NK132(no)004:1637: kun tu sbyor ba rnams ma ston cig /
NK132(no)004:1638: phung po rnams yongs su zungs shig /
NK132(no)004:1639: khams rnams ril por kyis shig /
NK132(no)004:1640: skye mched rnams la spyod cig /
NK132(no)004:1641: byis pa'i sa las ma 'da' zhig /
NK132(no)004:1642: mi dge ba la rtogs shig /
NK132(no)004:1644: sangs rgyas yid la ma byed cig /
NK132(no)004:1646: dge 'dun la ni mchod par ma byed cig /
NK132(no)004:1647: bslab pa dag yang dag par ma len cig /
NK132(no)004:1648: srid pa nye bar zhi ba don du ma gnyer cig /
NK132(no)004:1649: chu bo las ma brgal cig /
NK132(no)004:1650: ces gdams ngag 'di lta bu las dang po pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la gdams par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:1653: chos rnams kyi chos gnas pa 'di ni gnas pa kho na yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:1656: sems can sangs rgyas mi mnyam mnyam //
NK132(no)004:1657: bsgrub bya su zhig sgrub po gang //
NK132(no)004:1659: dngos rnams thams cad sgyu ma bzhin //
NK132(no)004:1660: skye dang sdud par mdzad pa po //
NK132(no)004:1661: des na de yis sdig mi 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1662: bsod nams dag kyang de bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:1663: gang la sdig dang bsod nams med //
NK132(no)004:1664: de ni byang chub yin par gsungs //
NK132(no)004:1666: de dag dang gcig par rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:1667: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor rang la rang snang bas //
NK132(no)004:1668: lha la mchod pa mi 'bul phul na 'ching bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1669: mchod pa phyag rgya la sogs sku la sgrib pa yin //
NK132(no)004:1670: phyag rgya mi bsgyur bsgyur na rin chen brlag par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1671: 'khor ba mi spang spangs nas sangs mi rgya //
NK132(no)004:1672: sangs rgyas gud na med pas rig pa nyid las gang yang med //
NK132(no)004:1673: 'khor ba gud na med de rang gi sems su thams cad 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1674: 'dus byas dge rtsa mi bya byas na 'ching bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1675: mchod rten lha khang la sogs 'dus byas dge rtsa spang //
NK132(no)004:1676: byas pa'i chos ni mi zin bzhag na zin par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1677: bya ba btang ba'i rnal 'byor mi spong spangs na de bzhin gshegs //
NK132(no)004:1678: yang dag sangs rgyas lam ni de bzhin kun la shes par bya //
NK132(no)004:1679: zhes gshis la bya ba thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK132(no)004:1680: chos nyid mnyam pa chen po'i don la gding gyur
NK132(no)004:1681: pa'i lta bas zin pa'i tshe /
NK132(no)004:1682: 'du byas pa'i dka' nag gi las kyang mnyam pa nyid du sgra ji bzhin par bstan pa /
NK132(no)004:1684: dge ba byar med sdig pa spang du med //
NK132(no)004:1685: dge sdig gnyis dang bral ba'i rig pa chos kyi sku //
NK132(no)004:1686: dge ba mi bya byas na sangs rgyas med //
NK132(no)004:1687: sdig pa mi spang spangs na sangs rgyas 'grub mi 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1689: tshul de lta bu thos nas snying 'gas nas srog 'dor ba tsam du byed pa mang mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:1690: de dag gi rang bzhin khong du ma chud pas blor ma shong ba la khag med de /
NK132(no)004:1691: 'di ltar 'phags pa kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:1693: lha'i bu don dam par na de bzhin nyid dang /
NK132(no)004:1695: shin tu mi skye ba gang dang mnyam pa /
NK132(no)004:1696: don dam par na mtshams med pa lnga po dag kyang de dang mnyam mo //
NK132(no)004:1697: don dam par na de bzhin nyid dang /
NK132(no)004:1699: shin tu mi skye ba gang dang mnyam pa /
NK132(no)004:1700: don dam par na lta bar gyur pa rnams de dang mnyam mo //
NK132(no)004:1702: de ltar bstan pa nyid kyis spyod pa'i phyogs rnams yal bar 'dor ba mi 'grub ste /
NK132(no)004:1703: rang lugs sems sde'i rgyud kyi lung rdo la gser zhun du /
NK132(no)004:1704: bde gshegs ma lus yum du gyur pas rgyal ba kun gyi lam gcig pu //
NK132(no)004:1705: tshul khrims la sogs pha rol phyin lam spyod pa rgya mtsho'i gzhir gyur pa //
NK132(no)004:1706: zhes shes rab kyi yan lag tu gyur pa'i thabs
NK132(no)004:1707: spyod pa'i phyogs mi 'dor ba'i grub mtha' chen po
NK132(no)004:1708: 'di yod bzhin / thabs la mkhas pa'i phyir gnas
NK132(no)004:1709: skabs su kun rdzob bden pa 'dor ba ma yin
NK132(no)004:1710: 'di yod bzhin / mod kyi / 'on kyang gnas
NK132(no)004:1711: lugs bden pa'i chos nyid ma 'khrul ba rang gi
NK132(no)004:1713: bden gnyis res 'jog gi phyogs su ma lhung bar /
NK132(no)004:1714: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu sogs byang chub phyogs
NK132(no)004:1715: su gyur pa'i lam bden gyi chos rnams kyang 'di
NK132(no)004:1718: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos sku nyid //
NK132(no)004:1719: gsal 'grib snang ba'i mun pa sangs //
NK132(no)004:1720: rtag chad gnyis kyi mtha' las 'das //
NK132(no)004:1721: mun snang gnyis kyis gzung du med //
NK132(no)004:1722: gcig dang du ma'i chos las 'das //
NK132(no)004:1723: snang dang mi snang chos las 'das //
NK132(no)004:1724: skye dang 'jig pa'i tshig dang bral //
NK132(no)004:1725: gol sgrib bdag rtog ga la yod //
NK132(no)004:1726: bsam pa nyid la bsal du med //
NK132(no)004:1727: shes rab pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1728: rig gsal chos kyi sku la 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1729: bsam gtan pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1730: sgron ma cog bzhag ngang du 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1731: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin mtha' ni //
NK132(no)004:1732: rtog med rang byung don la 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1733: bzod pa'i pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1734: snang ba thad kar gcod la 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1735: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1737: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1739: smon lam pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1740: snang ba re dogs med la 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1741: thabs kyi pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1742: rig pa cog bzhag ngang du 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1743: stobs kyi pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1745: ye shes pha rol phyin pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1746: rkyen dang bral bar snang la 'dus //
NK132(no)004:1747: de bzhin pha rol phyin pa'i don //
NK132(no)004:1748: rang bzhin kun khyab ye shes so //
NK132(no)004:1750: de dang mtshungs par tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:1751: gang mi 'dzin pa ni sbyin pa /
NK132(no)004:1756: mi dmigs pa shes rab bo //
NK132(no)004:1759: don gyi snying po rnal ma byar med la //
NK132(no)004:1760: rnal 'byor chen po rnams kyis mthong ba ni //
NK132(no)004:1761: ye nas rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK132(no)004:1762: rgyu las 'bras bu lha yi dkyil 'khor de //
NK132(no)004:1763: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi yis rdzogs byas te //
NK132(no)004:1764: 'phro 'du bdag nyid lhun gyis grub par gnas //
NK132(no)004:1766: 'o na chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs dge sdig
NK132(no)004:1767: bcings grol las 'das pa'i 'dus ma byas kyi khams
NK132(no)004:1768: su gnas na las dkar nag dang rgyu 'bras kyi
NK132(no)004:1769: tshul gsungs pa rnams dgos pa med par 'gyur ro
NK132(no)004:1770: zhe na / rnam shes kyi ngo la dgongs nas
NK132(no)004:1771: de skad du gsungs pa dper na rmi lam gyi
NK132(no)004:1772: yul du legs nyes gang snang rmi lam du bden
NK132(no)004:1773: zhe na / kyang / sad pa'i gnas skabs su
NK132(no)004:1774: mi bden pa lta bu la dgongs nas chos thams
NK132(no)004:1775: cad rmi lam lta bu dang /
NK132(no)004:1776: sgyu ma lta bu zhes mi bden pa'i dpes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:1777: rnam shes kyis bsdus pa'i 'khrul snang ma zad kyi bar du ni blang dor kyang yod la /
NK132(no)004:1778: las dkar nag gi rgyu dang 'bras bu'i rnam pa'ang mi bslu ba'i tshul gyis 'byung mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:1779: 'khrul pa zad nas bden pa mthong ba'i ye shes kyi ldog pa la de dag mi snang ste /
NK132(no)004:1780: yul can gzung 'dzin gyi shes pa med pas yul
NK132(no)004:1781: kun rdzob gnyis bcas snang bar mi 'gyur ba ni
NK132(no)004:1782: sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa'i dgongs pa sgra ji
NK132(no)004:1783: bzhin nges shing / mchog gzigs rnams kyi thugs rgyud la rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:1784: nges pa'i don zab mo 'grel par lung bstan pa'i
NK132(no)004:1785: shing rta chen po dag gi dgongs pa yang 'dir
NK132(no)004:1788: dper na gnyid log gnyid dbang gis //
NK132(no)004:1789: bu dang bud med gzhal yas khang //
NK132(no)004:1790: gnas la sogs pa mthong gyur pa //
NK132(no)004:1791: sad na de yis mi mthong ltar //
NK132(no)004:1792: de bzhin kun rdzob shes pa dag /
NK132(no)004:1793: blo gros mig ni bye gyur cing //
NK132(no)004:1794: mi shes gnyis dang bral gyur nas //
NK132(no)004:1795: sad pa'i tshe la mi gzigs so //
NK132(no)004:1796: de bzhin mkhas pa yang dag gis //
NK132(no)004:1797: shes pa'i nyi mas mi shes pa'i //
NK132(no)004:1798: bag chags ma lus bcom pa'i tshe //
NK132(no)004:1799: sems dang sems 'byung yul mi gzigs //
NK132(no)004:1802: mig ni rab rib can gyis dmigs pa yis //
NK132(no)004:1803: rab rib med shes la gnod min ji ltar //
NK132(no)004:1804: de bzhin dri med ye shes spang ba'i blos //
NK132(no)004:1805: dri med bloo la gnod pa yod ma yin //
NK132(no)004:1808: ji srid rkyen rnams tshogs gyur na //
NK132(no)004:1810: rkyen rnams rgyun ni chad pa na //
NK132(no)004:1811: kun rdzob tu yang mi 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)004:1812: gang tshe 'khrul pa yod min na //
NK132(no)004:1813: kun rdzob gang gis dmigs par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1814: zhes sogs kyis bshad pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:1815: de ltar grub pa'i rdzogs pa chen po 'dir /
NK132(no)004:1816: lta spyod mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes du ma
NK132(no)004:1817: ro gcig chen po'i ngang du la bzla ba'i dbang
NK132(no)004:1819: ye shes kyis kun rdzob rdzun par rtogs pas 'dus
NK132(no)004:1820: byas kyi dge rtsa la mi re bas shes rab
NK132(no)004:1822: rnam shes kyi ldog pa la blang dor yod pas thabs la skur ba ma btab /
NK132(no)004:1824: yid la byed pa thams cad rnam par rtog pa
NK132(no)004:1825: las ma 'das pas bsgom par bya ba rdul tsam
NK132(no)004:1826: med / 'bras bu'i dus su sems dang sems las
NK132(no)004:1827: byung ba thams cad rgyun 'gag na kun rdzob gang
NK132(no)004:1829: gnad 'di bka' 'khor phyi ma gnyis kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phug mthar thug pa /
NK132(no)004:1830: 'phags pa'i yul dang gangs can gyi khrod 'dir bde
NK132(no)004:1831: bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa ma 'khrul par bzung ba
NK132(no)004:1832: rnams kyis legs par bshad pa'i tshul rma med pa
NK132(no)004:1833: yin no // de ltar yin pa'ang rngog lo chen
NK132(no)004:1834: po nas jo zhal yan chad kyi klog pa mkhas
NK132(no)004:1835: yin no // pa rnams dang / bsam gtan pa
NK132(no)004:1836: 'khrul med thams cad kyi yig char 'di bzhin bshad
NK132(no)004:1837: yin no // pa rnams dang / pas so //
NK132(no)004:1838: spyir bdag cag gi ston pas rnam shes kyi ngo
NK132(no)004:1839: la dgongs nas blang dor dang rgyu 'bras kyi rnam
NK132(no)004:1840: gzhag rmi lam gyi yul du de'i rgyu 'bras tshad
NK132(no)004:1841: mar gyur pa tsam zhig bstan pas /
NK132(no)004:1842: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes kun rdzob tshad mar grub pa'i go ba zhig la glo ba zhen /
NK132(no)004:1843: rgyu des spyod pa'i phyogs su zhen pa a 'thas ko 'thas su song bas /
NK132(no)004:1844: 'phags pa'i shes rab dang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes la bcad dras byed pa zhig byung /
NK132(no)004:1845: des zab mo'i gnas phyin ci ma log pa'i grub mtha' la'ang yid mi ches pa 'di byung /
NK132(no)004:1846: de dag gis bde bar gshegs pa'i phrin las rmad
NK132(no)004:1847: po che chud gsan pa la rnam rig gzo ba
NK132(no)004:1849: mnyam gzhag gi tshe ci yang yid la mi byed pas ha shang gi sgom du gyur na /
NK132(no)004:1850: khyed cag gis dbu ma'i gzhung chen por 'dod pa'i
NK132(no)004:1851: slob dpon b+ha bya'i dbu ma rin chen sgron me
NK132(no)004:1852: las / shes pa gang la'ang mi rtog /
NK132(no)004:1854: dran pa dang yid la byed pa thams cad spangs te /
NK132(no)004:1855: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyas par bshad cing /
NK132(no)004:1856: de dang mthun par k+aa ma la sh+ai la'i bsgom
NK132(no)004:1857: rim gsum gar yang bshad pas dbu ma rang rgyud
NK132(no)004:1858: pa la grags pa'i gtam zhig yin ni yin /
NK132(no)004:1859: jo bo'i dbu ma'i sgom rim du'ang 'di bzhin bshad /
NK132(no)004:1860: de ha shang dang mthun rung mi mthun rung mthun par khas blangs zin pa de yin /
NK132(no)004:1861: rdzogs chen gyi rang byung rig pa ye grol spang
NK132(no)004:1862: gnyen dang bral ba'i lhag mthong gi ngo bo de
NK132(no)004:1863: nyid so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su nges pas
NK132(no)004:1864: de nyid bsgom gyi rten du byas na /
NK132(no)004:1865: rtog dpyod zhen 'dzin gyi mtha' dang bral ba'i chos nyid la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK132(no)004:1866: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngang der
NK132(no)004:1867: gshis mtha' grol chen po'i gnas lugs phyin ci ma
NK132(no)004:1868: log par gnas pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:1870: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:1871: chos rnams rang sar bzhag pa ste //
NK132(no)004:1872: snang shes chos nyid zung 'jug pas //
NK132(no)004:1873: ye grol cog bzhag nyid la thug /
NK132(no)004:1874: dgongs pa blo las 'das pa dang //
NK132(no)004:1875: mtshan bcas rang sar dag pa dang //
NK132(no)004:1876: stong dang ngo bo'i mtha' grol dang //
NK132(no)004:1877: 'gyu zad rtog pa med pa dang //
NK132(no)004:1880: tshul 'di ltar ma rtogs pas rtog dpyod kyi 'du
NK132(no)004:1881: 'phro 'ba' zhig la lhag mthong du re bas chos
NK132(no)004:1882: nyid rnal ma'i don la ma re zhig /
NK132(no)004:1883: sems sems byung gi rgyu ba ma log par rtog
NK132(no)004:1884: pas bzhag pa'i stong pa 'ba' zhig la mtshan mar
NK132(no)004:1885: dmigs pa'i 'dzin stangs kyi blo dang mi bral ba
NK132(no)004:1886: ni sgrib pa mi bzad pa skye ba'i bdag nyid
NK132(no)004:1887: can gyi lta ba chen por 'gyur te /
NK132(no)004:1889: gang zag tu lta ba ri rab tsam la gnas pa'ang sla'i /
NK132(no)004:1890: mngon pa'i nga rgyal can stong pa nyid du lta ba ni de lta bu ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:1892: 'od srungs lta bar gyur pa thams cad byung ba ni stong pa nyid yin na /
NK132(no)004:1893: 'od srungs gang stong nyid kho nar lta ba de ni gsor mi rung ngo //
NK132(no)004:1894: zhes dmigs pa can gyi stong nyid la 'dzin cing
NK132(no)004:1895: zhen pa ni thub pa'i gsung rab las nyams par
NK132(no)004:1896: ston pa rang nyid kyis gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:1897: de lta na'ang re zhig klu sgrub kyis /
NK132(no)004:1898: tha snyad la ni ma brten par //
NK132(no)004:1899: dam pa'i don ni rtogs mi 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:1900: zhes bshad pas dgag sgrub kyi rnam dpyod la brten
NK132(no)004:1901: nas rtogs dgos par bstan pa'i phyir zhe na ma
NK132(no)004:1902: yin te / lung de'i go ba ni /
NK132(no)004:1903: don dam pa'i bden pa thog mar brjod bya rjod
NK132(no)004:1904: byed kyi tshul la brten nas byis pa la mdzub
NK132(no)004:1905: mos zla ba mtshon nas ston pa bzhin rtogs dgos
NK132(no)004:1907: mtha' gcig tu rtog ge'i rigs pas dpyad nas rtogs par gsungs pa ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:1908: de phyir de ni rtog ge ba //
NK132(no)004:1909: ro dang 'dra bas rnam par brtag /
NK132(no)004:1910: ces rnam grangs du mas smad par mdzad pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:1912: dgag sgrub kyi brag ri la bskor ba byas nas
NK132(no)004:1913: rang gnas kyi ye shes sgro skur gyi lam du
NK132(no)004:1914: spur / blos dpyad par mtha' gnyis bsal bar rlom
NK132(no)004:1915: pa srin bu'i kha chus rang nyid bcings pa ltar
NK132(no)004:1916: chos nyid yin lugs kyi steng du phebs pa shin
NK132(no)004:1917: tu dka' ste chos nyid ni bsam gyis mi khyab
NK132(no)004:1918: spur / pa'i phyir / tha snyad kyis mtshon du med la /
NK132(no)004:1919: tha snyad ni rtog brtags kyi ngo bor gnas pa ste /
NK132(no)004:1921: so sor rang rig mtshan nyid spyod yul te //
NK132(no)004:1922: brjod du med cing tha snyad yongs chad pa //
NK132(no)004:1923: rtsod dang bral ba don dam chos yin te //
NK132(no)004:1924: de ni rtog ge kun las 'das mtshan nyid //
NK132(no)004:1926: 'di ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i bzhugs stangs gsum gyis gzer bsdams /
NK132(no)004:1927: gzigs stangs gsum gyis gnad gcun /
NK132(no)004:1928: sgron ma drug gi lam nas chos nyid yid dpyod
NK132(no)004:1929: dang bral bar mngon sum du mthong ba'i phyir lam
NK132(no)004:1930: khyad gnam sa tsam yod pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:1932: dam pa'i don ni blo bral bas //
NK132(no)004:1933: dbang po cig char rang grol nas //
NK132(no)004:1934: mngon sum mthong ba'i gnad kyis ni //
NK132(no)004:1935: rang gi grub pa'i mtha' zhig pas //
NK132(no)004:1936: gang la zhen dang 'dzin med par //
NK132(no)004:1937: yang dag chos nyid ro myong nas //
NK132(no)004:1938: khams gsum 'khor ba rten med par //
NK132(no)004:1939: mkha' la mkha' nyid thim pa ltar //
NK132(no)004:1940: rnal 'byor mchog kyang de bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:1942: rgyu mtshan de rnams la dgongs nas /
NK132(no)004:1944: a ti yo ga'i lta ba yang //
NK132(no)004:1945: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK132(no)004:1947: 'on kyang lta ba zab mo'i gnas lugs ma 'khrul
NK132(no)004:1948: bar grub pa'i ldog pa nas ye shes su legs
NK132(no)004:1949: par bshad kyang / de nyid theg pa ma yin pa ni nongs te /
NK132(no)004:1952: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes de nyid la /
NK132(no)004:1955: yongs su rdzogs pa la brten nas 'phags bzhi'i rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK132(no)004:1957: gzugs kyi rnam pa dman pa dang //
NK132(no)004:1958: bar ma mchog la nam mkha' bzhin //
NK132(no)004:1959: zhes snod bzang ngan gyi nang gi nam mkha' la
NK132(no)004:1960: bzang ngan med pa'i dpes rang bzhin dag pa'i chos
NK132(no)004:1962: chos can glo bur gyi dri ma de sgrib byed rnams bral stobs che chung gis /
NK132(no)004:1963: ye shes de nyid skabs dang mthun par mngon du
NK132(no)004:1964: 'gyur bar bya rgyu yod pa'i phyir theg par bzhag
NK132(no)004:1965: pa la 'gal ba'i gnas cha tsam med de /
NK132(no)004:1966: 'dis 'degs pa dang 'dir 'degs pa ste gnyis kar theg pa'i sgra bshad 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:1967: sangs rgyas ma yin pa'i 'phags pa gsum gyi rgyud la ye shes med par bzhed na der zad /
NK132(no)004:1968: cung zad mthong ba nas rdzogs pa mthong ba'i bar
NK132(no)004:1969: ye shes gcig pu'i steng du sa lam gyi rnam
NK132(no)004:1970: bzhag kun 'byung bas theg par bzhag pa mdo rgyud
NK132(no)004:1971: kyi dgongs pa zab mo yin te /
NK132(no)004:1972: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK132(no)004:1973: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni theg pa chen po'o //
NK132(no)004:1976: khyed rang gi gzhi yi skabs su 'khrul pa byung ste /
NK132(no)004:1977: de la gsar ma'i lugs ni /
NK132(no)004:1978: klu sgrub dpa' bo la sogs 'phags yul gyi mkhas grub phal mo che dang /
NK132(no)004:1979: khyad par chos kyi grags pa'i bzhed pa /
NK132(no)004:1980: de la kun gzhi'i rnam shes ni //
NK132(no)004:1981: ngo bo ma bsgrib lung ma bstan //
NK132(no)004:1982: zhes pa ltar me long rang gi ngo bo'i dus na gzugs brnyan gyis stong pa bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:1983: kun gzhi rang gi ngo bo'i dus na tshogs bdun sems byung dang bcas pas stong pa /
NK132(no)004:1984: gzugs brnyan cir yang snang rung gi gsal ba mi 'dor ba bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:1985: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi bag chags 'jog rung gi nus pa mi 'dor ba /
NK132(no)004:1986: yul rkyen dang ma 'phrad pa'i me long rang gi
NK132(no)004:1987: dus na lung ma bstan gyi gsal ba yin pa
NK132(no)004:1988: bzhin / kun gzhi 'khrul grol 'du byed ma g.yos
NK132(no)004:1989: pa'i dus na 'khor 'das kyi phyogs su ma lhung
NK132(no)004:1990: ba'i lung ma bstan du bzhed pa las /
NK132(no)004:1991: khyed rang gi lugs la gzhi ka dag dang ye grol du 'dod zer ba /
NK132(no)004:1992: kun gzhi dang ka dag gcig gam tha dad /
NK132(no)004:1993: gcig na kun gzhi 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i spyi gzhi
NK132(no)004:1994: yin pa'i don gyis lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig
NK132(no)004:1995: pa yod la / de ma rig pa thams cad
NK132(no)004:1996: kyi rtsa ba yin pas ka nas dag pa dang
NK132(no)004:1997: ye grol gyi don ma tshang /
NK132(no)004:1998: kun gzhi dang ka dag mi gcig na /
NK132(no)004:1999: de gnyis thog mar gang snga /
NK132(no)004:2001: dang po ka dag la rjes zhig nas kun gzhi'i
NK132(no)004:2002: gnas lugs byung ba ni lung rigs kyi ngos nas
NK132(no)004:2004: kun gzhi 'khor 'das kyi phyogs su ma lhung ba'i gdod ma'i gnas lugs yin la /
NK132(no)004:2005: de'i gong na gzhan med pas so //
NK132(no)004:2006: kun gzhi snga na ka dag dang ye grol du mi 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)004:2007: de bas na ka dag ces pa bon gyi brda ming barjesa pa ste /
NK132(no)004:2008: dang po ye grol med du 'dod pa la ka dag /
NK132(no)004:2009: de nas ye yod cung tsam srid pa la ma
NK132(no)004:2010: rtogs pa 'khor ba'i 'khrul gzhi zhes ming 'dogs bsgyur
NK132(no)004:2011: ba yin mod / ces par lan 'di skad smra ste /
NK132(no)004:2012: 'di don khyed rang thos rgya chung zhing kun gzhi'i spu ris ma 'byed par zad de /
NK132(no)004:2014: kun gzhi dbyings kyi cha dang /
NK132(no)004:2015: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi /
NK132(no)004:2016: bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi ste gsum las /
NK132(no)004:2018: dbyings de bzhin nyid de 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma phyes pa'i cha nas bzhag pa ste /
NK132(no)004:2019: 'di la ye don gyi kun gzhir bshad de /
NK132(no)004:2020: kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin te //
NK132(no)004:2024: de'i steng ngam ngang na rig pa ye nas 'dus
NK132(no)004:2025: ma byas pa'i rang bzhin lhun grub tu brten pa'i
NK132(no)004:2026: cha nas sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhir 'dod de
NK132(no)004:2029: thugs rje kun la khyab cing 'char ba /
NK132(no)004:2030: yon tan nor bu rin chen ltar lhun gyis grub pa /
NK132(no)004:2032: dri ma dang bral ba med pa /
NK132(no)004:2033: ye nas 'od gsal sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK132(no)004:2034: med pa'i dgongs pa gnas lugs kyi don zhes bya'o
NK132(no)004:2035: // de yang rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa'i cha nas nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK132(no)004:2039: mngon par 'dus ma byas sogs ming gis btags kyang /
NK132(no)004:2040: ci yang med pa'i stong pa phyang chad min te /
NK132(no)004:2041: sku dang ye shes sogs kyi yon tan lhun gyis grub pa can te /
NK132(no)004:2042: de'i ngor 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pas ka nas dag cing stong pa ste /
NK132(no)004:2043: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK132(no)004:2044: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor yongs gang yang //
NK132(no)004:2045: tshes kyi dbang gis 'jig rten na //
NK132(no)004:2046: zla ba skye 'bri rnam par rtog /
NK132(no)004:2047: de bzhin don gyi kun gzhi yang //
NK132(no)004:2048: rtag tu bde gshegs snying po can //
NK132(no)004:2049: snying po de la kun gzhi'i sgras //
NK132(no)004:2050: de bzhin gshegs pas bstan par mdzad //
NK132(no)004:2051: de nyid mi shes byis pa rnams //
NK132(no)004:2052: bag chags dbang gis kun gzhi yang //
NK132(no)004:2053: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs dang //
NK132(no)004:2054: las zhes kun nas nyon mongs med //
NK132(no)004:2055: rang bzhin dag cing dri ma med //
NK132(no)004:2056: yon tan yid bzhin nor bu 'dra //
NK132(no)004:2058: de ltar yongs shes rnam par grol //
NK132(no)004:2060: 'di la ming gi rnam grangs kyang /
NK132(no)004:2061: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi /
NK132(no)004:2062: thog med chos khams dge ba /
NK132(no)004:2064: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba /
NK132(no)004:2066: gnas lugs de kho na nyid kyi don /
NK132(no)004:2067: rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK132(no)004:2068: shes rab phar phyin sogs rten gzhi dang /
NK132(no)004:2070: bral rgyu byed pa sogs kyi cha nas btags pa bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK132(no)004:2071: 'di bral gazhi'am kun tu bzang po'i grol sa dngos yin /
NK132(no)004:2072: de'i phyir ka dag ces pa gdod nas 'khrul ma
NK132(no)004:2073: myong ba'i rang bzhin rnam dag de la zer zhing
NK132(no)004:2074: ye grol zhes pa'ang de dang don gcig /
NK132(no)004:2076: de nyid ma rig pas gzhi byas te /
NK132(no)004:2077: 'khor ba'i chos rnam shes tshogs brgyad bag chags dang
NK132(no)004:2078: bcas pa brten pa'i cha nas bag chags sna tshogs
NK132(no)004:2084: rnam par byang ba'i las rang bzhin gdod ma nas
NK132(no)004:2085: med la glo bur du skyes pa rnams gsog pa'i
NK132(no)004:2087: de yang dge mi dge gnyis char brten la ngo
NK132(no)004:2088: bo gti mug yin pa'i phyir lung ma bstan yin
NK132(no)004:2089: no // kha cig gis 'di gti mug ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2090: dug lnga ka'i rten byed pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2091: rnam byang gi rten byed par bshad pa'ang ma go ba'i rnam 'gyur te /
NK132(no)004:2092: 'dir dug lngar phye ba'i gti mug min te /
NK132(no)004:2093: lhan skyes kyi ma rig pa de la de ltar btags so //
NK132(no)004:2094: rnam byang gi rten byed pa'ang dpyad dgos te /
NK132(no)004:2096: glo bur gyi dri ma mtha' dag dag pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2097: dag pa gnyis ldan sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dang snying po gnyis kyi rten mi byed de /
NK132(no)004:2098: kun gzhi de gnas 'gyur dgos pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:2100: kun gzhi dag pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK132(no)004:2103: kun gzhi gnas 'gyur pa ni ngo bo nyid kyi chos kyi sku zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:2105: sdong bu la brten pa'i mar mes rang bsreg pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2106: bud shing la brten pa'i mes rang bsreg pa sogs bzhin /
NK132(no)004:2107: kun gzhi la brten nas tshogs gnyis kyi lam gyis 'khor ba'i bag chags rang sbyong zhing /
NK132(no)004:2108: rigs dang khams kyi dri ma bsal te /
NK132(no)004:2109: dang po ji ltar gnas pa bzhin mngon sum du
NK132(no)004:2110: gsal ba'i byang chub mngon du byed pas rkyen dag
NK132(no)004:2112: phyis sbyong byed kyi gnyen po de yang tshig par byed de /
NK132(no)004:2113: blos btags kyi dge ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:2115: shes bya'i bud shing skam po ma lus dag /
NK132(no)004:2117: de lta na dor ba med pa'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK132(no)004:2118: chos sum cu rtsa bdun yod pa ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK132(no)004:2119: sangs rgyas kyi sas bsdus pa'i chos de dag bral 'bras kyi tshul du yod mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:2120: slob lam gyis bsdus pa ni yod pa ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2121: lam mthar phyin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:2123: lhan skyes ma rig pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2124: bag chags sna tshogs kun gzhi dang /
NK132(no)004:2125: thog mtha' med pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2127: ye nas gnas pa'i mi shes pa sogs su bshad do //
NK132(no)004:2128: de la brten pa'i tshogs brgyad ni /
NK132(no)004:2129: dper na bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi lung
NK132(no)004:2130: ma bstan ni me long dang 'dra zhing kun gzhi'i
NK132(no)004:2131: rnam par shes pa ni me long gi dwangs gsal
NK132(no)004:2132: dang 'dra / sgo lnga'i rnam shes ni gzugs brnyan shar ba dang 'dra /
NK132(no)004:2133: sgo lnga'i snang yul la 'di zhes dang por shar ba ni yid shes /
NK132(no)004:2134: de'i rjes la yul chags sdang bar ma gsum dang
NK132(no)004:2135: mtshungs ldan du shar ba ni nyon mongs pa can
NK132(no)004:2138: shes pa gang la'ang mi rtog yengs thabs tshe //
NK132(no)004:2139: snang yul mi 'dzin rtse gcig kun gzhi'i dus //
NK132(no)004:2140: gsal snang gang la'ang der 'dzin mi 'jug pa //
NK132(no)004:2141: kun gzhi'i rnam shes dwangs gsal g.yo ba med //
NK132(no)004:2142: sgo lnga'i yul dang dgag sgrub gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK132(no)004:2143: tshogs bdun yul la rags par rtog pa na //
NK132(no)004:2144: rnam shes bdun zhes nye bar btags pa yin //
NK132(no)004:2146: des na kun gzhi lung ma bstan dang ka dag grol sa yin pas gcig ma yin la /
NK132(no)004:2147: de nyid rang thog tu rig na sangs rgyas dang /
NK132(no)004:2148: ma rig par 'khrul pa'i dbang du song na sems
NK132(no)004:2149: can zhes brjod pas tha dad pa'ang ma yin te
NK132(no)004:2151: 'du byed khams dang don dam mtshan nyid ni //
NK132(no)004:2152: gcig dang tha dad bral ba'i mtshan nyid de //
NK132(no)004:2153: gcig dang tha dad nyid du gang rtog pa //
NK132(no)004:2154: de dag tshul min lta la zhugs pa yin //
NK132(no)004:2157: sems dang rig pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK132(no)004:2158: gcig min tha dad ma yin la //
NK132(no)004:2159: dbye ba rab tu dka' ba'i chos //
NK132(no)004:2161: ka dag dang kun gzhi la snga phyi med de
NK132(no)004:2162: lhan cig skyes pa yin pas na bya dang sgo
NK132(no)004:2164: bya med na sgo nga mi 'byung la /
NK132(no)004:2165: sgo nga med na bya mi 'byung ba bzhin rang bzhin lhan cig skyes par 'dod do //
NK132(no)004:2166: des na sa bon gyi gzhung ltar ye med stong pa de la ka dag tu btags nas /
NK132(no)004:2167: des slar 'khrul snang gi 'khor ba'i gzhi byed pa ltar 'dod pa min te /
NK132(no)004:2168: gzhi ka dag rang gi ngo bo la dus gsum
NK132(no)004:2169: du 'khrul pas bslad gzhug tu med pa'i phyir ro
NK132(no)004:2171: thod rgal dang lhun grub 'od gsal gyi snang ba zhes zab zab mor rlom ste /
NK132(no)004:2174: mig la tshos ma bkab pa'i mthong snang dang /
NK132(no)004:2175: rna ba bkag pa'i sgra dang /
NK132(no)004:2177: 'bag chas la sogs pa'i ngo sprod zhig 'dug pa /
NK132(no)004:2178: de'i skabs shig na gsal ba'i rig pa rdo rje
NK132(no)004:2179: lu gu rgyud du grags pa de chos nyid mngon
NK132(no)004:2180: sum yin nam / nyams snang gi'am /
NK132(no)004:2182: chos nyid mngon sum yin na /
NK132(no)004:2183: chos nyid kyi spyod yul yin phyir rang snang ye
NK132(no)004:2184: shes kyi rol par ngang gis gsal ba las 'du
NK132(no)004:2185: byed kyi rkyen sna tshogs mi dgos la /
NK132(no)004:2186: dbang po dang dbang shes kyi mthong bya'i yul ma yin /
NK132(no)004:2187: nyams kyi mngon sum yin na /
NK132(no)004:2188: dus nyams ni sgom pa la ltos te lam rtags kyi ngo bor gsal ba zhig na /
NK132(no)004:2189: 'di ni de yang ma yin te lam ma bsgoms kyang rkyen snang sna tshogs dus na gsal /
NK132(no)004:2190: dbang po'i mngon sum yin na /
NK132(no)004:2191: chos nyid mngon sum zhes tags su mi rung la /
NK132(no)004:2192: rung na'ang dbang po'i yul du dngos su snang ba'i chos nyid gad mo'i gnas so //
NK132(no)004:2193: yang rkyen sna tshogs pa las byung ba'i kha dog de dag /
NK132(no)004:2194: rang gi snying ga na sems nyid 'od lnga'i rnam
NK132(no)004:2195: par bzhugs pa'i rtsal gdangs phyir shar ba'i rnam par
NK132(no)004:2196: mthong ba yin ces zer nas nyi zer sogs la
NK132(no)004:2197: lta bar byed / snying nang na rang la yod
NK132(no)004:2198: pa'i rtsal yin na nyi zer sogs la ma ltos
NK132(no)004:2199: par rtsol med du gsal dgos te mi gsal /
NK132(no)004:2200: rkyen gyis bskul dgos zer na /
NK132(no)004:2201: dper na 'char gzhi snying nang na 'od lnga'i rnam pa can gyi sems gcig /
NK132(no)004:2202: shar ba nyi zer gyi ngogs na lu gu rgyud
NK132(no)004:2203: kyi sems gcig /'dzin pa'i lu gu rgyud mig shes
NK132(no)004:2204: kyi lta ba'i sems gcig ste gsum yod par 'gyur
NK132(no)004:2205: la / de ltar 'dod na sangs rgyas pa las
NK132(no)004:2206: lkog tu gyur pa'i grub mtha' zhig yin pa 'dra
NK132(no)004:2207: la / la / snying nang na sems nyid 'od lnga'i rnam par 'dzin pa 'di dang /
NK132(no)004:2208: rtag par lta ba bdag tu lta ba bza' ba
NK132(no)004:2209: po byed pa po rang dbang can gyi sems zhig
NK132(no)004:2210: rnam par che ste sgo nga tsam /
NK132(no)004:2211: chung ste yungs 'bru tsam zhig yod par 'dzin pa ni khyad par cung zad kyang ma mchis /
NK132(no)004:2212: khyad yod na de'i sgrub byed kyang smra bar rigs la /
NK132(no)004:2213: 'on kyang 'od de snying nang du yod nges yin
NK132(no)004:2214: na'ang rtsal phyi rol du mthong ba'i nges pa med
NK132(no)004:2215: cing / 'od de'i rten snying dang nang khrol dngos
NK132(no)004:2216: su yod nges yin kyang de dag las 'di yin
NK132(no)004:2217: dngos su mthong ba med do //
NK132(no)004:2218: mthong ba'i zer thag sogs de dag mngon sum lta ba na /
NK132(no)004:2219: sems 'dzin gyi rten du byas te mnyam gzhag gi
NK132(no)004:2220: lta ba skyong rgyu yin na ni skyon cher med
NK132(no)004:2221: do // de bas kyang yul rkyen cir snang gi steng du skyong ba ches gnad zab la /
NK132(no)004:2222: zer de mthong ba dang ngan skyugs kyi phung po
NK132(no)004:2223: mthong ba gnyis mnyam gzhag gi lta ba skyong tshul
NK132(no)004:2225: ma shes na 'ching ba'i rgyur mtshungs so //
NK132(no)004:2226: des na lhun grub mngon sum gyi snang ba la
NK132(no)004:2227: zab gnad ci mchis zhes 'dri na rnam dag gtan
NK132(no)004:2228: tshig ci smra / yang thig le thig phran snang
NK132(no)004:2229: ba 'di dag longs sku'i zhing khams yin pas zhing
NK132(no)004:2230: khams mthong ba'o zhes khyod rang gi gzhung na bshad
NK132(no)004:2231: tshig ci smra / 'dug par / 'di zhing khams mtshan nyid pa yin nam ma yin /
NK132(no)004:2232: ma yin na zhing khams bshad pa don med du 'gyur /
NK132(no)004:2233: yin par ni rgyu mtshan gnyis kyis mi 'thad de /
NK132(no)004:2234: longs sku'i zhing khams lta ba la dbang ba'i gang
NK132(no)004:2235: zag des drug pa'i rtog pa yod pa zhig dgos
NK132(no)004:2236: par gsungs na / khyed kyi zhing khams de mthong
NK132(no)004:2237: ba la ni sa dang po'i bden pa tsam yang
NK132(no)004:2238: par gsungs na / mi dgos te / gang zag
NK132(no)004:2239: so skye zhig la bstan pas de ma thag tu
NK132(no)004:2240: des mthong ba'i phyir zhing khams mthong ba'i gang zag
NK132(no)004:2241: par gsungs na / mi dgos te / ma dag
NK132(no)004:2242: / longs sku'i zhing khams mtshan nyid pa yin na
NK132(no)004:2243: rgyud tshod mthor song ba bzhin zhing khams rgya cher
NK132(no)004:2244: par gsungs na / mi dgos te / ma dag
NK132(no)004:2245: / mthong ba'i mthar / rab bkram chen po gcig
NK132(no)004:2246: dang grangs med sogs mthong rgyur /
NK132(no)004:2247: khyod rang tshang rgyud mtho shos su byed pa'i chos
NK132(no)004:2248: nyid zad sar zhing khams kyi snang ba ba thag
NK132(no)004:2249: bsdus pa ltar bsdus mthar mi mthong bar bshad pas
NK132(no)004:2250: / des na lam gyi mthong snang yin gyi zhing
NK132(no)004:2251: khams ma yin pas zhing khams rang gi ngo bo
NK132(no)004:2252: ma dag ces lung rigs kyis dngos su dgag pa
NK132(no)004:2254: yang nged kyi chos nyid mngon sum dang /
NK132(no)004:2255: gzhan nas bshad pa'i du sogs kyi rtags mtshungs te skyon med do snyam na /
NK132(no)004:2256: du sogs mnyam gzhag gi brtan pa'i nyams snang la mig gdangs btsum med /
NK132(no)004:2258: rkyen 'dzom min la ma ltos la /
NK132(no)004:2259: rig pa lu gu rgyud mig btsum na mi gsal /
NK132(no)004:2261: yul rkyen sna tshogs med na mi gsal zhes bshad pas gang nas kyang mi mtshungs shing /
NK132(no)004:2262: mtshungs kyang du sogs kyi rtags me nas du ba
NK132(no)004:2263: 'dren pa lta bu'i lam rtags kyi rnam pa tsam
NK132(no)004:2264: las / de la ting nge 'dzin mchog tu yang mi 'dzin /
NK132(no)004:2265: nyams kyi shun pa yin pas dor nas grol ba thob par bzhed pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2266: chos nyid mngon sum dag pa'i zhing yin pas mthong
NK132(no)004:2267: bas grol bar bshad pas ting nge 'dzin mchog tu
NK132(no)004:2268: 'dzin pa gnyis skyel so mi mtshungs /
NK132(no)004:2269: de na 'di dag ni bon chos rnams na 'od la lta ba'i gdams pa mang po zhig dang /
NK132(no)004:2270: rang lus 'od la phar zhugs na lhag med g.yung drung gi sku thob /
NK132(no)004:2271: 'od rang la tshur zhugs na lhag bcas g.yung drung
NK132(no)004:2272: gi sku thob par bzhed pa'i lugs su snang bas
NK132(no)004:2273: de dang khyad par ma mchis pas de'i khyad sel
NK132(no)004:2275: ces pa 'di dag la lan tha ram zhig gdab na /
NK132(no)004:2276: de la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i snying po stong pa nyid dang snying rje'i bdag nyid can te /
NK132(no)004:2278: gang zhig stong nyid snying rje gnyis su med par smra ba po ste /
NK132(no)004:2279: 'dir snying rje dmigs pa med cing rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba dang /
NK132(no)004:2280: stong pa nyid rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang
NK132(no)004:2281: ldan pa dus gsum yongs su shes pa'i slad du
NK132(no)004:2283: zhes pa ni sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha' nges pa'o //
NK132(no)004:2284: zhes gsungs pa'i stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa de yang /
NK132(no)004:2285: khang stong mis stong pa lta bu'i nyi tshe ba'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK132(no)004:2286: rgyas 'debs kyi stong nyid sogs rnam par dpyad pa thams cad las 'das pa /
NK132(no)004:2287: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi yang dag pa'i ye
NK132(no)004:2288: shes chen po de ni 'od gsal rnam pa thams
NK132(no)004:2289: cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i stong pa nyid kyi
NK132(no)004:2291: 'jam dpal gyis lta 'dod mdor bstan pa las /
NK132(no)004:2292: phung po rnam dpyad stong pa nyid //
NK132(no)004:2293: chu shing ji bzhin snying po med //
NK132(no)004:2294: rnam pa thams cad mchog ldan pa'i //
NK132(no)004:2295: stong nyid de ltar 'gyur ma yin //
NK132(no)004:2296: skyes pa med pa 'gag med pa //
NK132(no)004:2297: shes bya gang zhig 'dir mthong bas //
NK132(no)004:2298: stong pa'i dngos po stong pa nyid //
NK132(no)004:2299: phung po rnam par dpyad pa min //
NK132(no)004:2301: de lta bu'i 'od gsal de ci lta bu zhe na /
NK132(no)004:2303: bcom ldan 'das 'od gsal zhes bgyi ba ji ltar lags /
NK132(no)004:2305: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK132(no)004:2306: 'od gsal ni nam mkha'i dbyings su gnas pa'i thig le ste /
NK132(no)004:2307: des ni phyag rgya chen po brnyes par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK132(no)004:2310: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la ltos pa'i //
NK132(no)004:2311: phyag rgya chen po rtag par ni //
NK132(no)004:2313: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon dag dang mtshungs //
NK132(no)004:2316: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs 'chang ba //
NK132(no)004:2317: sgyu ma 'ja' tshon lta bu ru //
NK132(no)004:2318: rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud sbyong ba //
NK132(no)004:2319: yang dag gsal ba zhes bshad do //
NK132(no)004:2320: zhes gsungs pa'i 'od gsal de ni mtshan ma can ltar mthong ste /
NK132(no)004:2322: gang rnams kyi blo rten dang bral //
NK132(no)004:2323: yod dang med las rnam par 'das //
NK132(no)004:2324: zab mo dmigs med de rnams kyi //
NK132(no)004:2325: mtshan ma'i don ni rnam par bsgom //
NK132(no)004:2328: de kho na nyid kyi 'bras bu'i snga ltas su gyur pa'i phyir mtshan ma'o //
NK132(no)004:2330: 'o na de rnams dngos po ci zhig yin snyam na /
NK132(no)004:2331: sems kyi snang ba tsam ste /
NK132(no)004:2332: rang gi yid las skyes pa me long gi ni gzugs brnyan lta bu nyid //
NK132(no)004:2334: sems snang ba tsam yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2335: de las gzhan pa'i dngos po'i chos ni ci yang ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:2336: sems kyang rtog pa dang bral zhing ma 'khrul pa'i mngon sum nyid yin la /
NK132(no)004:2337: de'i snang ba tsam yin pas bag chags kyis bskyed
NK132(no)004:2338: pa'i rnam par rtog pa'i snang ba yang ma yin
NK132(no)004:2339: la / mig skyon can gyi zla ba gnyis su
NK132(no)004:2340: snang ba sogs dbang po bslad pa'i shes snang ma
NK132(no)004:2341: la / yin / yid shes bslad pa'i snang ba min /
NK132(no)004:2342: dbang po lnga'i rnam par shes pa'i snang ba yang ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2343: don gyi bzhag pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:2344: ma bslad pa'i yid kyi shes pa'i rnam pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:2345: slob dpon +aar+ya de bas yid kyi dbang po snang ba gsum la bzhed pas so //
NK132(no)004:2346: slob dpon 'gro bzang snying pos kyang de kho na nyid kyi 'grel par /
NK132(no)004:2348: dngos po ngo bo nyid yin nam /
NK132(no)004:2350: yi ge med ces bya ba smos te /
NK132(no)004:2351: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid kun gzhi'i rnam
NK132(no)004:2352: par shes pa'i rang bzhin nam mkha' khyab par snang
NK132(no)004:2353: ngo // de lta bu'i mgon po bsgom pa las ye shes skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:2355: 'di ni don gyi kun gzhi'i snang ba zhes pa de yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2356: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi ya gyal kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa zhes pa de ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:2357: 'di dag 'khrul pa'i snang bar gsungs pa med /
NK132(no)004:2358: mngon sum gyi snang ba kho na yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2359: rtags tsam zhig kyang ma yin /
NK132(no)004:2360: zung du 'jug pa zhes rab tu basngagasa pa de'i
NK132(no)004:2361: ngo bo nyid du gyur nas rgyal ba'i sku chen
NK132(no)004:2364: mtho ris sa 'og sa steng rnams //
NK132(no)004:2365: skad cig las ni sku gcig 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2367: sngags kyi theg pa las gsang bar gsungs pa'i don gyi gtso bo yang 'di yin pas /
NK132(no)004:2368: dad pa dang shes rab med pa'i gang zag la gtam bya bar daka'o //
NK132(no)004:2369: da ni mngon sum zhes pa'i don brjod par bya ste /
NK132(no)004:2370: tshad ma dang bral ba'i lam gyis ni gol zhing bslu bar 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)004:2371: 'dir tshad mas gtan la dbab pa la /
NK132(no)004:2372: tshad ma de yang mngon rjes gnyis su nges par slob dpon chos kyi grags pas bshad pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:2373: gsang ba'i theg pa 'dir yang tshad ma gnyis kho na ste /
NK132(no)004:2375: lha yi dmigs pa mngon sum dang ni rjes su dpags pa rnam pa gnyis su gyur pa ste //
NK132(no)004:2376: mngon sum dang ni de nyid sbyor bas mkha' la
NK132(no)004:2377: skar ma bzhin du du ma longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK132(no)004:2378: sku // mngon sum med na rjes su dpags pa
NK132(no)004:2379: shi ba'i lus bzhin de nyid min pa yis ni
NK132(no)004:2380: sku // brtags pa gang // de ni ri mo
NK132(no)004:2381: la sogs blta bya yongs su ma smin blo can
NK132(no)004:2382: rnal 'byor rnams kyi bsgom pa'i don //
NK132(no)004:2384: mngon sum de la yang tha mal pa'i dbang po'i
NK132(no)004:2385: mngon sum nas nyan rang gi bar gyi rnal 'byor
NK132(no)004:2386: mngon sum gyis ni shes pa min pas /
NK132(no)004:2387: mngon sum khyad par can nang gi de kho na
NK132(no)004:2388: nyid bsgom pa' rnal 'byor mngon sum gyis gtan la
NK132(no)004:2390: de yang chos rnams la 'khrul pa'i shes pa sna tshogs kyis bslad pa'i snang ba ma yin pa /
NK132(no)004:2391: sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du rigs mi
NK132(no)004:2392: 'gyur bar gnas pa de la de kho na nyid
NK132(no)004:2393: ces bya ste / 'jam dpal zhal lung las /
NK132(no)004:2394: chos rnams gzugs la sogs pa nas //
NK132(no)004:2395: kun mkhyen bar gyi rang bzhin ni //
NK132(no)004:2396: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar rnam dag pa //
NK132(no)004:2397: zab gsal gnyis med ye shes te //
NK132(no)004:2398: de ni dngos med bsgom dngos med //
NK132(no)004:2399: dngos po thams cad dang bral ba //
NK132(no)004:2400: khams dang skye mched kyis ma zin //
NK132(no)004:2401: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal ba //
NK132(no)004:2402: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK132(no)004:2403: med pa'i chos rnams mtshan nyid spangs //
NK132(no)004:2404: chos dang chos nyid yang med de //
NK132(no)004:2405: dngos po med pa mkha' dang mtshungs //
NK132(no)004:2406: tshig dang yi ge kun las grol //
NK132(no)004:2407: de ni dus dang phyogs rnams dang //
NK132(no)004:2408: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bor song //
NK132(no)004:2409: lus ma yin te ngag dang ni //
NK132(no)004:2410: yid kyang ma yin 'dod khams dang //
NK132(no)004:2411: gzugs dang gzugs med khams ma yin //
NK132(no)004:2412: 'byung ba bzhi yang ma yin te //
NK132(no)004:2413: de bas de nyid gang na yang //
NK132(no)004:2414: mi gnas pas na mnyam pa nyid //
NK132(no)004:2416: chos rnams kun gyi chos nyid mchog /
NK132(no)004:2417: thabs kyis sgrub par bya ba'i dngos //
NK132(no)004:2418: brtags pa kun las rab dben pa //
NK132(no)004:2419: phun sum tshogs rgyu dpags dka' ba //
NK132(no)004:2420: phyag rgya chen po rab snang ba'i //
NK132(no)004:2421: zer gyis rang gzhan smin byed pa //
NK132(no)004:2422: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin mchog /
NK132(no)004:2423: rdo rje 'dzin pa chen pos kyang //
NK132(no)004:2424: brjod du med pa'i sku chen po //
NK132(no)004:2425: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa ni nang gi
NK132(no)004:2426: de kho na nyid kyi mthong ba'i mngon sum zhes
NK132(no)004:2427: bya zhing / rdo rje snying 'grel las /
NK132(no)004:2435: nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK132(no)004:2437: de la mngon sum gyi ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK132(no)004:2438: de kho na nyid stong nyid snying rje'i rnal 'byor
NK132(no)004:2439: bsgoms pas sha la sogs pa'i mig lngas rnam pa
NK132(no)004:2440: thams cad pa'i gzugs nam mkha' la skar ma bzhin
NK132(no)004:2441: du gsal bar mthong ba'i shes pa rtog pa dang
NK132(no)004:2442: bral zhing ma 'khrul ba de la bya ste /
NK132(no)004:2444: 'dir nam mkha' la dngos po bsgom bya ni rmi
NK132(no)004:2445: lam lta bus te rdul phra rab kyi chos nyid
NK132(no)004:2446: las 'das pa'o // de yongs shes pa ni dngos po med pa bsgom par bya ste /
NK132(no)004:2447: rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba'i sems kyi snang brnyan mthong ba'o //
NK132(no)004:2448: rtog pa dang bral zhing ma 'khrul pa na mngon sum zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:2450: de lta bu thabs gang gis mthong na /
NK132(no)004:2451: bde mchog ri ga'i a ra li'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:2452: dgon pa dben pa'i gnas su ni //
NK132(no)004:2453: gnyis gnyis thams cad rnam par spangs //
NK132(no)004:2454: mig dag steng du bzlog nas ni //
NK132(no)004:2455: smin ma'i dbus su sems byas na //
NK132(no)004:2456: mi bzad mun pa'i gzugs su ni //
NK132(no)004:2457: sgrub pas dang por mthong bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2459: tshul ji ltar mthong ba yang de nyid las /
NK132(no)004:2460: dang po mun pa mthong bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2461: gnyis pa dkar dang du ba mtshungs //
NK132(no)004:2462: gsum pa me khyer rnam par blta //
NK132(no)004:2463: bzhi pa ya ba'i me tog bzhin //
NK132(no)004:2464: lnga pa sprin med ye shes ni //
NK132(no)004:2465: rang gzhan yang dag rig pa spangs //
NK132(no)004:2466: rtag tu goms pa'i rnal 'byor gyi //
NK132(no)004:2467: rtse gcig sems kyi ri gir 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2470: dang po sprin dang 'dra bar snang //
NK132(no)004:2471: gnyis pa du ba 'dra ba yin //
NK132(no)004:2472: gsum pa me khyer 'dra ba ste //
NK132(no)004:2473: bzhi pa mar me cher 'bar ba //
NK132(no)004:2474: lnga pa rtag tu snang ba ni //
NK132(no)004:2475: sprin med nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:2477: bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtshor yang gsungs shing /
NK132(no)004:2479: dang po smig sgyu 'dra ba ste /
NK132(no)004:2480: gnyis pa du ba 'dra ba yin //
NK132(no)004:2481: gsum pa me khyer rnam pa ste //
NK132(no)004:2482: bzhi pa mar me 'bar ba nyid //
NK132(no)004:2483: lnga pa sprin med snang ba 'dra //
NK132(no)004:2486: dang po smig rgyu lta bu la 'od zer lnga'i tshogs dang ldan par mthong ngo //
NK132(no)004:2487: gnyis pa ni snang ba ste zla ba'i 'od zer lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:2488: gsum pa ni snang ba mched pa ste nyi ma'i 'od zer lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:2489: bzhi pa ni snang ba thob pa ste mun pa lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:2490: de nas mun pa dang bral ba'i skad cig la
NK132(no)004:2491: 'od gsal ba ste shin tu gsal ba rtag tu
NK132(no)004:2493: don dam pa'i bden pa'i rang gi mtshan nyid ye shes kyi mig gis mthong ngo //
NK132(no)004:2495: dang po smig rgyu lta bu la 'od zer lnga'i tshogs dang ldan pa mthong bar gsungs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2496: rdzogs chen nas thog mar dbyings rnam dag gi sgron
NK132(no)004:2497: ma dar mthing kha'i mdog lta bu'am rma bya'i mdongs
NK132(no)004:2498: lta bu 'char bar gsungs pa dang khyad par med
NK132(no)004:2499: / de las gzhan gsungs pa rnams ni /
NK132(no)004:2500: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang /
NK132(no)004:2503: de la sogs pa 'char sgo sna tshogs pa du ma dang /
NK132(no)004:2504: thig le gsum sbrel nas nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK132(no)004:2505: sogs pa'i bar du snang ba ni chos nyid mngon
NK132(no)004:2506: sum gyi snang ba zhes pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:2507: de yang sngar gsungs pa rnams kyi steng du nyin
NK132(no)004:2508: mo'i rtags lnga bsnan pas bcu po rdzogs phan chad
NK132(no)004:2509: la bya ste / rtags bcu ni dbang mdor bstan las /
NK132(no)004:2510: du ba smig sgyu mkha' snang dang //
NK132(no)004:2511: sgron me 'bar ba zla nyi ma //
NK132(no)004:2512: mun can cha dang thig le che //
NK132(no)004:2513: sna tshogs gzugs can 'od gsal ba //
NK132(no)004:2515: sna tshogs gzugs can 'od gsal ba ni nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:2516: 'od lnga ma 'dres pa snam bu lta bu dang /
NK132(no)004:2520: re lde lta bur snang ba tshun chad yin no //
NK132(no)004:2521: de nas 'od kyis snang srid thams cad la khyab par ma bltas kyang gsal la /
NK132(no)004:2522: thig le'i nang du sangs rgyas kyi sku zhi ba
NK132(no)004:2523: dang khro bo gang yang nges pa med pa sna
NK132(no)004:2524: tshogs 'char ba phyin chad ni rig pa tshad phebs
NK132(no)004:2527: nam mkha' kun nas zhen pa'i sems dang mig ni
NK132(no)004:2528: mi 'dzum rdo rje'i lam du rab tu zhugs pa
NK132(no)004:2529: yi // stong pa las ni du ba smig rgyu
NK132(no)004:2530: rab gsal dri ma med pa'i mkha' snang nyid dang
NK132(no)004:2531: yi // mar me dang // 'bar ba dang ni
NK132(no)004:2532: zla ba nyi ma rdo rje dang ni mchog gi
NK132(no)004:2533: cha dang thig le mthong bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2534: de yi dbus su sangs rgyas gzugs ni yul dang
NK132(no)004:2535: rnam par bral ba du ma longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK132(no)004:2537: nam mkha' chu 'dzin bral ba'i dbus su rnal 'byor pa yi bgrad pa'i mig gis blta bya ste //
NK132(no)004:2538: re kh+aa nag po dri med 'od zer 'phro ba
NK132(no)004:2539: dus kyi rtsa la mthong bar gyur gyi bar du'o
NK132(no)004:2542: rtags bcu rdzogs par gyur pa dang //
NK132(no)004:2543: thig le chen po'i snang ba 'byung //
NK132(no)004:2544: sna tshogs thig le chen po la //
NK132(no)004:2545: re kh+aa nag po'i ri mo 'byung //
NK132(no)004:2546: de nang 'gro drug la sogs dang //
NK132(no)004:2547: shin tu phra ba'i sprul sku dang //
NK132(no)004:2548: longs sku du ma mthong 'gyur ba //
NK132(no)004:2549: sna tshogs gzugs can 'od gsal yin //
NK132(no)004:2550: de la sems ni thim pa ni //
NK132(no)004:2551: ting 'dzin yan lag mthar phyin pa'o //
NK132(no)004:2552: zhes bshad pa'i don ni rdzogs chen nas chos nyid
NK132(no)004:2553: zad pa'i snang ba gsungs pa dang khyad par med
NK132(no)004:2554: do // de dag ni chos nyid kyi mngon sum yang yin te /
NK132(no)004:2555: ye gdod ma'i chos nyid ye shes kyi rang 'od
NK132(no)004:2556: du ye nas ngang gis gsal ba yin par sngar
NK132(no)004:2557: bshad pa'i lung rnams kyis bsgrubs zin te /
NK132(no)004:2558: dbang po'i yul du snang ba'i chos nyid de gad mo'i gnas su'ang mi rigs te /
NK132(no)004:2560: rang yod mtshan ma mtha' dag bral ba yi //
NK132(no)004:2561: mig phyed gyen du lta ba dang bcas pas //
NK132(no)004:2562: gang tshe rlung ni dbu mar bus gyur pa //
NK132(no)004:2563: de tshe rdo rje'i me dang du ba 'byung //
NK132(no)004:2565: nyams kyi mngon sum yang yin te /
NK132(no)004:2566: rnal 'byor pas lam bsgoms pa'i nyams kyi snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:2567: bir+wa pas lam 'bras rdo rje'i tshig rkang las /
NK132(no)004:2568: rnal 'byor pa la ting nge 'dzin la nyams kyi snang ba zhes bshad pas so //
NK132(no)004:2569: dbang po'i mngon sum yin par bshad pa ni /
NK132(no)004:2570: rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma zhes 'char ba'i sgo mig yin pa la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2571: don du dbang po'i mngon sum ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2572: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gdod ma nas ye shes lnga'i rang 'od du rang gsal ba de nyid /
NK132(no)004:2573: mig gis mthong bya mthong byed kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)004:2574: mun khung du rang gi lag pa brkyang ba mi mthong ba'i tshe na'ang mthong ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)004:2575: bar dor mig dang bral ba'i dus na'ang mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK132(no)004:2577: rang gi mig gis mi mthong zhing //
NK132(no)004:2578: gzhan gyi mig gis kyang min pa //
NK132(no)004:2579: skye ba med pa mthong ba ni //
NK132(no)004:2580: gzhon nu ma yi bu ji bzhin //
NK132(no)004:2583: gang gi phyir bkab pa dang ma bkab pa'i mig gi rtog pa de'i phyir gzugs ma yin zhing /
NK132(no)004:2584: gzugs las gzhan pa yang ma yin /
NK132(no)004:2585: mig gis rtog pa yang ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:2586: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyis shes so //
NK132(no)004:2587: yang rdo rje snying 'grel las gsungs pa ltar gyi mngon sum bzhi po'ang yin te /
NK132(no)004:2588: de'i tshul yang rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK132(no)004:2589: 'jug pa'i yul ni mi phyed pa'i thig le yin
NK132(no)004:2590: pas / de dbang po'i mngon sum gyis mthong ba tsam zhig byas /
NK132(no)004:2592: phyag rgya sgyu ma'i rjes su mthun pa yid dang
NK132(no)004:2593: nam mkha' la ni me long dag la gzugs brnyan
NK132(no)004:2594: bzhin // 'jig rten gsum po snang bar byed cing
NK132(no)004:2595: dri med glog dang mtshungs pa'i 'od zer du ma
NK132(no)004:2596: bzhin // 'phro bar byed // ces gsungs pas /
NK132(no)004:2597: yid kyi mngon sum gyis mi shigs pa'i thig le
NK132(no)004:2598: de'i nang du yid kyi gzugs brnyan mthong bas nges
NK132(no)004:2599: pa rnyed / de nas rig pa tshad la phebs
NK132(no)004:2600: pas rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum gyis rang rig pa'i
NK132(no)004:2602: chos nyid zad pa'i skabs su gzung 'dzin dang bral
NK132(no)004:2603: bas rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyi 'jug pa'i yul
NK132(no)004:2604: mi shigs pa'i thig le gnyis su snang ba med
NK132(no)004:2605: pa'i tshul gyis nyams su myong ba yin no //
NK132(no)004:2606: de la tshos ma bkab pa'i mthong snang dang /
NK132(no)004:2608: nyi zer la brten pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2609: 'bag chas la sogs pa la brten nas ston pa ni rig pa'i ye shes dngos ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2610: 'di pa'i lugs la dpe don rtags gsum gyi ngo sprod ces 'byung bas na /
NK132(no)004:2611: dpe la bltas nas don ngo sprod pas na mtshon byed kyi dpe zhes bya ba yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2612: 'di dag mngon sum ye shes su khas mi len no //
NK132(no)004:2613: de lta bu'i ye shes rang gi snying nang na stong gsal 'od kyi rang bzhin du yod la /
NK132(no)004:2614: de yang mu stegs rtag lta ba rnams 'dod pa ltar bdag tu lta ba ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2616: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK132(no)004:2617: gzhan du gang na'ang sangs rgyas med //
NK132(no)004:2618: mi shes mun pas bsgribs pa rnams //
NK132(no)004:2619: lus las gzhan du sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK132(no)004:2622: snying gi nang son pad+ma ni //
NK132(no)004:2623: 'dab ma brgyad po snying por bcas //
NK132(no)004:2624: de yi nang du son pa'i rtsa //
NK132(no)004:2625: mar me rang gi ngo bo can //
NK132(no)004:2626: chu shing gi ni me tog ltar //
NK132(no)004:2628: de yi nang na dpa' bo ni //
NK132(no)004:2629: yungs kar gyi ni sbom phra tsam //
NK132(no)004:2631: rtsa yi mdzes spyi las byung ba'i //
NK132(no)004:2632: de ni rdul bral rab tu grags //
NK132(no)004:2633: dag pa shel gyi 'od dang mnyam //
NK132(no)004:2634: byang chub sems ni 'od gsal ba //
NK132(no)004:2635: ye shes lnga yi dngos de nyid //
NK132(no)004:2636: yungs kar gyi ni sbom phra tsam //
NK132(no)004:2639: mkhas pa rnams ni bstan bcos 'chad pa yis //
NK132(no)004:2640: lus la ye shes yod par ma rtogs so //
NK132(no)004:2643: rtag tu snying la gnas pa yi //
NK132(no)004:2644: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK132(no)004:2645: de bsgom byed pa'i skye bo la //
NK132(no)004:2646: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2648: gzhan yang rgyud dang bstan bcos rnams nas rgya cher bshad pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:2649: de'i ngo bo ni rdul dang skad cig ma'i chos
NK132(no)004:2650: las 'das pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can mkha'
NK132(no)004:2651: khyab mkha' yi rdo rje can te /
NK132(no)004:2652: spros pa dang mtshan ma'i spyod yul kun las 'das
NK132(no)004:2653: pa'i zung 'jug mnyam pa nyid yin pas rtag mi
NK132(no)004:2654: rtag sogs spros pa'i mtha' kun dang bral yang dus
NK132(no)004:2655: gsum 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba'i cha nas rang byung
NK132(no)004:2656: ye shes dang rtag pa chen po'i tha snyad mdzad
NK132(no)004:2657: pa yin no // de'i phyir zab mo'i mdo rgyud
NK132(no)004:2658: kyi don legs par mkhyen pa'i mkhas pa dag gis
NK132(no)004:2659: pa yin no // kyang / gnas lugs dbu ma 'khor 'das kun khyab yin //
NK132(no)004:2660: sems can rnams la gzhi yi chos su snang //
NK132(no)004:2661: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la lam du snang //
NK132(no)004:2662: gdul bya dag pa rnams la 'bras bur snang //
NK132(no)004:2663: de gsum snang tshul yin gyi gnas tshul min //
NK132(no)004:2664: gnas lugs rjen pa sangs rgyas kho nas gzigs //
NK132(no)004:2665: lam zhugs rnams kyis phyogs rer mthong ba dang //
NK132(no)004:2666: gnas tshul snang tshul 'dres mar snang ba yod //
NK132(no)004:2667: gnas lugs de ni zung 'jug kho na ste //
NK132(no)004:2668: gzhi yi gnas tshul 'bras bu'i sdod lugs yin //
NK132(no)004:2669: gnas lugs de ni dbu ma yin pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:2670: de la mthun par 'jug na dbu ma'i lam //
NK132(no)004:2671: kun rdzob don dam zung 'jug ces pa dang //
NK132(no)004:2672: snang stong zung 'jug gsal stong zung 'jug dang //
NK132(no)004:2673: thabs shes stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug dang //
NK132(no)004:2674: bde stong sgyu lus 'od gsal zung 'jug dang //
NK132(no)004:2675: sku dang ye shes zung 'jug la sogs pa //
NK132(no)004:2676: de dag kun la'ang lam gyi zung 'jug dang //
NK132(no)004:2677: gnas lugs chos nyid zung 'jug so sor dbye //
NK132(no)004:2678: lam rnams bden med sgyu ma lta bu yin //
NK132(no)004:2679: don dam dbyings kyi zung 'jug ces bya ba //
NK132(no)004:2680: chos sku nges pa don gyi sangs rgyas te //
NK132(no)004:2681: bde gshegs snying po de yin chos dbyings de //
NK132(no)004:2682: stong nyid spros bral rang bzhin sher phyin te //
NK132(no)004:2683: kun 'gro yin phyir kun khyab cha med de //
NK132(no)004:2684: dus gsum kun la khyab phyir dus med de //
NK132(no)004:2685: mtshan dpe la sogs sangs rgyas yon tan kun //
NK132(no)004:2686: rang byung gdod nas grub pa'i rtag pa ste //
NK132(no)004:2687: mdo las chos dbyings sangs rgyas rtag par gsungs //
NK132(no)004:2688: de nyid sngags las rnam kun mchog ldan no //
NK132(no)004:2689: bde gshegs snying po rtag par 'jog pa'i gnad //
NK132(no)004:2690: gnas lugs 'gyur med bde ba yin par thug /
NK132(no)004:2691: rgyal ba'i yon tan rang byung lhun grub pa'ang //
NK132(no)004:2692: chos nyid rnam pa kun ldan nyid las so //
NK132(no)004:2693: 'gyur med de nyid rnam pa thams cad par //
NK132(no)004:2694: gdod nas rtag tu shar ba ngo mtshar che //
NK132(no)004:2695: rnam kun tshul du shar yang lhan skyes kyi //
NK132(no)004:2696: bde chen gcig tu ro mnyam rmad du byung //
NK132(no)004:2697: rnam pa kun ldan yin yang cha bcas min //
NK132(no)004:2698: rang bzhin 'gyur med gnas kyang dus kun shar //
NK132(no)004:2699: srid gsum rnam par shar yang spros dang bral //
NK132(no)004:2700: bde chen rang gis rig kyang myong tshor bral //
NK132(no)004:2701: rgyal ba'i yon tan shes bya kun khyab cing //
NK132(no)004:2702: ye shes gcig dang shes bya thams cad mnyam //
NK132(no)004:2703: shes bya ma lus ma 'dres gsal bar mkhyen //
NK132(no)004:2704: mkhyen pa de la spros pa ci yang med //
NK132(no)004:2705: chos nyid rang bzhin chos sku yin pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:2706: chos sku'i rang bzhin yon tan ldan par grub //
NK132(no)004:2707: chos sku shes bya kun mkhyen ye shes phyir //
NK132(no)004:2708: rnam pa thams cad par yang grub pa yin //
NK132(no)004:2709: chos dbyings ngo bo dbye ba med par gsungs //
NK132(no)004:2710: shes bya re re la yang chos dbyings re //
NK132(no)004:2711: yod pa lta bur gsungs pa'i skabs kyang yod //
NK132(no)004:2712: de gnyis bsdoms pas rnam kun mchog ldan grub //
NK132(no)004:2713: gzugs sogs mi dmigs gzugs sogs la mi gnas //
NK132(no)004:2714: yod med mi dmigs yod med la mi gnas //
NK132(no)004:2715: de ltar gsungs pas kun rdzob las grol zhing //
NK132(no)004:2716: mi rtag spros las grol bas rtag par grub //
NK132(no)004:2717: chos dbyings rang bzhin nam yang 'gyur med dang //
NK132(no)004:2718: sangs rgyas rtag pa 'gro la yod gyur la //
NK132(no)004:2719: rtag na rtag dngos spros par 'gyur snyam pa'i //
NK132(no)004:2720: dogs pa sel phyir spros bral stong par gsungs //
NK132(no)004:2721: stong pa ces pas nam yang bden med dang //
NK132(no)004:2722: ci yang ma yin tsam zhig bstan pa min //
NK132(no)004:2723: kun rdzob phyogs nas med dang ma yin stongs //
NK132(no)004:2724: don dam phyogs nas rtog pa'i yul gyis stongs //
NK132(no)004:2725: don dam rang gi ngo bos stong pa ltar //
NK132(no)004:2726: gsungs pa'i dgongs pa don dam la dmigs nas //
NK132(no)004:2727: blo yis bzung ltar ma grub pa la dgongs //
NK132(no)004:2728: ye med ye min tsam gyi stong pa min //
NK132(no)004:2729: snying po de nyid rnam pa kun ldan zhing //
NK132(no)004:2730: de nyid mi 'gyur rtag yin bde ba'ang yin //
NK132(no)004:2731: sngags kyi tshul las de ltar gsal bar bshad //
NK132(no)004:2732: mdo las de la dgongs nas phyogs mtshon gsungs //
NK132(no)004:2733: cha med kun khyab nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK132(no)004:2734: bsgribs dang mi bsgrib cha gnyis mi 'thad zer //
NK132(no)004:2735: de ni 'dod thog yin te chos dbyings kyi //
NK132(no)004:2736: rang ngos nas ni bsgribs dang ma bsgrib med //
NK132(no)004:2737: de la dmigs pa'i yul can shes pa la //
NK132(no)004:2738: gnas skabs du ma yod phyir dbye ba bstan //
NK132(no)004:2739: rtog pa po la dbye ba yod pas na //
NK132(no)004:2740: rtogs bya'i yul la dbyer yod lta bur bshad //
NK132(no)004:2741: dngos su rang blo sgrib pas bsgribs gyur ba'i //
NK132(no)004:2742: blo ngor chos nyid sgrib pas bsgribs ltar snang //
NK132(no)004:2743: grong khyer sprin dang smugs pas sgrib pa na //
NK132(no)004:2744: 'gro rnams nyi ma sprin gyis bsgribs par 'dzin //
NK132(no)004:2745: sa la sprin de rlung gis gtor ba na //
NK132(no)004:2746: nyi ma'i sgrib byed sangs zhes rtog pa ltar //
NK132(no)004:2747: gdul bya'i blo dang bstun nas de bzhin nyid //
NK132(no)004:2748: dri bral gnas skabs thob par gyur zhes gsungs //
NK132(no)004:2749: sangs rgyas dam pa'i don du yod pa ste //
NK132(no)004:2750: sangs rgyas nyid ni don dam yin pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:2751: gzhan du sangs rgyas don dam min gyur te //
NK132(no)004:2752: khyad gzhi med na khyad chos mi srid de //
NK132(no)004:2753: thob bya sangs rgyas gnas lugs yin nam min //
NK132(no)004:2754: min na 'khrul snang thob pas dgos pa ci //
NK132(no)004:2755: gnas lugs yin pas sangs rgyas thob gyur na //
NK132(no)004:2756: sems can dus kyi chos nyid de yin pas //
NK132(no)004:2757: de de'i bar du yod cing mi 'gyur rtag /
NK132(no)004:2758: sngon dang phyi mtha' dus gsum don la med //
NK132(no)004:2759: gnas skabs gsum sogs blo yi mthong tshul yin //
NK132(no)004:2760: dus kyi gos ma myong ba'i chos nyid gnas //
NK132(no)004:2761: 'khrul dang 'khor ba rnam rtog dbang gis byung //
NK132(no)004:2762: gnyen po rnam par mi rtog lam sgom byas //
NK132(no)004:2763: rtog pa'i bzhon pa las kyi rlung yin pas //
NK132(no)004:2764: rlung rnams dbyings su dag byed lam bsgom na //
NK132(no)004:2765: 'bras bu don gnyis phun tshogs mngon gsal 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:2766: zhes gnas snang legs par phyes te gsal bar gsungs
NK132(no)004:2767: pa bzhin don gyi e wam zung 'jug lhan skyes
NK132(no)004:2768: kyi 'gyur med bde ba chen po nyid la rtsa
NK132(no)004:2770: de la snying nang na 'char gzhi 'od kyi rnam pa'i sems dang /
NK132(no)004:2771: shar ba lu gu rgyud kyi sems dang /
NK132(no)004:2772: 'dzin pa mig gi dbang shes kyi lu gu rgyud kyi sems gsum yod pa'i skyon brjod pa ni /
NK132(no)004:2773: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi don spyi tsam yang blo
NK132(no)004:2774: yul du ma shar ba'i blun tshig zang ma ste
NK132(no)004:2775: / de ltar na nyi ma dang nyi ma'i 'od
NK132(no)004:2776: zer gyi sgo nas nyi ma gnyis yod par 'gyur
NK132(no)004:2777: / ba dang / chos drug pa las /
NK132(no)004:2778: snang ba sgyu mar bsgom pa'i sgyu lus kyi sems gcig /
NK132(no)004:2779: thams cad rmi lam du bsgom pa'i rmi lam gyi
NK132(no)004:2780: sems gcig sogs sems drug yod par thal ba sogs
NK132(no)004:2781: skyon mang ngo // de lta ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2783: sems nyid lhan cig skyes pa chos kyi sku //
NK132(no)004:2784: snang ba lhan cig skyes pa chos sku'i 'od //
NK132(no)004:2785: de phyir snang sems gnyis med lhan cig skyes //
NK132(no)004:2786: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)004:2787: zhes gsungs pa ma yin nam /
NK132(no)004:2788: 'od snang de dag gi steng du mnyam bzhag gi
NK132(no)004:2789: lta ba mi skyong bar byis pas lha khang lta
NK132(no)004:2790: ba lta bu ni ma yin te sbyor rdzogs kyi
NK132(no)004:2791: khrid yig khungs ma rnams su zhib tu gzigs ma
NK132(no)004:2792: grub pas nongs / zer de mthong ba dang ngan
NK132(no)004:2793: skyugs kyi phung po mthong ba mnyam par 'dzin pa'ang
NK132(no)004:2795: 'di nges pa'i don gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yin pas mthong tsam gyis grol ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:2796: sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa las /
NK132(no)004:2797: 'dir mthong ba la don yod pa /
NK132(no)004:2798: mkhas pa rnams kyi so so rang gi rig par bya ba /
NK132(no)004:2800: sor sdud kyi rtags bcu mthong bas bden tshig grub pa sogs gsungs shing /
NK132(no)004:2801: ngan skyug gi phung po ni lta ba can la don du ma grub pa yin kyang /
NK132(no)004:2802: mthong ba la de lta'i yon tan med pas ngan skyug nyid du zad do //
NK132(no)004:2803: chos nyid mngon sum gyi zab gnad ci yin zhes 'dri na /
NK132(no)004:2804: 'di ni grong khyer rgyun gcod kyi lta ba zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)004:2805: mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun gcod pas na phyis 'khor bar mi 'khyams te /
NK132(no)004:2806: mngon sum gnad 'di sus mthong ba //
NK132(no)004:2807: khams gsum ldog pa ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:2809: rgya gar gyi grub chen rnams kyang lam 'di'i sgo
NK132(no)004:2810: nas bgrod pa sha stag yin te rang rang gi
NK132(no)004:2811: mgur rnams na gsal mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:2812: 'dir yi ger 'jigs pas bri bar ma nus la /
NK132(no)004:2815: rmad byung nam mkha' dkyil shar b+hu su ku //
NK132(no)004:2816: dpe med me tog rgyas so b+hu su ku //
NK132(no)004:2817: rin chen rin thang med pa'i me tog longs //
NK132(no)004:2818: me tog 'di ni stong nyid dgon par skyes //
NK132(no)004:2819: me tog 'di ni kha dog sna tshogs can //
NK132(no)004:2822: snang ba thob pa'i rnam 'byor pas //
NK132(no)004:2823: gzhan du rtags ni shes bya ste //
NK132(no)004:2824: grub pa'i 'khrul pa med pa rnams //
NK132(no)004:2825: lam nag gi ni du ba bzhin //
NK132(no)004:2826: mig dag rengs par byed pa dang //
NK132(no)004:2827: mgo bo dud pa nyid dang ni //
NK132(no)004:2828: sems dang sems byung mi g.yo dang //
NK132(no)004:2829: stong nyid mthong ba' stong pa nyid //
NK132(no)004:2832: gang tshe zla ba nya ba shar gyur pa //
NK132(no)004:2833: de tshe sems kyi rgyal po kun tu nyal //
NK132(no)004:2834: dga' dang snying rje'i d+aa ma ru yi sgra //
NK132(no)004:2835: 'phags pa lha yi dmigs pa med par gsal //
NK132(no)004:2838: zab mo'i chos mthong nas ni lam ngan pa //
NK132(no)004:2839: mun pa'i lam la ci yang mthong ba med //
NK132(no)004:2840: gang tshe nam mkha'i rtse mor me tog rgyas //
NK132(no)004:2841: sh+aan+tisa smas pa de tshe 'khrul pa chad //
NK132(no)004:2843: lta zhing lta bas nam langs kyang //
NK132(no)004:2847: me tog lnga byung de ru thim //
NK132(no)004:2848: dga' ba'i sems nyid nam mkhar 'byin //
NK132(no)004:2850: slob dpon dpe med a tshos /
NK132(no)004:2851: dri ma med pa'i nam mkha' gang la sprul pa'i mig phye la //
NK132(no)004:2852: thugs rje chen po rgyas pa brlan pa bsam pa'i rten za las //
NK132(no)004:2853: yod dang med dang dngos po dngos med 'byed pa bral //
NK132(no)004:2854: stong pa nyid kyi rjes 'gro du sogs ma lus glo bur shar //
NK132(no)004:2855: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:2856: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni sa bcu'i byang chub
NK132(no)004:2857: sems dpa' kho na la snang ba yin na gnas
NK132(no)004:2858: skabs 'dir ji ltar mthong zhe na /
NK132(no)004:2860: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gzugs can rnams dang mkha' la rgyal ba'i sras sogs chos sku yi //
NK132(no)004:2862: gnas gtsang ma'i gnas na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)004:2863: sku la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes bya zhing
NK132(no)004:2865: longs spyod pa chen po ni 'dir chos sku'i ming du bshad par mngon no //
NK132(no)004:2866: rnam pa gcig tu na thig le'i dbus su mthong
NK132(no)004:2867: ba'i sku gang yin pa de dag la sprul sku
NK132(no)004:2868: zhes bya zhing / sna tshogs pa'i sgra skad mang
NK132(no)004:2869: po snang ba la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes
NK132(no)004:2870: zhes bya zhing / bya'o // zhes sbyor drug pa'i bla ma gong ma rnams kyis bshad cing /
NK132(no)004:2872: rig pa tshad phebs snang ba yis //
NK132(no)004:2873: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ngos zin //
NK132(no)004:2874: zhes pas rig pa tshad phebs kyi rnal 'byor pa
NK132(no)004:2875: de gar gnas pa'i yul de longs sku'i zhing khams
NK132(no)004:2876: dang / 'khor rnams longs sku'i 'khor du bzhag pa sogs yod kyang /
NK132(no)004:2877: rig pa tshad la ma phebs gong gi snang ba rnams la longs sku'i zhing du ma bshad cing /
