NK132(no)004:2878: rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i rnal 'byor pa de
NK132(no)004:2879: rang gi blo ngo na rang gnas pa'i yul longs
NK132(no)004:2880: sku'i zhing khams dang 'khor rnams kyang de ltar yin
NK132(no)004:2881: mod / gzhan gyi blo ngo na de ltar med do //
NK132(no)004:2882: des na rang snang chos nyid kyi rol pa yin pa'i phyir bzhag pa ste /
NK132(no)004:2885: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung /
NK132(no)004:2887: sems can thams cad ni rtag tu de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can no //
NK132(no)004:2889: de ltar yin pa'i sgrub byed /
NK132(no)004:2891: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK132(no)004:2892: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK132(no)004:2893: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK132(no)004:2894: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK132(no)004:2895: zhes mtshan nyid gsum gyi sgo nas gsal bar bstan cing /
NK132(no)004:2896: de nyid chu khams gser dang nam mkha' sogs kyi
NK132(no)004:2897: dpes rang bzhin gdod nas dag par gsungs pa bzhin
NK132(no)004:2899: lus las ma rtogs gang zhig khyab byed thar pa ster ba'i sangs rgyas 'ga' yang yod ma yin //
NK132(no)004:2900: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas yin te sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:2901: chen po gzhan 'dir 'jig rten khams na yod ma
NK132(no)004:2904: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK132(no)004:2905: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK132(no)004:2908: 'di ni ye shes chen po nyid //
NK132(no)004:2909: thams cad lus la rnam par gnas //
NK132(no)004:2910: gnyis dang gnyis su med pa'i tshul //
NK132(no)004:2911: dngos dang dngos med bdag nyid gtso //
NK132(no)004:2912: brtan dang g.yo ba khyab gnas pa //
NK132(no)004:2913: sgyu ma gzugs can nyid du gnas //
NK132(no)004:2916: rang gi lus la sangs rgyas bzhugs //
NK132(no)004:2917: gzhan du gang la'ang sangs rgyas med //
NK132(no)004:2918: mi shes mun pas sgrib pa rnams //
NK132(no)004:2919: lus las gzhan du sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK132(no)004:2920: rtogs pa thams cad rnam spangs pa'i //
NK132(no)004:2921: ye shes chen po lus la gnas //
NK132(no)004:2923: rdo rje me long gi rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:2924: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK132(no)004:2925: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK132(no)004:2926: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK132(no)004:2927: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK132(no)004:2928: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK132(no)004:2929: zhes sogs gsar rnying gi rgyud sde kun nas lus
NK132(no)004:2930: la ye shes chen po gnas par gsungs pa la
NK132(no)004:2932: de ltar yod pa'i gnad kyis sgo gsum gyi gnad
NK132(no)004:2933: gzir ba sogs thabs zab mos nang gsal sku gsum
NK132(no)004:2934: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang gdangs phyir
NK132(no)004:2935: gsal du snang ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:2937: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid de mtshan sum
NK132(no)004:2938: cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa yang sems can thams
NK132(no)004:2941: de ltar 'char gzhi chos nyid dang de las 'char
NK132(no)004:2942: ba'i 'od gdangs gang la 'char ba'i lam pa'i skye
NK132(no)004:2943: mched la sogs pa'ang gdod nas rang bzhin gyis dag
NK132(no)004:2944: pa yin gyis / gzod gsar du dag par byed dgos pa ni ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2946: rang rig bdag nyid dag pa nyid //
NK132(no)004:2947: dag pa gzhan gyis rnam grol min //
NK132(no)004:2950: chos phung po khams skye mched la sogs pa rnams
NK132(no)004:2951: dngos po la grub par gnas pa zhig lus ngag
NK132(no)004:2952: yid gsum gyi 'bad rtsol gyis dag par byas pa
NK132(no)004:2953: ma yin / 'o na lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK132(no)004:2954: 'bad rtsol la brten nas nyams su blangs pas chos
NK132(no)004:2955: nyid kyi don mthong ba de 'bad rtsol gyis dag
NK132(no)004:2956: par byas pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK132(no)004:2957: 'bad rtsol gyis chos nyid kyi don mthong ba'i tshe
NK132(no)004:2958: na yang gzhi la sngar mi gnas pa zhig mthong
NK132(no)004:2959: ba ma yin / gzhi la gnas pa'i don gsal bar byas pa tsam yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:2960: des na gzhi la sngar ma dag pa zhig dag par byas pa ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:2961: dper na bum pa'i nang na gnas pa'i mar me
NK132(no)004:2962: de bum pa bcag pa la brten nas gsal bar
NK132(no)004:2964: sngar mi gnas pa zhig gsal bar byas pa ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:2966: des na sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi chos
NK132(no)004:2967: nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po la ni zag
NK132(no)004:2968: med kyi yon tan thams cad rang chas su yod
NK132(no)004:2969: pa'i gnad kyis / 'dir thabs la mkhas pas da
NK132(no)004:2970: lta so skye'i sa nas mngon du byed nus pa
NK132(no)004:2971: ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi khyad
NK132(no)004:2973: 'di la zhib tu dbye na sngar sbyor drug gi
NK132(no)004:2974: rtags tshad sogs las 'phags chos thun min bsam gyis
NK132(no)004:2975: mi khyab pa yod pa ni kun mkhyen chos kyi
NK132(no)004:2976: rgyal po dri med 'od zer sogs snga 'gyur mkhas
NK132(no)004:2977: grub rim byon gyi gsung dang /
NK132(no)004:2978: khyad par kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i
NK132(no)004:2979: zhal snga nas stsal ba'i gnyug sems kyi skor sogs
NK132(no)004:2980: su gsal ba bzhin shes par bya dgos so //
NK132(no)004:2981: des na sems can thams cad rigs gcig dang theg
NK132(no)004:2982: pa gcig par klu sgrub yab sras sogs kyis seng+ge'i
NK132(no)004:2983: sgra bsgrags pa bzhin yin pas mthong ba'i gang zag
NK132(no)004:2984: la ma dag pa'i skyon ma mchis shing /
NK132(no)004:2985: mthong ba'i zhing khams kyang chos nyid kyi rang gdangs
NK132(no)004:2986: rtsol med du rang la rang snang ba las gzhan
NK132(no)004:2988: 'khrul pa'i slad ma zhugs par zag med 'dus ma
NK132(no)004:2989: byas chos nyid kyi rang gdangs dngos yin pas zhing
NK132(no)004:2990: khams rang gi ngo bor ma dag pa'i skyon med
NK132(no)004:2991: / mthar chos nyid zad pa'i dus su snang ba thams cad dbyings su sdud dgos pa'i gnad kyang /
NK132(no)004:2992: mdo sogs las shing las byung ba'i mes shing rang nyid bsreg ste zhi ba'i dpes bstan pa dang /
NK132(no)004:2994: spang phyir bslu ba'i chos can phyir //
NK132(no)004:2998: 'dus byas thams cad bslu ba'i chos can du gsungs pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:2999: slob lam gyi rtog pa zag med gsar thob kyi
NK132(no)004:3000: cha rnams mthar 'gags nas don dam pa'i chos sku
NK132(no)004:3003: sems 'gags pa ste sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK132(no)004:3005: snang bzhi'i 'char cha 'di thams cad lam pa'i lam
NK132(no)004:3006: snang yin pa'i phyir ma dag rlung sems kyi cha'ang
NK132(no)004:3007: ci rigs 'dres pas 'phel 'grib ltar snang ba'i mthar
NK132(no)004:3008: kun rdzob chos can gyi snang ba thams cad chos
NK132(no)004:3009: nyid don dam 'dus ma byas kyi dbyings su 'gags
NK132(no)004:3010: pa'ang thim nas de phyin rten nas ltos pa tsam
NK132(no)004:3011: gyi tha snyad las kyang 'das pa'i sangs rgyas bde
NK132(no)004:3012: chen rdo rje'i sku mngon du mdzad pa yin te
NK132(no)004:3014: gang las srid pa gsum po du gyur mi yi bdag po slar yang gang du thim pa'o //
NK132(no)004:3016: de'i tshe na chos dbyings rang snang gi sku dang zhing khams sogs ni 'gags pa ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:3017: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa'i zhing sku'i bkod pa
NK132(no)004:3018: mi zad rgyan 'khor lnga'i bkod pas 'khor ba ma
NK132(no)004:3019: stong gi bar du gdul bya'i don mdzad pa yin
NK132(no)004:3020: te / de lta bu'i yon tan gyi chos rnams
NK132(no)004:3021: kyang rigs khams snying po'i dri ma bral stobs kyis
NK132(no)004:3022: mngon du gyur pa las rgyu rkyen gyi rtsol bas
NK132(no)004:3023: gsar du sgrub pa ni min no //
NK132(no)004:3024: des na lam pa'i du sogs kyi rtags snang 'di
NK132(no)004:3025: la slob dpon dus zhabs pas kyang longs sku'i zhing
NK132(no)004:3026: khams mthong ba yin par bshad de /
NK132(no)004:3027: dkar dang ser dang dmar dang ljang //
NK132(no)004:3030: de snang gzugs brnyan yul med pas //
NK132(no)004:3031: longs spyod rdzogs sku du ma mthong //
NK132(no)004:3033: rig pa lu gu rgyud mig btsum na mi gsal /
NK132(no)004:3034: nyi ma med na mi gsal /
NK132(no)004:3035: yul rkyen med na mi gsal snyam pa ni ma nges pa chen po ste /
NK132(no)004:3036: rang nyid rdo rje rtse mo'i lam la zhal 'dris
NK132(no)004:3037: che ba'i rnam dpyod bstan pa tsam du zad do
NK132(no)004:3038: // du sogs kyi rtags la ting nge 'dzin mchog tu yang mi 'dzin /
NK132(no)004:3039: nyams kyi shun pa yin pas dor nas grol ba thob par bzhed ces pa'ang ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:3040: rgya bod gnyis su byon pa'i dus 'khor gyi mkhas
NK132(no)004:3041: grub thams cad kyis rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong
NK132(no)004:3042: nyid ces gces spras su mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:3043: ye shes de la gzhom zhig med pas na /
NK132(no)004:3044: ji ltar bum pa zhig gyur kyang //
NK132(no)004:3045: nam mkha' la ni 'jig pa med //
NK132(no)004:3046: de bzhin sems ni zhig gyur kyang //
NK132(no)004:3047: ye shes la ni 'jig pa med //
NK132(no)004:3050: ji ltar zangs kyi dri ma ni //
NK132(no)004:3051: bcud kyi sbyor bas nyams par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:3052: de yi ye shes nyid mnyam med //
NK132(no)004:3053: dri med nyid ni yang dag gnas //
NK132(no)004:3054: zhes gser 'gyur gyi rtsi la dpe mdzad de yang
NK132(no)004:3055: dag pa'i ye shes nyams pa med par gsungs pa
NK132(no)004:3056: yin no // gzhan yang thos grol dang btags grol
NK132(no)004:3057: sogs rgyal ba'i thabs mkhas kyi sgo zab mo rnams
NK132(no)004:3058: ni phyogs mtshungs par gsar rnying gnyis ka'i phyogs su
NK132(no)004:3059: yin no // yod de / sangs rgyas kyi mtshan dang gzungs sngags khyad par can sogs thos grol /
NK132(no)004:3060: so sor 'brang ma'i 'khor lo dang jo bo'i grong khyer sgrol 'khor sogs btags grol dang /
NK132(no)004:3062: de zos pa tsam gyis dus gsum gyi ye shes can du 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:3065: de ni zos pa tsam gyis ni //
NK132(no)004:3066: skad cig mkha' spyod nyid la spyod //
NK132(no)004:3067: ces gsungs pas mtshon rgyud sde du ma nas skye
NK132(no)004:3068: bdun gyi phan yon dang sha ril sgrub tshul gsungs
NK132(no)004:3070: ush+ni shas basngagasa pa'i spos bdug dang sngags bye sogs
NK132(no)004:3071: tshod grol dang reg grol sogs kyis mtshon de dag
NK132(no)004:3072: gsar ma la grags pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3074: 'jam dpal 'byung ba bzhi ni nam mkha'i gter las 'byung gi /
NK132(no)004:3075: de bzhin du chos thams cad rgyal ba'i thugs gter
NK132(no)004:3076: las 'byung bas gter gyi don la spyod shes par
NK132(no)004:3078: klu'i rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:3079: dkon mchog gsum gyi gdung mi chad pa'i gter chen po mi zad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3080: chos rtog pa chen po tshad med pa'i gter chen po mi zad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3081: sems can mgu bar byed pa'i gter chen po mi zad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3082: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i gter chen po mi zad pa ste /
NK132(no)004:3083: bzhi po de dag ni gter chen po mi zad pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:3084: zhes pas gter gyi ngo bo'am rang bzhin tsam bstan nas /
NK132(no)004:3085: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas mngon du bzhugs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK132(no)004:3086: nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi
NK132(no)004:3087: stong du ting nge 'dzin 'di 'dzam bu gling du
NK132(no)004:3090: de'i 'og tu sa yi khung du song bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:3091: yang de lo lnga brgya pa tha ma phyi ma'i
NK132(no)004:3092: dus phyi ma'i tshe lnga brgya pa tha mar gyur
NK132(no)004:3093: pa / dam pa'i chos 'jig par 'gyur ba /
NK132(no)004:3095: dam pa'i chos spang bar 'gyur ba /
NK132(no)004:3098: tshul khrims dang ldan pa phyogs dmas pa'i dus la babs pa /
NK132(no)004:3099: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i phyogs 'phel ba'i dus la babs pa /
NK132(no)004:3100: dam pa'i chos kyi phyogs dmas pa'i dus la babs pa /
NK132(no)004:3101: dam pa ma yin pa'i phyogs kyi chos 'phel ba'i dus la babs pa /
NK132(no)004:3102: zad pa'i dus la babs pa na /
NK132(no)004:3103: sems can gang mdo sde 'di lta bu thos par 'gyur ba'i phyir dge ba'i rtsa ba 'bar ba /
NK132(no)004:3104: sngon gyi rgyal ba la bya ba byas pa /
NK132(no)004:3105: dge ba'i rtsa ba skyed pa /
NK132(no)004:3106: dge ba'i rtsa ba smin pa /
NK132(no)004:3107: sa bon btab pa'i sems can rnams ni nyung zad cig 'byung ste /
NK132(no)004:3108: sems can 'di lta bu dag gi don du 'di lta ste /
NK132(no)004:3109: sangs rgyas kyi mthus ting nge 'dzin 'di sa yi
NK132(no)004:3110: khung nas thon te 'dzam bu gling du spyod par
NK132(no)004:3111: 'gyur ro // rgyas par byed par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:3113: nga ni phyi dus mya ngan 'das pa'i tshe //
NK132(no)004:3114: sku gdung thams cad rgyas par byed gyur nas //
NK132(no)004:3115: sangs rgyas byang chub 'di dag legs bzung ste //
NK132(no)004:3116: yi ger bris te sgrom du bcug nas kyang //
NK132(no)004:3117: mchod rten sa dang brag dang ri dag dang //
NK132(no)004:3118: lha dang de bzhin klu yi lag dag tu //
NK132(no)004:3119: mdo sde bzhag par byas nas de dag rnams //
NK132(no)004:3120: lha yi brtul zhugs 'dra bar bya phyir 'gro //
NK132(no)004:3121: de dag phyi ma'i dus tshe so so'i rigs //
NK132(no)004:3122: thams cad bor nas slad du bab gyur nas //
NK132(no)004:3123: sangs rgyas byang chub 'di dag legs bzung ste //
NK132(no)004:3124: bsam pa ji bzhin du ni byed par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:3125: de dag chos 'di 'dod pas yul yul du //
NK132(no)004:3126: gdong zhing mdo sde bzang po 'di rnyed 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:3127: rnyed nas yid ni mchog tu dga' 'gyur pas //
NK132(no)004:3128: rten pa med par skye bo mang la gtong //
NK132(no)004:3130: dge slong brgyad dang de bzhin byang phyogs su //
NK132(no)004:3131: yongs su len cing chos 'dzin dga' ba dang //
NK132(no)004:3132: chos 'dod 'jig rten phan zhing brtse ldan dag /
NK132(no)004:3133: len pa'i phyir ni mang po 'byung bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:3135: bsod nams thams cad sdud pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:3136: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK132(no)004:3138: khyod kyis chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams la ni /
NK132(no)004:3139: nam yang de bzhin gshegs pa mya ngan las 'da' bar mi 'gyur la /
NK132(no)004:3140: dam pa'i chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur ba de ltar rigs par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:3142: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK132(no)004:3143: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK132(no)004:3144: po bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa gus pa dang
NK132(no)004:3145: bcas pa rnams ni 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan na
NK132(no)004:3146: 'dug kyang / sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams zhal
NK132(no)004:3147: ston par mdzad cing chos kyang thos par mdzad do
NK132(no)004:3148: 'dug kyang / // dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK132(no)004:3149: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi chos kyi gter /
NK132(no)004:3152: shing gi nang du bcug pa dag yod de gzungs
NK132(no)004:3153: dang chos kyi sgo mtha' yas pa glegs bam du
NK132(no)004:3155: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK132(no)004:3156: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK132(no)004:3157: po rnams la ni sngon sangs rgyas mthong ba'i lha
NK132(no)004:3158: rnams spobs pa sgrub par byed do //
NK132(no)004:3160: de bzhin du sangs rgyas dang lha rnams kyi tshe dang /
NK132(no)004:3162: de dag gis byin gyis brlabs kyis bdag ji 'dod
NK132(no)004:3163: pa'i bar du 'tsho zhing rga ba dang nad kyang
NK132(no)004:3164: sel la / dran pa dang rtogs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3165: spobs pa sgrub par mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:3166: lta ba ngan pa sel la /
NK132(no)004:3167: yang dag pa'i lta ba sgrub par mdzad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3168: gzhan gyi gnod pa thams cad mi 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:3171: byang chub sems dpa' bsam pa dag pa ni rang
NK132(no)004:3172: gi yid kyi 'dod pa nyid las gdams ngag dang
NK132(no)004:3173: rjes su bstan pa thams cad 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)004:3175: don la nges pa'i gding thob na //
NK132(no)004:3176: sems la chos gter 'bum phrag brdol //
NK132(no)004:3179: nga yis bstan pa'i chos kyi gzhung //
NK132(no)004:3180: thugs nas thugs kyi gter du sba //
NK132(no)004:3181: yang na sa yi snying por bya //
NK132(no)004:3182: ci phyir mu stegs can mgo rgod //
NK132(no)004:3183: nges don dkrugs par 'gyur ta re //
NK132(no)004:3184: de phyir chu rlung rgyun mi gcod //
NK132(no)004:3186: dpa' mchog dang po'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:3187: rgyud dang rgyud kyi rgyal po gang //
NK132(no)004:3188: phyag na rdo rje khyod nyid kyis //
NK132(no)004:3189: gter nas gter du phyung ste stsal //
NK132(no)004:3192: dge slong grags pas bum pa bzang po zhig las mdo sogs chos gang 'dod bton pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3193: mdzangs blun nas khyim bdag zhig gi ka ba nas
NK132(no)004:3194: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'i dpe phyung bar gsungs
NK132(no)004:3195: pa dang / gzhan yang theg chen gyi mdo mang
NK132(no)004:3196: po tho gar gyi yul nas dge slong ni ra
NK132(no)004:3197: ban rak+ti tas phyung ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3198: klu sgrub kyis 'bum rgyas pa klu yul nas spyan drangs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3199: mnga' ba dag mee tri pas mchod rten gyi ser
NK132(no)004:3200: kha zhig nas rgyud bla dang chos nyid rnam 'byed
NK132(no)004:3201: phyung ba dang / nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul nas /
NK132(no)004:3202: sa ra has sangs rgyas thod pa /
NK132(no)004:3204: la li tas 'jigs byed rtog pa bdun pa /
NK132(no)004:3205: ku ku ris pas ma h+aa ma ya'i skor sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:3206: dur khrod dpal gyi rgyu skar rol pa nas pha
NK132(no)004:3207: dam pas zhi byed drangs pa sogs so so'i lo
NK132(no)004:3209: bod du mnga' bdag mar pas rdzogs rim rlung sems dbyer med /
NK132(no)004:3210: rdo rje gdan pa dang ba ri lo ts+aa bas seng gdong ma'i sgrub skor /
NK132(no)004:3211: gnyan lo ts+aa bas ku ru kul+le'i skor /
NK132(no)004:3212: jo bo rjes lha sa'i dkar chag /
NK132(no)004:3213: bla ma zhang dang jo gdan dkon mchog grags kyis phan gnod las tshogs skor 'ga' zhig dang /
NK132(no)004:3214: gtsang pa rgya ras kyis ro snyoms skor drug /
NK132(no)004:3215: dung mtsho ras pas sems khrid yid bzhin nor bu /
NK132(no)004:3216: gnyal pa nyi ma shes rab kyis rnam sras dang /
NK132(no)004:3217: lha btsun byang chub 'od kyis pu tra'i sgrub skor /
NK132(no)004:3218: ma gcig gi gcod skor kun spangs brtson 'grus seng+gesa bton pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3219: sras brgyud kyi mgon khang du 'dul nag pa dpal
NK132(no)004:3220: ldan bzang pos sbas pa'i chos rgyal gyi las tshogs
NK132(no)004:3221: 'ga' zhig rgyud chen sangs rgyas rgya mtshos bton par
NK132(no)004:3222: grags pa dang / khyad par du rje bdag nyid
NK132(no)004:3223: chen pos kyang chos dung sogs rdzas gter ci rigs
NK132(no)004:3224: grags pa dang / dang / lhag par lho brag
NK132(no)004:3225: mkhan chen brgyud gsang bdag las rdzogs pa chen po
NK132(no)004:3226: zhus lan bdud rtsi' sman mchog gsan pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3227: sa chen gyis bir+wa pa las lam 'bras dang 'jam dpal lam zhen pa bzhi bral /
NK132(no)004:3228: sa pan gyis dbyig gnyen las mdzod kyi bshad bka' gsan pa sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:3229: rgyal mchog lnga pa chen po'i rgya can nyer lnga sogs dag snang nye brgyud dang /
NK132(no)004:3230: gter brgyud kyang 'phags bod gsar rnying kun la khyad med lta bur bzhugs te /
NK132(no)004:3231: de dag gi rnam bzhag phyogs mtshon ni gzhan dang
NK132(no)004:3232: gzhan du brjod zin pas 'dir yi ges 'jigs la
NK132(no)004:3233: / sngon gyi mkhas grub chen po sog bzlog pa sogs kyi lan zhib rgyas su bzhugs /
NK132(no)004:3234: phyis kyi rtog ge ba 'ga' zhig gis snga ma'i
NK132(no)004:3235: gtam rnying pa rjes brjod kyi lad mo byed pa
NK132(no)004:3236: dang / mkhan slob chos gsum gyis bstan la bya ba ma byas par /
NK132(no)004:3237: glang dar ma spyan ras gzigs yin pas bstan pa'i
NK132(no)004:3238: ga dar byas tshul sogs brjod pa ni snying pos
NK132(no)004:3239: dben zhing mtshang smra bas lan gyi ngal bas ci
NK132(no)004:3240: zhig bya / sngar gsang snying la logs pa'i skyon bzhi sogs smras mod /
NK132(no)004:3241: de dag ni bcom ldan 'das ral gris rgya dpe
NK132(no)004:3242: rnyed pa dang log rtog gi skyon bsal zin pas
NK132(no)004:3243: deng sang yongs grags su gyur pas smos ma dgos
NK132(no)004:3244: / zhib par ni rgyud gzhung rang rang 'chad pa'i skabs thob tu shes par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:3245: gsum pa rang lugs tshad mar grub cing che ba drug ldan gyi sgo nas bshad pa ni /
NK132(no)004:3246: kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal dgyes pas 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK132(no)004:3247: da ni rang lugs snga 'gyur gyi chos de rnam dag yin pa'i sgrub byed 'god pa la /
NK132(no)004:3250: rigs pa'i dan dpang gsum yod de /
NK132(no)004:3252: snga dus kyi pan chen lo ts+aa chos rgyal rnams gdan 'dzom dus su bsgyur ba 'di dag nii /
NK132(no)004:3253: gang zag khyad par can de dag dan dpang yod pas yid ches su rung ba nyid de /
NK132(no)004:3254: de dus chos min mi spel bar nges shing /
NK132(no)004:3255: rdzun chos dar bar byar med pa'i bka' btsan khungs btsun gyi rgyu mtshan yod pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:3256: dper na khyod kyis rgya gar nas byung ba tsam gyis chos rnam dag gi khungs su rung na /
NK132(no)004:3257: rgya gar nas byung tshad chos rnam dag yin pa'i rgyu mtshan gzhan med de /
NK132(no)004:3258: 'phags yul gyi pan grub tshad ma las brgyud pa nyid rgyu mtshan yin te /
NK132(no)004:3260: dus 'khor lta bu rgya gar du gsar du byung mod /
NK132(no)004:3262: dus zhabs pa sogs gang zag tshad ma las brgyud
NK132(no)004:3263: pa'i phyir rgya bod sus kyang the tshom mi za
NK132(no)004:3264: ba bzhin no // gal te gang zag tshad mas ma grub na /
NK132(no)004:3265: 'jigs byed la li tas rtsom pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3266: dus 'khor dus zhabs pas rtsom pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3267: 'bum rgyas pa klu sgrub kyis rtsom pa sogs su
NK132(no)004:3268: cis mi 'gyur te rgyu mtshan mtshungs pas de 'dra'i
NK132(no)004:3269: smra ngan de khyod la sus bgos pa yin /
NK132(no)004:3270: rgya gar bas rgyud mi rtsom la bod kyis rtsom pa'i nges pa yod na smros shig /
NK132(no)004:3271: khyod phyir rgol mkhan po la smra rgyu yod na
NK132(no)004:3272: smra ba'i dus yin te smra lce nang du bsdu
NK132(no)004:3274: smra rgyus dbul na smra bcad las 'os med do //
NK132(no)004:3275: gzhan yang sangs rgyas 'das nas lo bdun brgya na
NK132(no)004:3276: bdud sdig can gyis bka' la bslad gzhug tshul lung
NK132(no)004:3277: bstan pa dang / dge slong lha chen po hu
NK132(no)004:3278: lu hu lu sogs rung ba ma yin pa'i gzhi
NK132(no)004:3280: bram ze rgyal bshes kyis gsung rab kyi glegs bam bsdus nas mer bsreg rjes /
NK132(no)004:3281: 'dul ba gzhung bla ma'i dpe btsal kyang ma rnyed nas /
NK132(no)004:3282: kha che'i yul du dge slong zhig gis gzhung bla
NK132(no)004:3283: ma 'don to zhes thos nas dge slong rnams de'i
NK132(no)004:3287: cung zad cig ni mi dran no //
NK132(no)004:3289: ji ltar dran pa de kho na bzhin thon cig /
NK132(no)004:3290: des kyang de ltar kha ton byas te /
NK132(no)004:3291: phyis tshig dang don gyi sgo nas rnam par dpyad
NK132(no)004:3292: de sbyar bar bya'o snyam du bsam nas bris pa
NK132(no)004:3293: las / phyis 'phral gyi bya bas rnam par g.yengs nas /
NK132(no)004:3294: dus ring mo zhig gi bar du ji lta ba
NK132(no)004:3295: bzhin ma 'grub cing dge slong gzhan dag kyang yul
NK132(no)004:3297: de'i phyir bsdu ba'i gzhi nyams pas /
NK132(no)004:3298: gzhung bla ma 'di la 'don pa yang rnam pa du ma la /
NK132(no)004:3299: don yang rnam pa du ma ste /
NK132(no)004:3300: de'i phyir btsun pa yon tan 'od kyis 'dul ba'i
NK132(no)004:3301: bshad pa las yang dang yang du zhus pa las
NK132(no)004:3305: thig le mang nyung yod pa yig skyon sogs rgya gar na yang yod par bshad /
NK132(no)004:3306: rgya las byung tshad chos rnam dag yin par bsgrub par ga la nus te /
NK132(no)004:3307: mu stegs pa'i gzhung thams cad rgya gar nas byung yang sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang /
NK132(no)004:3308: de'i dgongs 'grel du mi 'dod pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:3309: des na rgya gar gyi yul phal nas byung ba tsam khungs su byed la /
NK132(no)004:3310: rgya gar gyi pan grub kun gyi nang na nyi zla ltar 'phags pa'i mkhan slob gnyis dang /
NK132(no)004:3313: dzi na mi tra sogs gang zag dam pa 'di rnams dang /
NK132(no)004:3314: sa bcu'i dbang phyug sprul pa'i sku bee ro tsa na dang /
NK132(no)004:3315: ska cog sogs kyis bsgyur ba nyid khungs su che dgos te /
NK132(no)004:3316: rgya gar rang na'ang de las lhag pa'i sgrub byed med do //
NK132(no)004:3317: gzhan yang rgya gar nas ma byung zhes pa'i mtshang rkub brtol zhing byung ba'i rgyu mtshan yod de /
NK132(no)004:3318: gsang snying rma ri na gyis brtsam par bsgrags kyang /
NK132(no)004:3319: phyis bsam yas nas rgya dpe kha che pan chen gyi phyag tu byung ba /
NK132(no)004:3320: rta ston gzi brjod la babs /
NK132(no)004:3321: de nas sha gad lo ts+aa la byung ba /
NK132(no)004:3322: bcom ldan 'das rig pa'i ral gris blangs te 'gyur bcos dang sngar ma 'gyur ba'i le'u gnyis bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:3323: gsang snying me tog rgyan gyi me tog zhes pa'i bstan bcos kyang mdzad de dril bsgrags /
NK132(no)004:3324: rgyud phyi ma thar pa lo ts+aa bas bsgyur ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3325: bal po b+hi ha ra nas glo bo lo ts+aa
NK132(no)004:3326: ba dpal ldan byang chub kyis rnyed pa'i rgya dpe
NK132(no)004:3327: las / 'bri gung lo ts+aa ba ma ni ka
NK132(no)004:3328: sh+r+ai dz+ny+aa nas zur mkhar dga' ldan gling du bsgyur
NK132(no)004:3329: las / ba dang / der ma zad rdo rje
NK132(no)004:3330: bzhad pas mdzad pa'i gsang 'dus kyi 'grel pa dang
NK132(no)004:3331: las / ba dang / / 'dus pa phyi ma'i
NK132(no)004:3332: 'grel pa slob dpon bi shwa mi tras mdzad pa
NK132(no)004:3333: las / ba dang / / dang / brgya byin
NK132(no)004:3334: sdong pos mdzad pa'i mnyam sbyor 'grel pa sogs su'ang
NK132(no)004:3335: gsang snying gi lung mang du drangs /
NK132(no)004:3336: de bzhin du pad+ma'i thugs dam gshin rje pra khog
NK132(no)004:3337: snang ba'i rgyud gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis brtsams
NK132(no)004:3338: par bsgrags kyang / rgyud de slob dpon shan+ti pas
NK132(no)004:3339: spyod rgyud du bkral zhing dpal 'dzin gyis bya rgyud
NK132(no)004:3340: du bzhed de rgya dpe dngos pos khungs brtol /
NK132(no)004:3341: gzhan yang 'gos kyis rgyal po sprin gyi shugs can
NK132(no)004:3342: las gshin rje 'char kha'i rgyud sgrub thabs mdos gzhung
NK132(no)004:3343: sogs zhus pa 'char kha 'gos lugs su grags pa
NK132(no)004:3344: dang / kha thun skor rang slob rngog kha ba
NK132(no)004:3345: can la brgyud pa deng sang gi bar du yod
NK132(no)004:3346: dang / pa dang / yang dag me gcig thod
NK132(no)004:3347: gcig skor pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai dang khro phu lo
NK132(no)004:3348: dang / pa dang / ts+aas bsgyur / sa skya
NK132(no)004:3349: pan+di tas phur pa rtsa dum gyi rgyud la 'gyur
NK132(no)004:3350: bcos mdzad pa sogs rnying chos phyis gsar du bsgyur
NK132(no)004:3351: ba dang 'gyur bcos mdzad pa'ang mang du mchis shing
NK132(no)004:3352: dang / pa dang / ts+aas bsgyur / / des
NK132(no)004:3353: mtshon nas rgya gar dang o rgyan sogs thams cad
NK132(no)004:3354: du rgyu nus shing bka' yi gnyer kha ba mkha'
NK132(no)004:3355: 'gro'i tshogs dbang du khol nus pa zhig yin na
NK132(no)004:3357: rnying rgyud thams cad la'ang rgya dpe dang mkha' 'gro'i
NK132(no)004:3358: gsang mdzod kyi dpe yod par gor ma chag ste
NK132(no)004:3360: / ci rigs pa bod du bsgyur ba 'dis dan
NK132(no)004:3362: des ma chog par re re bzhin du rgya dpe
NK132(no)004:3363: re gsar du ma mthong bar yid mi ches na
NK132(no)004:3364: / phyis kyi 'gyur ba'i chos thams cad la rgya
NK132(no)004:3365: dpe re re bzhin ston rgyu khyod tsho la yod
NK132(no)004:3366: / dam soms shig / mkhas grub o rgyan pas /
NK132(no)004:3367: bal po na rgya dpe mang du 'dug pa la /
NK132(no)004:3368: ngas bod kyi sngags pa rnams la /
NK132(no)004:3369: khyed rang tsho mang yul du 'dong /
NK132(no)004:3370: ngas rnying ma'i pan+di ta dang rgya dpe tshur dgug /
NK132(no)004:3371: lo ts+aa ba ngas byas te bsgyur byas pa la /
NK132(no)004:3372: bod kyi sngags pa rnams bu smad gso bas g.yengs te ma 'grub /
NK132(no)004:3373: da dung 'gyur mang du bya rgyu 'dug pa la gsungs shing /
NK132(no)004:3374: lo ts+aa ba gzu dga' rdor gyis dpal n+aa len+d+ra'i
NK132(no)004:3375: gtsug lag khang na lha khang la rgyud kyi po
NK132(no)004:3376: ti char babs pa'i ri mo mthong ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3377: lo ts+aa ba 'ga' zhig gis rgya gar gyi pan+di
NK132(no)004:3378: ta'i phyag dpe'i nang na rnying ma bka' brgyad kyi
NK132(no)004:3379: sgrub thabs nyung ngu re mthong yang /
NK132(no)004:3381: mi shes mi shes sngar gyi bla rgan tsho'i red
NK132(no)004:3382: zer nas gsang ba zab chos yin pa'i lo rgyus
NK132(no)004:3383: dang / der ma zad rnying ma'i tshe bdag gnubs kyis rtsom par 'gos lhas btsas kyis 'dod bzhin /
NK132(no)004:3384: kho rang la rnying ma'i mthu rtags byung nas rgya
NK132(no)004:3385: gar du de la phan pa'i zab chos tshol du
NK132(no)004:3386: phyin pa'i tshe / pan+di ta nag po pas rnying
NK132(no)004:3387: ma'i tshe bdag gnang ste lo ts+aa ba kho rang
NK132(no)004:3388: gis bsgyur ba da lta bstan 'gyur khrod na yod
NK132(no)004:3389: pa des dan dpang byas pa yin /
NK132(no)004:3390: 'gos 'di lo ts+aa ba mkhas pa zhig yin tshod kyang /
NK132(no)004:3391: rnying ma la zhe sdang ba sngon zur ba'i chos
NK132(no)004:3392: gral nas phud pa'i zhe nad kyis kha nas skur
NK132(no)004:3393: 'debs mang po smra ba zhig yin tshod gda' ste
NK132(no)004:3394: / mi gshis zhig gi de 'dra yin par /
NK132(no)004:3395: ga ya d+ha ra la'ang skur pa gdab tshul dang /
NK132(no)004:3396: 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba'i gam du byon dus su'ang
NK132(no)004:3397: chos 'ga' ma gnang bas thugs mug ste rgya gar
NK132(no)004:3399: slob gnyer phul phyin zhig ma byung na 'brog ldom
NK132(no)004:3400: de la ngo tsha ba yod ces rang gi bla
NK132(no)004:3401: ma la'ang skur 'debs mdzad pa zhig yin par grags
NK132(no)004:3403: kyi min par kha g.yar ba gzhan zhig gis byas
NK132(no)004:3404: zer ba bden shas che ste /
NK132(no)004:3405: 'byams yig 'di la blun po ci yang mi shes
NK132(no)004:3406: pa zhig gi tshig dngos su gsal 'dug pas so
NK132(no)004:3407: // gal te 'gos lo yin na'ang ma brtag gya
NK132(no)004:3408: tshom gyi tshig phrag dog kho nas smras pa rang
NK132(no)004:3409: mtshang ston byed du song ba dngos gsal 'di 'dra'o
NK132(no)004:3410: // // de bzhin dpal 'dzin gyi rtsod yig chos
NK132(no)004:3411: dang chos ma yin pa rnam par dbye ba'i rab
NK132(no)004:3412: tu byed pa zhes pa 'di ni /
NK132(no)004:3413: rnying bstan la snying nas zhe sdang drag pos smras pa dngos su gsal /
NK132(no)004:3414: de yang rang gi slob dpon la zhe sdang bas yin tshul bshad /
NK132(no)004:3415: gang ltar yang chos la zhe sdang bas mthar lus
NK132(no)004:3416: des sa gas nas song ba'i shul deng sang yang
NK132(no)004:3417: yod tshul lnga pa rin po che sogs kyis gsungs
NK132(no)004:3418: shing / kha cig gis sa spyod du gshegs zer yang /
NK132(no)004:3420: rnying ma'i mthu ci yin kyang rung /
NK132(no)004:3421: rdo rje'i dmyal ba a la la zhes khrag gis
NK132(no)004:3422: bris pa'i rdo char babs te 'og tu song ba
NK132(no)004:3423: ni rdzun gtam ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:3424: lo rgyus 'di ltar grags pa la /
NK132(no)004:3425: phyis stag lung ngag dbang grags pas rtsad gcod mdzad pas /
NK132(no)004:3426: khung thub mang pos bden par gleng gi 'dug gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3427: rnying mar kha zer ba'i thog ma yin 'dug /
NK132(no)004:3430: ye shes 'od sogs kyis sngags 'chal ches pa bkag pa ni bden gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3431: rang gzhan sus kyang de ltar shes dgos pa zhig 'dug gi /
NK132(no)004:3432: dpyad na gang zag gi rgyud dang chos 'dzol ba'i
NK132(no)004:3433: sngags log sun 'byin yin gyi rnying chos la skur
NK132(no)004:3435: mi shes pa dag gis de dag rnying ma bkag pa yin par sems kyang /
NK132(no)004:3436: de'i tshig don la dpyod dang chos la skur 'debs gtan nas med /
NK132(no)004:3437: zhi ba 'od kyis rnying rgyud rnams rtsom chos yin
NK132(no)004:3438: zhes 'gog pa'i dam bca' tsam las rigs pa ci
NK132(no)004:3439: yang med / dpal 'dzin gyis sun 'byin mi rigs
NK132(no)004:3440: pa sna tshogs smras pa ni rigs pas sun dbyung
NK132(no)004:3442: mkhas grub chen po sog bzlog pas kyang lan legs par gdab pas chog par gda'/
NK132(no)004:3443: gzhan rgya ra klong chen pa sogs snga phyi'i mkhas pas mdzad pa'i rtsod lan du ma yod do //
NK132(no)004:3444: gnyis pa lung gi dan dpang ni /
NK132(no)004:3445: gsar rgyud thams cad kyi rim gnyis rnal 'byor bshad pa dang rnying rgyud phyogs mthun la /
NK132(no)004:3446: de dag gi gnad zab mo rgyud 'di dag tu gsal bas /
NK132(no)004:3447: rgyud 'di dag yin na yin mnyam /
NK132(no)004:3448: min na yin mnyam ste lung gi dpang po'o //
NK132(no)004:3449: khyad par rdzogs chen chos skad thun min rnams /
NK132(no)004:3450: mthar thug gi gsang chen 'bras bu'i lung rnams kyis bsgrub par nus shing /
NK132(no)004:3451: chos skad zur ba re zung gsar rgyud yongs grags
NK132(no)004:3452: re zung dang mi 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas kyi bka'
NK132(no)004:3453: min snyam pa blo rgya shin tu chung ba byis
NK132(no)004:3454: pa'i gtam ste / sangs rgyas kyi gsung gis chos bstan pa'i sgo sna tshogs tshad med kyi /
NK132(no)004:3455: gcig yang yang bskyar zlos kho na ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:3456: dus 'khor la'ang gza' skar shar du 'gro ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3457: rgya nag bod kyi byang du yod par gsungs pa
NK132(no)004:3458: sogs la yang dag min par rig ral sogs kyis
NK132(no)004:3459: bshad pa dang / re mda' bas kyang /
NK132(no)004:3460: rtsa ba'i rgyud la e wam med pa dang //
NK132(no)004:3461: bsdus pa'i rgyud la 'gal ba du ma mthong //
NK132(no)004:3462: gang las byung ba'i khungs kyang mi snang na //
NK132(no)004:3463: 'phyon ma'i bu bzhin 'di la su yid rton //
NK132(no)004:3464: sogs rnam grangs du mas dgag pa brjod mod /
NK132(no)004:3465: deng sang dus 'khor rgyud kun gyi rtse mor yongs la grags shing grub la /
NK132(no)004:3467: rdzogs chen gyi thod rgal sogs khyad chos rnams lam
NK132(no)004:3468: gyi mthar thug tu 'grub nus pa bzhin yin te
NK132(no)004:3469: / sangs rgyas kyi bka' rgyud rnams //
NK132(no)004:3470: rgyud rnams rgyud gzhan gyis shes bya //
NK132(no)004:3472: gsang 'dus sogs su rgyud ltar mtha' drug gis dpyad dgos pa rdo rje'i tshig tu sbas pa /
NK132(no)004:3473: zab mo'i rgyud 'ga' zhig tu ma sbas par bshad pas /
NK132(no)004:3474: dus 'khor la sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog
NK132(no)004:3475: kha 'byed pa zhes gsungs pa de las kyang dbang
NK132(no)004:3476: bzhi pa'i ye shes gsal bar rdzogs chen gyi rgyud
NK132(no)004:3478: rgyud kun gyi 'bras bu'i mthar thug dgongs pa'i skyel sor nges nus so //
NK132(no)004:3479: gsum pa rigs pa'i dpang po ni /
NK132(no)004:3480: rgyud kyi gzhung nyid la dpyad pa gsum gyis dag par byas te /
NK132(no)004:3481: sngags rgyud spyi dang mi 'gal la /
NK132(no)004:3482: thun min man ngag gi gnad yod par nges pa bskyed dgos kyang /
NK132(no)004:3483: de dag gi rgyud dang man ngag gi yig cha
NK132(no)004:3484: so sor rgyas par bstan gyi 'dir yi ge mang
NK132(no)004:3486: spyir rgyud sde'i dka' gnad rnams tshur mthong gi ris pa kho nas dpag bya gtan min yang /
NK132(no)004:3487: ci rigs mthar thug dpyod pa'i rigs pas mi 'grub pa'ang ma yin la /
NK132(no)004:3488: rigs pas gnod pa mi 'byung ba ni lung rigs kyis 'grub nus so //
NK132(no)004:3489: de ltar dan dpang gsum po 'di dag cag gi
NK132(no)004:3490: rgyud yod pas yid ches su rung ba nyid do
NK132(no)004:3491: // phyis kyi 'gyur phal cher la snga 'gyur dang mthun pa rnams der zad /
NK132(no)004:3492: sgrub thabs sogs yig cha sne phran mang po la
NK132(no)004:3493: ni snga 'gyur dang mtshungs pa'i khungs btsun sgrub mi
NK132(no)004:3494: nus te / rog shes rab 'od kyi gsungs las kyang 'di ltar /
NK132(no)004:3495: dus phyis rgya gar du bstan pa'i grwa nyams /
NK132(no)004:3496: rgyud sde rnams rim gyis nub /
NK132(no)004:3497: rgya dpe rnams kyang phal cher chud zos /
NK132(no)004:3498: grub thob kha yar gyis mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod nas
NK132(no)004:3499: blangs pa rnams khong du ma chud de gnyer tshag
NK132(no)004:3500: ma byas / de'i tshe bstan pa phyi dar du grags pa'i skabs na /
NK132(no)004:3501: rgya pan gser 'dod rnams kyis bod na chos gang rtsis che dris nas bcos ma mang po byas /
NK132(no)004:3502: lo ts+aa mkhas grags 'dod pa rnams kyis /
NK132(no)004:3505: sngon gyi lo pan byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis
NK132(no)004:3506: bsgyur ba rnams la rang bzo'i 'gyur bcos sna tshogs
NK132(no)004:3507: byas / rtsa rlung thig le sogs phyi rol pa
NK132(no)004:3508: dang thun mong ba'i chos la ngo mtshar ba'i gnas
NK132(no)004:3509: su byas nas rgya gar ba'i khung bzang drangs te
NK132(no)004:3510: gsar chos rtsis che byas pas bstan pa nyams dmas
NK132(no)004:3512: gser 'dod kyi pan+di ta ji ltar byung tshul yang
NK132(no)004:3513: sa chen bsod nams rtse mo'i bka' 'bum gtor chen
NK132(no)004:3515: sngon ba ri lo ts+aa bas bal yul nas pan+di
NK132(no)004:3516: ta zhig spyan drangs nas gser med pas spu rang
NK132(no)004:3517: du byon pa dang btsad po rtse sde mjal nas
NK132(no)004:3518: dbang bskur chos bshad pas rgyal pos gser srang brgya
NK132(no)004:3519: phul / de rnams pan+di tas tshag byas pas /
NK132(no)004:3520: bla ma bdag la cung zad gnang bar zhu byas
NK132(no)004:3521: kyang ma gnang bar ma zad slar brgal ba log
NK132(no)004:3523: shin tu sun pas pan+di ta bal yul du skyel du byon skad /
NK132(no)004:3525: ka ma'i yul du mu stegs kyi pan+di ta skal
NK132(no)004:3526: ldan rgyal po zhes bya bas khyod nga'i lo ts+aa
NK132(no)004:3527: gyis la bod du 'gro dgos zer /
NK132(no)004:3528: de mi byed byas pas khong na re /
NK132(no)004:3529: ngas mu stegs pa'i chos mi bshad /
NK132(no)004:3530: sangs rgyas pa'i chos bshad zer yang ma nyan pas /
NK132(no)004:3531: ngas khyod la mthu byed zer /
NK132(no)004:3532: ngas nyes pa byas pa med pas mthu bya thabs med zer nas rgya gar du song /
NK132(no)004:3533: de nas bla ma rdo rje gdan pa dang mjal nas chos gsan zhing yod pa dang /
NK132(no)004:3534: bla mas khyod la mu stegs pas gnod pa yong bar 'dug gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3536: 'o na bal yul du ji ltar byung ba zhus pas /
NK132(no)004:3537: b+ha ya na sa'i sngags dang gtor ma 'di gnang /
NK132(no)004:3538: gtor chen lan gsum btang bas mu stegs kyi pan+di ta kho shi skad ces gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3539: des mtshon dus phyis kyi pan+di ta phal pa rnams lta ci /
NK132(no)004:3540: gang zag dam pa yin nges ga ya d+ha ra
NK132(no)004:3541: lta bu lam skor gyi gdams pa la mkhas shing
NK132(no)004:3542: brgyud pa 'dzin nges yin pa des kyang /
NK132(no)004:3543: gser btsal ba'i tshul lam 'bras lo rgyus las /
NK132(no)004:3544: bla chen 'brog mis rin 'byung zhi ba las 'dul ba phar phyin gsang sngags mang du gsan /
NK132(no)004:3545: bir+wa dang dom+bi mi thub zla ba'i slob ma dge
NK132(no)004:3546: slong dpa' bo rdo rje las kye rdor rgyud gsum
NK132(no)004:3547: yan lag dang bcas pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK132(no)004:3548: rim pa lam 'bras rtsa ba med pa gsan /
NK132(no)004:3549: lo bcu gnyis bzhugs nas bod du byon /
NK132(no)004:3551: ga ya d+ha ras bsur shog gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3552: chos ci shes dris pas rdo rje theg par mkhas par dgongs te bsus /
NK132(no)004:3553: bram pa lha rtse'i brag la lo lngar bzhugs /
NK132(no)004:3560: byon nas gser srang brgya phul /
NK132(no)004:3561: de nas ga ya d+ha rar gser srang lnga brgya dus gcig phul /
NK132(no)004:3562: thugs ma ches sgyu ma yin nam dgongs te /
NK132(no)004:3563: lam khar mang gar dril chen gyi mi mang 'gro
NK132(no)004:3564: ba la 'di rnams gser du 'dug mi 'dug dris
NK132(no)004:3565: pas gser du 'dug smras pas shin tu dgyes /
NK132(no)004:3566: da khyod ci dga' bya gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3569: 'o na gsung ngag 'di gzhan la mi gsungs par zhu ba phul /
NK132(no)004:3570: bla mas zhal gyis bzhes nas rgya gar du gshegs /
NK132(no)004:3571: bla chen 'brog mi la 'brom gyis chos thun re la gser zho re /
NK132(no)004:3572: dar chen zab yug re dang 'dra ba phul /
NK132(no)004:3573: nang gcig man+dala gyi gser zad /
NK132(no)004:3575: kho rang gi jo mo'i dar sham phud nas phul bas cung ma mnyes /
NK132(no)004:3576: de ltar snga phyir 'bul chen blos mi lcog pa byas kyang /
NK132(no)004:3577: res zhig rta gcig g.yor byas pas /
NK132(no)004:3578: slob dpon gyis slob ma la 'bul ba byed pa'i lugs med gsungs nas ma g.yar /
NK132(no)004:3579: des da phan 'brog mi sh+aakya thub pa dngos su gyur kyang 'dir mi 'ong smras /
NK132(no)004:3580: de nas khrag skyugs nas 'da' khar /
NK132(no)004:3581: nga'i bla ma sangs rgyas yin par 'dug /
NK132(no)004:3582: slob ma'i snod brtag pa ma shes gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3584: 'brog mis 'brom gyi rus pa pang du blang nas bshums /
NK132(no)004:3585: de rjes gdams ngag gang yod dka' ba med par gsungs skad /
NK132(no)004:3586: spyir bla chen 'brog mis gzhung gsungs pa la man ngag mi gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3587: man ngag gsungs pa la gzhung mi gsungs pa yin kyang /
NK132(no)004:3589: jo mo'i ming po sogs la ngo chen du gsungs
NK132(no)004:3590: par sa skya'i gong ma rnams kyi bka' 'bum las
NK132(no)004:3591: 'byung / de dag gdul bya 'dul ba'i dgos pa yin mchi ste /
NK132(no)004:3592: tshul des gdams ngag btab pa'i gang zag thams cad nyams rtogs rgya cher smin cing /
NK132(no)004:3593: rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa la lo pan 'di tsho bka' drin che ba yin mod /
NK132(no)004:3594: rnam pa'i tshul la gser la de tsam gdung tshul mdzad /
NK132(no)004:3595: des na de 'dra'i gser 'dod kyi pan+di ta rnams las /
NK132(no)004:3596: gser gyis sa steng bkang yang dgos pa med pa'i pang 'byung bi ma sogs /
NK132(no)004:3597: gzhan don 'ba' zhig gis dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro'i snying
NK132(no)004:3598: khrag lta bu'i chos sde bod du spel ba rnams
NK132(no)004:3599: bka' btsan la khungs bzang bar cis mi 'gyur /
NK132(no)004:3600: pan grub de dag gis gser bsgrub nas rang yul
NK132(no)004:3601: du log pa'i lo rgyus mi snang ba 'dis kyang
NK132(no)004:3602: snga 'gyur gyi dus kyi gang zag rnams la yid
NK132(no)004:3604: pan chen jo bo rjes kyang bsam yas kyi rgya
NK132(no)004:3605: dpe rnams gzigs dus sngar ma gzigs pa'i rgya dpe
NK132(no)004:3607: gsang sngags 'di la mis shes pa med pa'i mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis kyang /
NK132(no)004:3608: nam mkha' gzhal med khang dpag tu med pa'i sgo
NK132(no)004:3609: phyes nas rgyud sde mang po bstan pa la'ang 'di
NK132(no)004:3610: rnams mi gda'/ theg chen gsang sngags 'di la mtha'
NK132(no)004:3611: chod rgyu rang yod pa mi 'dra gsungs nas thugs
NK132(no)004:3612: rnams mi gda'/ rgyal chag / bod kyi rgyal po la rjes su yi rang mdzad /
NK132(no)004:3613: bod du bstan pa dar ba'i dus de 'dra rgya gar du'ang ma byung /
NK132(no)004:3614: rgya gar du me dgra lan gsum byung bas tshig pa 'dra /
NK132(no)004:3615: rgya gar na med pa'i dpe mang po 'di na snang gsungs nas btsal /
NK132(no)004:3616: zhal bshus nas rgya gar du bskur /
NK132(no)004:3617: slob dpon pad+ma nam mkhar byon nas lha klu dang
NK132(no)004:3618: n+aa len+d+ra sogs nas rgyud sde thams cad bsam yas
NK132(no)004:3620: rgyu mtshan des rgya gar bas bod mang ba yin gsungs pa jo bo'i rnam mthar chen mor snang /
NK132(no)004:3621: snga rgyud rdzun yin na bdag nyid chen po des /
NK132(no)004:3623: bod rdzun red gsungs rigs kyi /
NK132(no)004:3624: phyis su rgyal bstan gyi byi dor mdzad pa'i gtso bo 'di mtshungs gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:3625: de'i phyir sngar gyi lo pan chen po de rnams
NK132(no)004:3626: ni chos kyi bsdu ba po rigs gsum mgon po
NK132(no)004:3627: sogs kyi sprul par gdon mi za ste /
NK132(no)004:3628: cis shes na lung dang rigs pa gnyis kyis te /
NK132(no)004:3631: rgyal bka' rnams bod du ni bod kyi skad du bris so //
NK132(no)004:3632: gsungs pa 'dis bod kyi lo ts+aa chen po de
NK132(no)004:3633: dag bka' yi sdud pa po rnams su 'grub ste
NK132(no)004:3634: / 'di rnams kyi sngon du rgyal ba'i bka' bod
NK132(no)004:3635: kyi yi ger byas pa med pa'i phyir zhes mkhas
NK132(no)004:3636: mchog bu ston sogs bzhed la /
NK132(no)004:3637: rigs pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK132(no)004:3638: bod du chos dar bar mkhan slob chos gsum smon lam btab pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:3639: mkhan pos lo dgu brgyar chos rgyal bsgug tshul dang /
NK132(no)004:3640: pad 'byung ni rgya bod du yongs su grags /
NK132(no)004:3641: gzhan bi ma la sogs pan+di ta dang /
NK132(no)004:3642: thon mi sam+b+ho ta dang bee ro sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba de rnams /
NK132(no)004:3643: mdo dang rgyud sde'i gnad zab mo 'di rnams bod skad du thog mar bsgyur ba la /
NK132(no)004:3644: nges pa'i tshig so so yang dag par rig pa
NK132(no)004:3645: thob pa min na ji bzhin ma nor bar bsgyur
NK132(no)004:3646: mi nus te / bod skad la de'i sngon du
NK132(no)004:3647: gsung rab 'gyur ba'i brda' chad med pas lam srol
NK132(no)004:3649: legs sbyar gyi skad gcig la ming don sna tshogs su 'jug pa yod pas /
NK132(no)004:3650: don ji bzhin pa nges tshig thad kar bsgyur bas don thog khel dka'/
NK132(no)004:3651: khyad par rgyud kyi tshig rnams ni phal cher mtha'
NK132(no)004:3652: drug gis rgyas btab pas mngon shes can min par
NK132(no)004:3653: thad kar sbre mi nus zhes dri med 'od las
NK132(no)004:3655: rgya gar du sa ra ha dang /
NK132(no)004:3656: lu nag dril gsum sogs rdo rje 'chang dang bka'
NK132(no)004:3657: yi sdud po dpa' bo mkha' 'gro rnams kyis lung
NK132(no)004:3658: bstan pa'i grub pa chen po rnams kyis dgongs pa
NK132(no)004:3659: bkral nas gtan la phab pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:3660: rtog ge'i yul ma yin pa'i mdo rgyud kyi chos
NK132(no)004:3661: thams cad don 'gyur mdzad pas don la nor 'khrul
NK132(no)004:3663: tshig bying che go bde snyan legs rgya gzhung dang bsdur na'ang tshig zur ma nyams pa /
NK132(no)004:3664: phyis kyi lo ts+aa mkhas pas rgya dpe bod dpe
NK132(no)004:3665: kun nas brtag dus lhag par yid ches skye yis
NK132(no)004:3666: bcos dgos mi snang ba sha stag yin te /
NK132(no)004:3667: phyis kyi lo ts+aa'i nang nas mchog gyur rngog lo chen pos kyang /
NK132(no)004:3668: mdo rgyan nang a ra ga ra ga'i sgra kho na snang bas 'gyur ma shes /
NK132(no)004:3670: ma chags mi chags sogs su bsgyur ba la ya mtshan skyes te /
NK132(no)004:3671: bee ro tsa na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK132(no)004:3672: ska cog rnam gnyis nyi zla zung gcig la //
NK132(no)004:3673: rin chen bzang po tho rang skar chen tsam //
NK132(no)004:3674: kho bo de drung srin bu me khyer bzhin //
NK132(no)004:3675: zhes snga 'gyur gyi lo ts+aa ba rnams la basngagasa pa cher mdzad cing /
NK132(no)004:3676: sgra dang don gyi gnas la mkhas pa sa skya pan+di tas kyang /
NK132(no)004:3677: legs par sbyar las bod skad du //
NK132(no)004:3678: mkhas pas bsgyur ba thams cad dag /
NK132(no)004:3679: sgra mi shes pas bsgyur ba la //
NK132(no)004:3680: tshig don nor ba ci rigs mthong //
NK132(no)004:3681: de 'dra bdag gis bcos nas bshad //
NK132(no)004:3682: ska cog sogs kyis bsgyur ba la //
NK132(no)004:3683: 'ga' zhig sgra dang cung ma mthun //
NK132(no)004:3685: 'ga' zhig brda rnying go ba dka' //
NK132(no)004:3686: 'ga' zhig snga ma btsan par byas //
NK132(no)004:3687: la la gsar bcad dag gis bcos //
NK132(no)004:3688: la la rgya skad sor bzhag snang //
NK132(no)004:3689: la la khams kyi bye brag gis //
NK132(no)004:3690: rgya skad gcig la bshad tshul gyis //
NK132(no)004:3691: bod kyi sgra 'gyur tha dad snang //
NK132(no)004:3693: de dag legs par dpyis phyin pa //
NK132(no)004:3694: blun po rnams kyis lta ci smos //
NK132(no)004:3695: mkhas pa yin kyang shes par dka' //
NK132(no)004:3696: de dag bdag gis tha snyad la //
NK132(no)004:3697: sbyangs pa'i stobs kyis legs par shes //
NK132(no)004:3698: 'on kyang skye bo chags sdang dang //
NK132(no)004:3699: blun phyir bdag ni khyad du bsad //
NK132(no)004:3701: mgon po sras dang bcas pas mkhyen //
NK132(no)004:3703: 'dis nges pa'i tshig so so yang dag par rig pa thob par sgrub nus te /
NK132(no)004:3704: de ltar bsgyur nas da phyin chad kyang de ltar
NK132(no)004:3705: ma bsgyur na tshig dang don legs par ston mi
NK132(no)004:3706: nus pa'i phyir / sgra sbyor bam po gnyis pa
NK132(no)004:3707: sogs su rgya skad bod skad sbyar te bsgyur tshul
NK132(no)004:3708: 'di 'dra dgos pa'i gnad bkas bcad pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:3709: phyis kyi lo ts+aa thams cad de'i rjes su zhugs nas 'gyur ba sha stag yin /
NK132(no)004:3710: shin tu rgya che don zab mdo dang rgyud kyi
NK132(no)004:3711: gzhung de dag gi don 'grel chen mo rgya gar
NK132(no)004:3712: gyi pan grub kyis brtsams pa rnams dang bstun dus
NK132(no)004:3713: tshig don gang nas kyang sngar ltar sor bzhags las
NK132(no)004:3714: bcos mi dgos pa 'di mkhas pas bltas na ngo
NK132(no)004:3715: mtshar rmad du byung ba'i gnas yin no //
NK132(no)004:3716: kha cig gis don 'gyur zhes pa bstan bya'i don yod tsam las /
NK132(no)004:3717: tshig gi tshul rgya skad dang thad sor mthun pa zhig yin nam snyam na de min te /
NK132(no)004:3718: bstan bya'i don ji bzhin khong du chud nas tshig
NK132(no)004:3719: de nyid rgya bod skad rigs mi 'dra yang don
NK132(no)004:3720: 'dra bas tshig don gnyis ka ma nyams par bsgyur
NK132(no)004:3722: dper na go sgra gcig la'ang /
NK132(no)004:3723: sa dang ba lang dang rdo rje sogs don dgu la 'jug pa yod kyi /
NK132(no)004:3724: skabs de'i go sgra gang la 'jug pa'i don nyid ma shes na 'gyur nyes 'ong bas /
NK132(no)004:3725: phyis kyi tshig 'gyur phal cher don nor zhing sdeb mi legs pa byung ba yin /
NK132(no)004:3726: sngar lo pan 'dzom nas bod skad du bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:3727: slar yang ma nor bar zhus dag byas /
NK132(no)004:3728: de 'chad nyan gyis gtan la phab pa yin pas
NK132(no)004:3729: snga 'gyur zol med yin na shin tu yid ches
NK132(no)004:3731: 'dul ba mdo sde'i gzhung thams cad bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:3732: kha cig chags sdang gi bsam pas snga 'gyur las
NK132(no)004:3733: phyi 'gyur rtsis che bar byed pa ni zhen lta
NK132(no)004:3735: dbu ma rtsa shes lta bu sogs la /
NK132(no)004:3737: 'gyur mi bcos su mi rung ba rnams bcos zhes 'jug pa'i gzhung sogs la brten /
NK132(no)004:3738: 'phags pa yab sras kyi lugs dang mi mthun pa'i 'gyur nyes yod pa ltar bstan 'dug kyang /
NK132(no)004:3739: 'gyur nyes min yang yig skyon 'dra song ba bsal yod na 'thad pa las /
NK132(no)004:3740: dngos don mi bcos mi rung ba ni ci zhig bcos 'dug dpyad na /
NK132(no)004:3741: ngo bo nyid zer ba thams cad rang bzhin du
NK132(no)004:3742: bsgyur ba 'gyur khyad tsam las don sngar dang mi
NK132(no)004:3744: pa tshab kyis 'gyur bcos can gyi rtsa shes rtsa ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3745: dbu ma sher sgron legs ldan 'byed kyi 'grel ba'i
NK132(no)004:3746: nang gi rtsa ba snga 'gyur dang bstun te ltos
NK132(no)004:3748: des mtshon 'gyur rnying dang 'gyur gsar la dpyad na /
NK132(no)004:3749: don zab barlinga tshig go bde rlabs che ba snga 'gyur dang mtshungs pa med la /
NK132(no)004:3750: de nyid bsdus pa sogs phyi nang gi rgyud sde
NK132(no)004:3751: phal cher snga yod la rgya dpe dang bstun zhus
NK132(no)004:3753: snga 'gyur gyi 'gyur byang snga na med pa'am yod kyang ma bzhag par /
NK132(no)004:3754: rin bzang sogs phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur byang
NK132(no)004:3755: gsar ma dag gis phyogs zhen gyis byas par mngon
NK132(no)004:3756: pas nor 'khrul med don de las byung /
NK132(no)004:3757: phyis kyi mkhas pas bsgyur ba la nor 'khrul med pa yod mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:3758: snga 'gyur lo pan 'dzoms nas bsgyur ba la 'gran zla med pas /
NK132(no)004:3759: rin bzang rngog lo sa pan bu ston sogs phyis
NK132(no)004:3760: kyi lo ts+aa ba thams cad kyis kyang tshad mar
NK132(no)004:3761: 'dzin cing de la khungs gtugs te sngar ma 'gyur
NK132(no)004:3762: ba rnams kyang de'i 'gyur tshul dang mtshungs par bsgyur
NK132(no)004:3763: ba yin / phyis 'gyur la de 'dra dka' ste /
NK132(no)004:3764: mkhas mchog bu ston sogs kyi 'gyur la'ang /
NK132(no)004:3765: phyis si tu kun mkhyen d+harma ka ra sogs kyis bcos dgos pa du ma byung 'dug pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:3766: deng sang rgya skad kyi mtshams sbyor dang ming le
NK132(no)004:3767: tsam yang yid ches shing dpyis phyin par mi shes
NK132(no)004:3768: pas 'gyur bzang ngan dpyad pa ni /
NK132(no)004:3769: chu bran brgal bar mi nus par rgya mtsho chen po rkyal gyis chod par rlom pa dang 'dra'o //
NK132(no)004:3770: des na bdag nyid chen po rin bzang dang pa
NK132(no)004:3771: tshab sogs la snga 'gyur khyad du gsod pa'i bsam
NK132(no)004:3772: pa mi mnga' zhing byas pa gzo ba'i thugs mnga'
NK132(no)004:3773: mod kyi / phyis kyi phyogs zhen can dag gis
NK132(no)004:3774: rang che 'byin pa'i tshig zur ci rigs bsnan par
NK132(no)004:3776: de bzhin dkar chag 'phang thang ma sogs su tshad
NK132(no)004:3777: ma rnam 'grel sogs gzhung bsgyur kyang zhus dag ma
NK132(no)004:3778: byas pas 'gyur byang ma phog pa phal mo che
NK132(no)004:3779: la phyis kyi 'gyur byang btab cing /
NK132(no)004:3780: mkhas pa rnams kyis 'grel pa sogs bsdur te 'chad
NK132(no)004:3781: nyan gyi gtan la phab pa du ma yod pa
NK132(no)004:3782: yod mod / de thams cad snga 'gyur gyi drin
NK132(no)004:3783: las byung bar mi shes par snga 'gyur pa dman
NK132(no)004:3784: par sems pa ni byas pa khyad du gsod pa'i
NK132(no)004:3786: des na snga 'gyur gyi dus su bsgyur ba'i mdo
NK132(no)004:3787: rgyud 'di dag rgyal ba'i bka' la tshad med kyang
NK132(no)004:3788: de'i nang gi zab rgyas kyi don tshang zhing lam
NK132(no)004:3789: gyi lus rdzogs pa'i snying po gser zhun lta bu
NK132(no)004:3790: rnams sprul pa'i lo pan mchog rnams kyi bka' drin
NK132(no)004:3791: las bod kyi skal par thob pa yin pa kun
NK132(no)004:3793: de ltar legs par dpyad na /
NK132(no)004:3794: sangs rgyas kyi bka' yin min gyi thag chod pa so skye sus kyang mi nus te /
NK132(no)004:3795: mngon sum tshad mas sangs rgyas kyi bka' min par ji ltar nges nus te /
NK132(no)004:3796: gzhung de dngos su rdzun rtsom byed par mthong na der zad /
NK132(no)004:3797: de min na mngon shes med pas sangs rgyas kyi bka' yin min mi shes te /
NK132(no)004:3798: bka' yin par 'dod pa 'di rnams kyang /
NK132(no)004:3799: bla ma brgyud pa tshad ldan las yid ches par byas pa yin gyi /
NK132(no)004:3800: sangs rgyas las dngos su ni phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba sus kyang blang ba'i lo rgyus med la /
NK132(no)004:3801: rigs pas dpyad na'ang sangs rgyas kyi bka' ni yul gyi skad sna tshogs kyis gsungs pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:3802: rnam pa thams cad pa'i gsung yin pas gdul bya'i mos pa bzhin du 'char ba'i gsung gcig las /
NK132(no)004:3803: rang rang gi mos pa dang 'tshams par tshig rgyas bsdus sna tshogs /
NK132(no)004:3804: don sbas ma sbas sna tshogs yod pas gzhung nyi
NK132(no)004:3805: tshe ba gcig la cha bzhag nas thams cad de
NK132(no)004:3806: dang mthun mi mthun dpyod pas bka' yin min 'byed
NK132(no)004:3807: ga la nus / gsung tshul rgyud kyi gleng gzhi
NK132(no)004:3808: ston 'khor sogs sangs rgyas kyi gsung tshul yod pa
NK132(no)004:3809: tsam gyis gsung du ma nges te /
NK132(no)004:3810: rgyud bardzusa pa rtsom shes mkhan zhig yin na gleng
NK132(no)004:3811: gzhi sogs sbyar te sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa lta
NK132(no)004:3813: kho bos byas so zhes gsal bar brjod na sangs rgyas kyi bkar bardzusa par mi 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:3814: tshig ris la dpyad na rgya skad las bsgyur ba'i nyams dang /
NK132(no)004:3815: bka' dang dgongs 'grel rnams la tshig gi babs rgya
NK132(no)004:3816: gzhung snga ma tsho dang 'dra mi 'dra'i nyams yod
NK132(no)004:3817: mod / sgyur byed kyi lo ts+aa'i 'gyur mdzad tshul dang /
NK132(no)004:3818: rgyud dang 'grel ba rnams su'ang bka'i tshig dngos ci rigs 'dres yod pas /
NK132(no)004:3819: de bka' nas kyang byung ba'i dpe mthong zin na ma gtogs /
NK132(no)004:3820: tshig ris la bltas pas bka' dang bstan bcos so sor rtags 'god pa ji ltar yod /
NK132(no)004:3821: don la dpyad na'ang sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde
NK132(no)004:3822: bzhi'i dgongs pa dang 'gal ba zhig rgyud bardzusa par
NK132(no)004:3823: ci la rtsom / gal te 'gal ba ltar snang na'ang /
NK132(no)004:3824: pha dang ma ni bsad bya zhing //
NK132(no)004:3825: zhes sogs dang mtshungs par sngags rgyud rnams su mtha' drug gis rgyas btab yod pas /
NK132(no)004:3826: de'i tshig sgra ji bzhin yin kyang the tshom chod dka' bas bka' min du thag ga la chod /
NK132(no)004:3827: rgyud la'ang tshig dam zhing sbas tshul can gyi rgyud kyi rigs rnams bshad rgyud kyis gsal dgos la /
NK132(no)004:3828: ma sbas pa rnams nges don dang sgra ji bzhin pa'ang yod /
NK132(no)004:3829: sdeb sbyor phun sum tshogs pa'i tshul can yang yod /
NK132(no)004:3830: sgra nyams pa lta bur snang ba'ang yod /
NK132(no)004:3831: bsdus rgyud lta bu'i tshig don phun sum tshog pa
NK132(no)004:3832: las sgra'i nga rgyal bcag pa'i phyir bdun pa'i don
NK132(no)004:3833: la gnyis pa sogs ched du mdzad pa bzhin dang
NK132(no)004:3834: / go bde zhing lhug par ston pa'i bod rtsom
NK132(no)004:3835: dang bon po gter ma phal dang tshul 'dra ba'ang
NK132(no)004:3836: gdul bya'i snod kyi dbang gis te /
NK132(no)004:3837: bstan bya nyi tshe ba dang /
NK132(no)004:3840: yul sna tshogs kyi nges tshig yod pas tshig ris tsam gyi ngos nas mi zin no //
NK132(no)004:3841: des na 'di 'dra'i rigs rnams dpyad par dka' bas kha tshon mi chod de /
NK132(no)004:3842: bka' yin pa la min par skur pa btab na
NK132(no)004:3843: chos spang gi las gsog pas rnying ma pa rnams
NK132(no)004:3844: kyi bka' dang bstan bcos la g.yo can gyi skur
NK132(no)004:3846: bdag gis kyang btang snyoms su bzhag pa las shes
NK132(no)004:3847: mdog gi kha tshon nam yang gcod par mi bya
NK132(no)004:3848: ste / nges pa'i gtan tshig rnyed dka' bas thag gcod rgyu ga la yod /
NK132(no)004:3849: tshig ris la brtag na mkhas pas rtsom pa'i nyams dang /
NK132(no)004:3850: de ltar min pa grong tshig gi gshis can gang yin sus kyang shes sla ste /
NK132(no)004:3851: de tsam gyi bka' yin min sogs nges dka' ste /
NK132(no)004:3852: sangs rgyas kyi gsung ni gdul bya'i dbang gis rjod
NK132(no)004:3853: byed sna tshogs dang don sna tshogs su yod pa
NK132(no)004:3856: ji ltar bsil dang zhim dang 'jam pa dang //
NK132(no)004:3857: yang ba'i chu ni sprin chen las thon pa //
NK132(no)004:3858: sa la ba tsh+wa la sogs gnas 'brel bas //
NK132(no)004:3859: shin tu mang po'i ro ni 'byung ba yin //
NK132(no)004:3860: de bzhin 'phags lam yan lag brgyad chu'i char //
NK132(no)004:3861: rab yangs brtse sprin snying po las thon pa //
NK132(no)004:3862: 'gro ba'i rgyud kyi gnas kyi dbye ba yis //
NK132(no)004:3863: rnam pa mang po'i ro dang ldan par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:3865: de bzhin sngags kyi yi ge la'ang sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)004:3866: gsung yin na legs sbyar kho na yin pa'i nges
NK132(no)004:3867: pa med de / lha klu mi sogs skad sna tshogs par byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags yod pas /
NK132(no)004:3868: legs sbyar kho nar ma nges te /
NK132(no)004:3870: kun mkhyen lam don gnyer ba rnams la sgra dang sgra min la sogs rnam dpyad chen po med //
NK132(no)004:3871: sna tshogs yul skad ngan pa yis kyang chen po rnams kyi lam la rtag tu 'jug /
NK132(no)004:3872: sems can rnams kyi dbang gis thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung mchog la //
NK132(no)004:3873: brda' sprod pa dang klus bkod sgra brtsegs rtsod pa don gnyer rnams kyis de las gzhan //
NK132(no)004:3875: dud 'gro yi dwags lha min rnams dang lto 'phye lha mi 'phags pa bod la sogs rnams la //
NK132(no)004:3876: byung dang 'byung 'gyur de ltar byung ba rnam pa gsum dang rtag tu bden pa'i chos gsungs shing //
NK132(no)004:3877: rang rang skad gzhan rnams kyis srid gsum ma tshang med pa lam la yang dag 'god byed pa //
NK132(no)004:3878: 'di ni bde nyams 'bras bu ster ba thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung ste lha yi skad kyis min //
NK132(no)004:3880: dper na legs sbyar la yi ge mang po brtsegas pa med kyang /
NK132(no)004:3881: dus 'khor la rnam bcu dbang ldan gyi sngags sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:3882: rnying ma'i tshe bdag +ye lta bu sogs shin tu mang zhing /
NK132(no)004:3883: brda' don tshe'i sgo nas +amo la ring chab tags pa /
NK132(no)004:3884: sgra bsgyur te kro d+ha la kro ta sogs su
NK132(no)004:3885: 'bod pa sogs sgra nyams sna tshogs ni man ngag
NK132(no)004:3886: can gyi sngags kyi sgyur so gang zhig rno ba'i
NK132(no)004:3887: gnad dang ldan pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:3888: 'di 'dra mtha' dag phyogs re'i dpyad pas shes mi nus te /
NK132(no)004:3889: dper na mtshan brjod thig le stong pa yi ge brgya'i skad dod dang /
NK132(no)004:3890: sha ta drug gi skad dod la /
NK132(no)004:3891: thig stong yig drug mtshon byed dbyug pa'i rnam pa
NK132(no)004:3892: drug 'dus pa'i e yig tu grub pa de yin
NK132(no)004:3893: la / sha ta shwa ta ra bsgyur na rgya yi skad dod de /
NK132(no)004:3894: yi ge bargya'am lha brgya yi sa bon du'ang rung ba lta bu /
NK132(no)004:3895: brgya dang drug khyad che yang don la mi 'gal
NK132(no)004:3896: ba lta bu 'di 'dra phal gyi blo ngor mi
NK132(no)004:3897: 'thad kyang mkhas pa la ches mdzes gsungs /
NK132(no)004:3898: rnying ma'i sngags phal cher bod skad yin pas 'di la the tshom za 'dug kyang /
NK132(no)004:3899: gsar rgyud phyag rdor gsang ba mngon bstan gyi rgyud
NK132(no)004:3900: sogs na'ang de 'dra bod skad kyi sngags mang du
NK132(no)004:3901: yod la / kye rdo rje'i rdo rje'i glu sogs
NK132(no)004:3902: rgyud phal mo'i sngags sam glu rnams kyang legs sbyar
NK132(no)004:3903: kho na min par zur chags sogs du ma yod
NK132(no)004:3904: yod la / / de'i phyir mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i brda' dang lha klu gnod sbyin rnams dang /
NK132(no)004:3905: mi yi skad kyi bye brag legs sbyar zur chag sogs bzhi dang /
NK132(no)004:3906: bod sogs yul so so'i skad du byin gyis brlabs pa yod de /
NK132(no)004:3907: chos thams cad kyang nges tshig sna tshogs kyis ma bstan na /
NK132(no)004:3908: skad rigs gcig gis yul gcig gi ston par 'gyur gyi /
NK132(no)004:3909: yul thams cad du ston mi nus kyi /
NK132(no)004:3910: nges tshig so so yang dag par rig pa thob
NK132(no)004:3911: pa'i sangs rgyas byang sems rnams kyis skad sna tshogs
NK132(no)004:3913: lha yi skad dang klu dang gnod sbyin skad //
NK132(no)004:3914: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang //
NK132(no)004:3915: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra rnams ji tsam par //
NK132(no)004:3916: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos bstan to //
NK132(no)004:3918: de bzhin du bzla ba'i sngags kyang legs sbyar kho
NK132(no)004:3919: nar byin gyis rlobs kyi gzhan pa'i skad la byin
NK132(no)004:3920: brlab mi nus pa ma yin te gang la'ang brlab
NK132(no)004:3921: nus so // de'i phyir rnying rgyud rnams su rgya
NK132(no)004:3922: skad du sngags byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags sor bzhag
NK132(no)004:3923: nus so // pa'ang yod / sham bu sogs sngags dngos la'ang bod skad du byas pa yod de /
NK132(no)004:3924: de dag rno myur khyad du 'phags par sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:3925: las mi gzhan pa'i pad+ma 'byung gnas sogs kyis dgongs
NK132(no)004:3927: de ltar bzlas na bslu ba med pa ni /
NK132(no)004:3928: pu tra b+ha dra'i sngags zhang zhung gi skad du yod pa bsam yas su gter du sbas /
NK132(no)004:3929: phyis kha cig gis bton pa'i tshe lo chen rin
NK132(no)004:3930: bzang gi las sbyor mdzad pa rgya skad kyi sngags
NK132(no)004:3932: zhang zhung gi skad kyi sngags kyis dgra thul bas /
NK132(no)004:3933: pad 'byung dus gsum mkhyen pa yin no zhes basngagasa
NK132(no)004:3934: par sa skya'i mgon pod sogs su gsungs pas mtshon
NK132(no)004:3935: nas shes so // des na dbyig gnyen gyis /
NK132(no)004:3936: dam chos tshul la tshad ma thub rnams yin //
NK132(no)004:3938: chos dang gang zag gi tshad 'dzin shin tu daka'o //
NK132(no)004:3939: rang the tshom med pa'i chos zhig la blo gtad /
NK132(no)004:3940: gzhan la sgro skur mi bya bar btang snyoms su bzhag na legs te /
NK132(no)004:3942: yid kyi nyes pa rang bzhin gdug pa ste //
NK132(no)004:3943: mi rigs pa yi gzugs la'ang mi rigs na //
NK132(no)004:3944: the tshom za ba'i chos la smros ci dgos //
NK132(no)004:3945: de bas btang snyoms bzhag legs nyes pa med //
NK132(no)004:3947: nges par zog pos chos la slad btang nas bstan
NK132(no)004:3948: pa'i tshig dang don dkrug pa mthong na bstan pa
NK132(no)004:3949: la gces spras kyis ma dag pa sun 'byin pa
NK132(no)004:3950: gnad yin kyang / sngar yod kyi chos 'di dag
NK132(no)004:3951: la ha cang dag ma dag gi dpyad ra dang
NK132(no)004:3952: brjod pa mang ba la dgos pa cher ma mthong
NK132(no)004:3953: gnad yin kyang / ngo // de ltar gsar rnying grub matha'i chags sdang gis /
NK132(no)004:3954: rnying chos mi dag par smra ba'i tshul rnams legs par brtags te the tshom bcad nas /
NK132(no)004:3955: da ni gsar ma las che ba drug gis khyad
NK132(no)004:3956: par du 'phags pa'i tshul sngon gyi mkhas grub dag
NK132(no)004:3957: gis gsungs pa'i don brjod par bya ste /
NK132(no)004:3958: de yang smra ba'i seng chen rong zom pa chos kyi bzang po'i zhal snga nas /
NK132(no)004:3959: spyan 'dren pa po yon bdag gi che ba /
NK132(no)004:3960: snga 'gyur yon bdag 'phags pa rigs gsum mgon po'i
NK132(no)004:3961: rnam 'phrul chos rgyal mes dbon rnam gsum yin pas
NK132(no)004:3962: phyi 'gyur gyi yon bdag dang mi 'dra /
NK132(no)004:3963: gang du bsgyur ba'i gnas kyang /
NK132(no)004:3964: sngon sprul pa'i gtsug lag khang bsam yas sogs chos
NK132(no)004:3965: 'khor stod smad yin pas da lta'i grong dgon phag
NK132(no)004:3968: sngon sgra bsgyur bee ro tsa na dang ska cog
NK132(no)004:3969: zhang gsum rma gnyags gnubs sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa
NK132(no)004:3971: da lta brda' sprod gzhung du ma re shes pa la lo ts+aar btags /
NK132(no)004:3973: dgun bal yul du yug re phyin nas bsgyur ba dang mi 'dra /
NK132(no)004:3978: bi ma la sogs sangs rgyas dang sa chen po
NK132(no)004:3979: la bzhugs pa'i byang 'phags rnams kyis spyan drangs pa'i
NK132(no)004:3980: chos yin / da lta gser 'dod du 'khyams pa rnams dang mi 'dra /
NK132(no)004:3982: sngon gser sha ba'i blud bu dang bre la gzhal nas phul ba'i chos yin /
NK132(no)004:3983: da lta mchan nas gser zho re gnyis bton nas zhus pa dang mi 'dra /
NK132(no)004:3984: chos kyi khyad par sngon 'phags yul du sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:3985: kyi bstan pa gra ma nyams dus bsgyur bar ma
NK132(no)004:3986: zad / 'phags yul na med pa'i rgyud /
NK132(no)004:3987: byang chub sems dpa' dang grub pa dang rig 'dzin
NK132(no)004:3988: dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bzung ste dag pa'i
NK132(no)004:3990: 'dzam gling gi bye brag o rgyan dang /
NK132(no)004:3992: slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma la sogs grub pa'i
NK132(no)004:3993: khyu mchog rnams kyis rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pas blang
NK132(no)004:3995: 'gyur yang sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba rnams sprul pa'i
NK132(no)004:3996: sku yin pas don ji lta ba bzhin du gtan
NK132(no)004:3997: la phebs pas go sla zhing byings 'jal ba la
NK132(no)004:3998: rlabs che zhing / phyis kyi lo ts+aa rnams kyis
NK132(no)004:3999: don bsgyur ma nus par rgya dpe'i go rim ltar
NK132(no)004:4000: sgra bsgyur byas pas tshig grim la go dka'/
NK132(no)004:4001: byings 'jal ba la rlabs chung bas mi 'dra ba yin gsungs /
NK132(no)004:4002: 'di dag rnying ma pas rang bstod yin snyam na ma yin te /
NK132(no)004:4003: don la gnas pa'i che ba yang dag yin no //
NK132(no)004:4005: lo pan gdan 'dzom byas nas yid ches khung btsun
NK132(no)004:4006: gyi chos dag ther du btab ste bsgyur ba de
NK132(no)004:4008: dang po spyan 'dren pa yon bdag gi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4009: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan 'dra ba'i mnga' dbang chen po /
NK132(no)004:4010: rgya dkar nag zhang zhung sogs kyi pan grub bsdus
NK132(no)004:4011: nus pa phyis su ji ltar byung ste ma byung
NK132(no)004:4012: ngo // 'di rgyal po mnga' thang chen po yin
NK132(no)004:4013: du chug na'ang chos kyi che bar mi 'gyur snyam
NK132(no)004:4014: ngo // na / rgyal po mnga' thang chen pos
NK132(no)004:4015: mtha' bzhi'i mkhas grub sdud pa'i sgo nas spel pa'i
NK132(no)004:4016: chos yin pas gsar 'gyur las yid ches khungs btsun
NK132(no)004:4017: gyi che ba nges par yin te /
NK132(no)004:4018: phyis 'gyur la'ang gdan 'dren pa lha bla ma lta bu dang /
NK132(no)004:4019: pan+di ta jo bo chen po lta bu sogs yod mod kyi /
NK132(no)004:4020: de dus gsar 'gyur phran tshegs re las snga dus ltar ma byung na /
NK132(no)004:4021: de las gzhan pa'i lo ts+aa ba rgya gar du
NK132(no)004:4022: rkang pas phyin pa re zung gi lta ci smos
NK132(no)004:4023: / de dag gsar ma'i lo pan khyad gsod min te /
NK132(no)004:4024: bdag nyid chen po de dag kyang bstan 'gror phan bde'i byed po yin mod /
NK132(no)004:4025: chos kyi khungs snga 'gyur pa 'phags tshul bstan pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:4026: gnyis pa gang du bsgyur ba'i gnas phyag bzhes gtsug lag khang gi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4027: sngon gyi dus su grub pa'i slob dpon chen po
NK132(no)004:4028: pad+ma sam+b+ha was gangs can gyi mi dang mi min
NK132(no)004:4029: nag phyogs 'byung po'i tshogs rnams nus pa'i mthus tshar
NK132(no)004:4030: bcad / dkar phyogs kyi lha ma srin sde brgyad
NK132(no)004:4031: rnams dbang du bsdus shing bran du bkol te rgyal
NK132(no)004:4032: chen bzhi sogs las dpon byas te bzhengs shing /
NK132(no)004:4033: khyad par lha klu gnod sbyin mi la sogs pa'i
NK132(no)004:4034: gnas tha dad pa nas rig pa 'dzin pa dang
NK132(no)004:4035: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bzung ba'i rgyud sde mtha' yas
NK132(no)004:4036: pa'i glegs bam rnams spyan drangs shing bzhugs su gsol
NK132(no)004:4037: ba dang / rab tu gnas pa'i me tog 'thor
NK132(no)004:4038: ba sogs kyi tshe ngo mtshar gyi bkod pa bsam
NK132(no)004:4039: gyis mi khyab pa lha mi kun gyi mig gi
NK132(no)004:4041: sngags bdag srung ma'i tshogs kyis bka' yi gnyer kha
NK132(no)004:4042: mdzad pa sogs o rgyan he ru ka'i lha khang
NK132(no)004:4043: dang rnam dbyer med par yongs la grags shing grub
NK132(no)004:4044: pa'i lugs gsum mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug
NK132(no)004:4045: lag khang sogs chos 'khor rnam gsum ste /
NK132(no)004:4046: phyis 'gyur gyi skabs su tho ling gser khang sogs
NK132(no)004:4047: ci rigs yod mod kyi snga ma dang 'gran bzod
NK132(no)004:4048: pa ni 'ga' yang ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:4049: des na de 'dra'i gtsug lag khang bka' nyan zhing zil che ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4050: gtso bor rgya dpe'i dan dpang dang lo pan mkhas
NK132(no)004:4051: grub du ma bzhugs pa'i drung yin pas rang bzo'i
NK132(no)004:4052: tshig bslad phra mo tsam yang gzhug mi nus pa'i
NK132(no)004:4053: phyir / der bsgyur ba'i chos rnams bsregs bcad bdar
NK132(no)004:4054: ba'i gser bzhin tshad mar 'os pa ni snga 'gyur
NK132(no)004:4055: gyi che ba yang dag pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:4056: gsum pa sgra sgyur lo ts+aa ba'i che ba /
NK132(no)004:4057: sa bcu'i dbang phyug 'phags pa kun tu bzang po
NK132(no)004:4058: nyid mi yi tshul bzung ba rnam snang lo ts+aa
NK132(no)004:4059: ba chen po sogs chos kyi gting dpog pa /
NK132(no)004:4061: grub pa'i mtshan rtags mngon du 'chang ba /
NK132(no)004:4062: rje 'bangs nyer lnga sogs dam pa mang po 'dus pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:4063: sgra sgyur brgya rtsa brgyad sogs 'dzoms nas /
NK132(no)004:4064: dang po gzhung bod skad du bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:4065: de'i tshig don la pan chen rnams dpang por byas nas zhus dag byas /
NK132(no)004:4066: de nas 'chad nyan gyis gtan la phab pa de 'dra'i lo ts+aa phyis su yang dkon te /
NK132(no)004:4067: rngog lo ts+aas basngagasa pa gong brjod ltar ro //
NK132(no)004:4068: de ltar lo pan mkhas grub 'dzoms nas dag ther
NK132(no)004:4069: phud pa'i chos yin pas chos kyi che ba dngos
NK132(no)004:4070: su 'agro'o // bzhi pa pan+di ta'i che ba /
NK132(no)004:4071: gsar 'gyur phal la rgya dpe las lo ts+aa bas skad dod bsgyur ba mang la /
NK132(no)004:4072: phal cher pan+di ta las thos nas 'gyur ba dang
NK132(no)004:4073: pan+di ta de dag kyang tshad ldan yin mod kyi
NK132(no)004:4074: snga 'gyur dus kyi pan grub lta bu ches dkon
NK132(no)004:4075: te / bdag nyid chen po sa pan gyis /
NK132(no)004:4076: sdom brtson dam pa dpal ldan zhi ba 'tsho //
NK132(no)004:4077: brtul zhugs grub pa pad+ma 'byung gnas dpal //
NK132(no)004:4078: blo gsal dbang po pad ma'i ngang tshul can //
NK132(no)004:4079: rtsod pa'i dus kyi rgyal ba gnyis pa yin //
NK132(no)004:4081: mkhan chen zhi ba 'tsho lta bu'i sdom brtson chen
NK132(no)004:4082: po shing rta'i srol 'byed kyi slob dpon yongs su
NK132(no)004:4083: grags pa rgya gar na yang dkon par rje tsong
NK132(no)004:4084: kha pas kyang / 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi rdzes bzung bas //
NK132(no)004:4085: rang gzhan grub matha'i pha rol son //
NK132(no)004:4086: zab mo'i don la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK132(no)004:4089: 'di yi rigs pa'i dga' ston myongs pa na //
NK132(no)004:4090: skye ba mang por rigs pa'i lam du ni //
NK132(no)004:4091: ngal ba mang byas sgrub dang sun 'byin la //
NK132(no)004:4092: legs par byang ba'i rgol ba mkhas mang gi //
NK132(no)004:4093: gtsug na gtsug rgyan nor bu ltar mtho ba //
NK132(no)004:4094: smra ba ngan pa'i tshogs rnams mthar mdzad pa //
NK132(no)004:4095: 'phags pa'i yul na'ang ches dkon 'di 'dra ni //
NK132(no)004:4096: bod kyi rje rgyal btsan pos spyan 'drong pa //
NK132(no)004:4097: e ma bdag cag bod 'bangs skal bzang zhes //
NK132(no)004:4098: yid ni rmad byung bde la rol pa yis //
NK132(no)004:4099: yongs su bskyod pas gzhan gyi dbang gyur pas //
NK132(no)004:4101: grub pa'i dbang phyug pad+ma 'byung gnas ni 'phags yul
NK132(no)004:4102: gyi grub thob skar tshogs lta bu'i dbus na zla
NK132(no)004:4103: ba ltar 'phags par yongs su grags shing /
NK132(no)004:4104: 'phags bod 'gro lding sogs su grub pa'i rtags mtshan
NK132(no)004:4105: bsam gyis mi khyab par mngon du bstan pa'i lo
NK132(no)004:4106: rgyus deng sang yang nyams pa med par yongs la
NK132(no)004:4108: pan chen bi ma mi tra ni /
NK132(no)004:4109: mkhas shing grub pa'i khyu mchog yin par rgya bod
NK132(no)004:4110: kun tu grags shing 'pho chen 'ja' lus 'chi med
NK132(no)004:4111: rdo rje'i sku brnyes te da lta'ang rgya nag ri
NK132(no)004:4113: des mtshon nas sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK132(no)004:4114: dzi na mi tra sogs rgya gar na yongs su grags pa /
NK132(no)004:4115: phyis kyi rgya gar gyi pan grub rnams kyis tshad mar 'dzin pa sha stag yin la /
NK132(no)004:4116: de 'dra re zung tsam min par pan grub mang po dus gcig tu zhal 'dzoms nas /
NK132(no)004:4117: mdo sngags kyi chos sgyur zhus gtan la phab pa
NK132(no)004:4118: de 'dra phyis su gsar 'gyur la ji ltar byung
NK132(no)004:4119: / des na sgyur byed pan grub khyad 'phags mang
NK132(no)004:4120: po dpang por bzhugs bzhin chos rnams bslad med gser
NK132(no)004:4121: zhun ma lta bu ma nor bar bsgyur ba ni
NK132(no)004:4122: snga 'gyur ba'i chos kyi che ba yin no //
NK132(no)004:4123: de ltar pan grub khyad 'phags de rnams dbang bcu'i
NK132(no)004:4124: go 'phang brnyes pas bye ma gser dang rde'u g.yu
NK132(no)004:4126: gser dang bong ba mnyam zhing nor gtso bor mi byed pa /
NK132(no)004:4128: smon lam dang thugs bskyed kyis gangs can mun pa'i smag rum 'dul ba'i phrin las can /
NK132(no)004:4129: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i sras po rnams mkhas grub kyi
NK132(no)004:4130: tshul du byon pa yin pa ni sngar dus 'khor
NK132(no)004:4131: gyi lung dang 'jam dpal rtsa rgyud las rgyal po
NK132(no)004:4132: mi yi lha zhes rgyal lung bstan pa sogs kyis
NK132(no)004:4133: grub bo // lnga pa phyag rten me tog gi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4134: chos kyi rgyal pos gser phye bre la gzhal //
NK132(no)004:4135: gser gyis sha ba'i blud bu bkang ba lta bu 'byor pa'i mnga' thang chen pos /
NK132(no)004:4136: lo pan 'di snyed cig bod du gdan 'dzoms par byas pa 'di nyid de /
NK132(no)004:4137: 'di nor gyi che ba tsam yin la chos kyi che bar mi 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)004:4138: gsar ma ba kha cig gis rang lugs la dam
NK132(no)004:4139: pa'i chos dpyad gsum gyis dag pa gser zhun ma
NK132(no)004:4140: lta bu'i che ba brjod mod /
NK132(no)004:4141: dpyad gsum gyis dag pa'i gser zhun ma lta bu
NK132(no)004:4142: de khyed cag mgo rgod pas rnyed pa yin na
NK132(no)004:4143: de ltar yin du chug rung /
NK132(no)004:4144: chos de chos rgyal chen po'i smon lam thugs bskyed
NK132(no)004:4145: mnga' dbang gis byung ba khyed cag gis ma go
NK132(no)004:4146: bar zad do // 'on kyang nor gyi 'byor pa de lta bu med na /
NK132(no)004:4147: jo bo rje bod du spyan 'dren 'dod kyis gser
NK132(no)004:4148: btsal bas lha bla ma ye shes 'od gar log
NK132(no)004:4149: gi btson zhabs su 'da' dgos byung ba'i dpe ltar
NK132(no)004:4150: bsam pa che yang lag tu mi lon mod /
NK132(no)004:4151: chos kyi rgyal po mnga' dbang chen pos /
NK132(no)004:4152: chos kyi sde 'dzug pa'i phyi gtsug lag khang /
NK132(no)004:4153: nang sku gsung thugs kyi rten /
NK132(no)004:4154: bstan pa'i bdag po lo pan gyi lam rgyags dang /
NK132(no)004:4156: zhabs 'bring pa'i skye bo dang bcas pa'i dgos pa'i
NK132(no)004:4157: yo byad thams cad ma tshang ba med pa'i mthu
NK132(no)004:4158: las / lo pan mkhas grub zhal 'dzoms nas chos
NK132(no)004:4159: rnam dag 'gyur ba yin pas 'di yang che bar
NK132(no)004:4161: chos 'byung ba'i yan lag yin pas so //
NK132(no)004:4162: 'di la ltos nas gser chos zer ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4163: rgya gar du bgrod nas dka' bas btsal ba'i chos zhes sam /
NK132(no)004:4164: pan grub kyi gdams pa gcig brgyud ma zhes sogs
NK132(no)004:4165: su bod na 'bod pa gzhan chos yin pa dang
NK132(no)004:4166: rnyed dka' ba yin pa bden kyang /
NK132(no)004:4167: chos rgyal gyi sku dus lta bu'i yon phul ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4168: bee ro lta bu'i dka' ba spyad pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4169: rgya gar gyi pan chen sprul pa'i sku mchog rnams
NK132(no)004:4170: las dngos su blangs pa lta bu shin tu dkon
NK132(no)004:4171: no // des na 'di yang chos kyi che ba yang dag pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:4172: gzhan la che ba yod mod kyi de dang mtshungs pa'i che ba med do //
NK132(no)004:4173: drug pa bsgyur bya chos kyi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4174: mdo rgyud za mo ji snyed 'di snga 'gyur ba'i dus su byung ba yin la /
NK132(no)004:4175: phyis su gzhung re zung gi bsgyur 'phro bsgyur ba yod kyang /
NK132(no)004:4176: sngar ltar rgya che ba bsgyur ma nus te /
NK132(no)004:4177: bye brag bshad mdzod chen po sngar ma bsgyur bar
NK132(no)004:4178: lo ts+aa ba bzang ngan bstan pa'i phyir rgya dpe
NK132(no)004:4179: bsam yas su bzhag pa yin mod /
NK132(no)004:4180: phyis sus kyang bsgyur ba 'dug gam /
NK132(no)004:4181: de bzhin du rgyud 'bum lnga dang /
NK132(no)004:4182: gzhan yang mdo rgyud bod du ma 'gyur ba ches
NK132(no)004:4183: mang po rgya gar du yod na zhing gzhan dang
NK132(no)004:4184: mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod na lta ci smos te /
NK132(no)004:4185: de dag bsgyur nus pa'i stobs 'byor dang nus mthu
NK132(no)004:4186: blo gros byung na 'gyur rigs kyi sus kyang bsgyur
NK132(no)004:4188: khyad par nang rgyud sde gsum 'di ni gsar rnying
NK132(no)004:4189: gnyis kar thun mong du grags pa'i rgyud rnams kyis
NK132(no)004:4190: mtshon pa'i rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho
NK132(no)004:4194: rgyal ba yongs kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phug yin pas /
NK132(no)004:4195: rgya gar du'ang mkhas grub nyung shas kyi thugs la
NK132(no)004:4196: ci rigs mnga' yang shin tu gsang ba'i zab chos
NK132(no)004:4197: yin pas phal pa sus kyang rnyed par dka' ba
NK132(no)004:4198: yin mod / pad 'byung dang bi ma la sogs
NK132(no)004:4199: grub pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba chen po rnams kyis
NK132(no)004:4201: yon la lta ba med pa'i snying rje'i thugs kyis bod kyi skal bar gnang ba yin na'ang /
NK132(no)004:4202: chos dang gang zag gi bar du bdud kyis 'byed
NK132(no)004:4203: pa'i sbyor ba byung nas rtsod pa can du byas
NK132(no)004:4204: te gsar ma ba rnams la the tshom du song
NK132(no)004:4205: / rnying ma pa'i khud pa'i chos skal du thob pas /
NK132(no)004:4206: sngar rig 'dzin gyi sa la bya khyu 'phur ba ltar gshegs pa /
NK132(no)004:4208: yer pa'i grub chen brgyad cu /
NK132(no)004:4209: so zur gnubs sogs grub pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba ches mang po byon /
NK132(no)004:4210: deng sang yang skal ldan re zung gi spyod yul
NK132(no)004:4211: du rang nus dang bstun pa'i nyams len gyi rgyun
NK132(no)004:4212: ma nub tsam du bzhugs kyang /
NK132(no)004:4213: deng sang ni zab mo'i chos mdzod de bzhag nas rtog ge'i zer sgros lhur len pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4214: gter chos gsar pa 'don rgyu nyab nyob tsam don du gnyer ba mang zhing /
NK132(no)004:4215: nang rgyud sde gsum gyi grub matha'i gnad gsang shes
NK132(no)004:4216: 'dod kyis 'chad nyan dang sgom sgrub kyis mtshon bya
NK132(no)004:4218: thu kwan rin po ches mdo sgyu sems gsum gar
NK132(no)004:4219: yod mi shes sogs gsungs pa thog tu 'babs te
NK132(no)004:4220: / 'di bden pa'i gsung gzhan bskul 'debs pa yin par go //
NK132(no)004:4221: nang rgyud 'di'i bstan don phra mo re la nges
NK132(no)004:4222: shes skyes na'ang sngags rgyud rnams kyi rim gnyis kyi
NK132(no)004:4223: gnad la nges shes khyad 'phags res the tshom gcod
NK132(no)004:4225: bde gsang sogs chos rnam dag yin na de'i man
NK132(no)004:4226: ngag 'di na gsal bas 'di chos rnam dag yin
NK132(no)004:4227: par ma zad / chos kyi snying po yin par rigs pas nges nus pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:4228: chos kyi che ba 'di 'dra gsar ma la med de /
NK132(no)004:4230: bde gsang sogs kyi rgyud dang /
NK132(no)004:4232: bskyed rdzogs kyi nyams len yod mod kyang /
NK132(no)004:4233: rnying ma'i rgyud rnams kyi dgongs gzhi bslab ma nus na de dag tshogs bshad tsam las /
NK132(no)004:4234: slob bshad thun min gyi 'chad pa dang nyams len du mi 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)004:4235: zab mo'i gnad snga 'gyur gyi rgyud lung man ngag la ltos nas shes dgos te /
NK132(no)004:4236: sangs rgyas la nye ring gi 'du shes mi mnga' mod /
