NK132(no)004:4237: gdul bya rnams kyi snod dang sbyar na mdo dang rgyud dang /
NK132(no)004:4238: rgyud kyi dgongs pa sbas pa dang ma sbas pa'i rim pas ston par mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:4240: rgyud ni rgyud gzhan gyis shes bya //
NK132(no)004:4242: dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud rgyud gzhan gyi sbas pa
NK132(no)004:4243: mngon du ston pa'i sangs rgyas rin chen za ma
NK132(no)004:4244: tog kha 'byed pa zhes gsungs pa ltar yin pa'i
NK132(no)004:4245: nges shes rnyed rgyu yod pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:4246: nang rgyud sde gsum 'di yang rgyud kun gyi dgongs pa'i mthil yin te /
NK132(no)004:4248: sngags rgyud kyi nyams len mthar thug dbang bzhi pa'i
NK132(no)004:4249: ye shes ni rig stong gnyug ma bde ba chen
NK132(no)004:4250: po srid zhi kun khyab kyi ye shes yin kyang
NK132(no)004:4251: / de rgyud gzhan na sbas pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:4253: 'gyur bde dang stong rkyang sbyar ba'i 'dus byas kyi spyod yul zhig las /
NK132(no)004:4254: 'dus ma byas pa'i rang byung gi ye shes sam /
NK132(no)004:4255: skad cig ma'i cha las 'das pa'i 'gyur med kyi bde ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4256: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid zung 'jug don
NK132(no)004:4257: gyi lhan skyes ji bzhin gtan la dbab ma nus
NK132(no)004:4258: pa'i phyir / de dag dus kyi 'khor lor ma sbas kyang /
NK132(no)004:4259: da dung sngar gyi zhen pas ji zhin nges pa dkon la /
NK132(no)004:4260: dbang po gnyis sbyor gyi bde ba mi rtag pa 'gyur ba de yin /
NK132(no)004:4261: bde ba chen po mi 'gyur rtag pa yin zhes gsungs pa sogs sems 'grel skor gsum dang /
NK132(no)004:4262: grub pa sde bdun rdo rje'i do ha sogs na'ang de bzhin gsal mod /
NK132(no)004:4263: rdzogs chen lugs ltar man ngag gi ngo sprod thebs pas /
NK132(no)004:4264: sngags kyi bden pa dbyer med zung 'jug gi don slong ma nus na /
NK132(no)004:4265: gsal bde rig pa'i ye shes zhes smos pa na /
NK132(no)004:4266: de 'dra la rtag pa zhig ga la yod snyam du /
NK132(no)004:4267: 'dus byas bde ba dang 'dus ma byas stong rkyang
NK132(no)004:4268: gnyis lhan cig gsar du sbyar ba la lhan skyes
NK132(no)004:4270: rgyud dang man ngag gi dgongs pa sgra ji bzhin nges ma nus pa ni /
NK132(no)004:4271: so so'i yid 'jog gis dan dpang byed chog pa 'di byung bas /
NK132(no)004:4272: rnying ma'i lugs kyi rig stong dbyer med /
NK132(no)004:4274: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo'i bde gshegs snying po gdod
NK132(no)004:4275: nas rnam dag sku dang ye shes nyid dang 'du
NK132(no)004:4276: 'bral med pa rtag pa chen po ji bzhin 'dzin
NK132(no)004:4277: mi nus par dgongs pa can dang sgra ji bzhin
NK132(no)004:4278: min par 'dod pas byung ba yin no //
NK132(no)004:4279: de bzhin du bskyed rim gyi lta ba snang srid ye sangs rgyas pa'i tshul dang /
NK132(no)004:4280: thabs lam gyi rtsa ba lus thabs kyi rgyud yin
NK132(no)004:4281: pas de la gnad du bsnun na rang bzhin 'od
NK132(no)004:4283: mi shigs dwangs ma gsum ldan gyi thig le nyid
NK132(no)004:4284: 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i lhun grub kyi sku
NK132(no)004:4285: dang ye shes su khas len mi nus bzhin /
NK132(no)004:4286: dbu mar srog gzhug pa'i bdag byin rlabs kyi rim
NK132(no)004:4287: pa bsgom pas gzod zhig yid lha skur smin pa
NK132(no)004:4289: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo las lam lnga bral byed
NK132(no)004:4290: kyi rgyu dang 'bras bu chos sku bral 'bras su
NK132(no)004:4291: gsungs pa dang / ye shes rdo rje kun btus sogs sngags rgyud las kyang /
NK132(no)004:4292: 'od gsal ba'i sems gdod nas rnam dag la /
NK132(no)004:4293: sgrib byed glo bur gyi rlung rtog thabs kyis bkag pas /
NK132(no)004:4294: zung 'jug don gyi sangs rgyas bral 'bras dngos su gsungs pa yod bzhin /
NK132(no)004:4295: de dag gi dgongs don ji bzhin slong ma nus par /
NK132(no)004:4296: sangs rgyas kyi gnyug sems sam mi shigs pa'i thig le'am /
NK132(no)004:4297: gzugs sku'i nyer len gyi rgyu rlung 'od zer lnga pa sogs thabs kyis sbyang nas /
NK132(no)004:4298: gzod sangs rgyas su 'grub par smra ba'i gzhung 'dzug pa'i gnad de yin no //
NK132(no)004:4299: 'di dag snang tshul la de ltar brjod pa tsam la 'gal ba med mod /
NK132(no)004:4300: gnas tshul la'ang gdod nas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor
NK132(no)004:4301: sems can thams cad la chos nyid kyi ngo bor
NK132(no)004:4302: ye nas rang chas su med na /
NK132(no)004:4303: gnyug sems 'od gsal dang mi shigs pa'i thig le
NK132(no)004:4304: sogs kyang ma dag pa'i char gtogs par 'gyur na
NK132(no)004:4305: / thabs kyi lam gyis de la gnad du bsnun
NK132(no)004:4306: pa'ang don med par 'gyur ba sogs skyon mtha' yas
NK132(no)004:4307: / yod mod / nyung dur brjod pas the tshom
NK132(no)004:4308: chod dka' bas dpyad pa'i snying po tsam las ma
NK132(no)004:4309: / yod mod / smos so // gsar ma'i nang
NK132(no)004:4310: du'ang dus 'khor gyi man ngag la brten pa 'ga'
NK132(no)004:4311: zhig ni rnying ma'i khas len ltar /
NK132(no)004:4312: rang bzhin 'od gsal gyi sems sam bde gshegs snying
NK132(no)004:4313: po rdo rje can gyi sems ni sangs rgyas su
NK132(no)004:4314: zhal gyis bzhes pa yod do //
NK132(no)004:4315: lam de tshul bzhin sgom pa rnams la grub thob du ma byung ngo //
NK132(no)004:4316: 'on kyang rnying mas ngo bo stong par gtan la
NK132(no)004:4317: 'bebs pa sogs go bde zhing yid ches skye sla
NK132(no)004:4318: ba yod / des na chos kyi che ba 'di
NK132(no)004:4319: ni gzhan la med cing snga 'gyur gyi chos la
NK132(no)004:4321: bde gsang sogs sngags kyi dgongs pa ji bzhin bslang
NK132(no)004:4322: na ni 'di dag bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK132(no)004:4323: rgyud yin pas rgyud la bzang ngan med mod /
NK132(no)004:4324: man ngag gi gnad spangs pa'i rgyud 'dzin pa po
NK132(no)004:4325: rnams la ltos nas man ngag ma sbas pa'i rgyud
NK132(no)004:4326: rnams sbas pa rnams las ches che bar 'grub pa
NK132(no)004:4327: yin no // de'i phyir gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi
NK132(no)004:4328: chos sde rin po che rnams ni sa gsum na
NK132(no)004:4330: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i gter las kyang gces spras
NK132(no)004:4331: kyi sgo nas chos spyod bcu'i tshul gyis ji nus
NK132(no)004:4332: su 'dzin dgos pa yin pas gang zag skal pa
NK132(no)004:4333: rab tu gyur pa rnams kyis de ltar rtogs par
NK132(no)004:4334: 'tshal lo // rgyal bstan ljongs 'dir 'dren pa mes dbon gsum //
NK132(no)004:4335: bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan sgreng mdzad mkhan slob chos //
NK132(no)004:4336: bstan pa yun ring skyong ba bstan 'dzin tshogs //
NK132(no)004:4337: 'di dag bod na bka' drin 'gran zla bral //
NK132(no)004:4338: gangs ljongs smra ba'i sgo 'byed sam+b+ho ta //
NK132(no)004:4339: mdo sngags bstan pa'i snang byed ka cog zhang //
NK132(no)004:4340: bcu phrag rigs lam gsal byed mkhas dbang tshogs //
NK132(no)004:4341: 'di dag bod yul chos kyi nyi ma yin //
NK132(no)004:4342: de phyir mdo sngags rig gnas bcas pa yi //
NK132(no)004:4343: shing rta'i lam srol snga 'gyur pa yis phyes //
NK132(no)004:4344: de yi rtsa lag ris bral dam pas spel //
NK132(no)004:4345: deng sang bar du bstan pa'i mnga' thang rgyas //
NK132(no)004:4346: de lta na yang nu zhos 'grang ba yi //
NK132(no)004:4347: phru gu'i tshogs kyis ma la 'khu ba ltar //
NK132(no)004:4348: blo zhan byas pa mi gzo 'ga' zhig gis //
NK132(no)004:4349: rang che 'byin zhing bstan rnying dman par 'dzin //
NK132(no)004:4350: kye ma ho rgyal bstan chu gter zab mo'i klong brgal nas //
NK132(no)004:4351: mdo sngags rgyud sde'i chos kyi snying po ni //
NK132(no)004:4352: 'gran zla med pa'i mkhas grub mchog rnams kyi //
NK132(no)004:4353: drin las snga 'gyur pa la mchis mod kyi //
NK132(no)004:4354: so so'i grub matha'i zab gnad ma phig pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4355: blo chung rnams kyis bltas na rnying ma'i chos //
NK132(no)004:4356: phal dang mi 'dra sger chos mang ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:4357: yang dag yin min som nyi'i gzeb tu chud //
NK132(no)004:4358: rgya che'i chos mdzod rtogs shing zab mo'i gnad //
NK132(no)004:4359: khong du chud pa'i blo ldan 'gas bltas na //
NK132(no)004:4360: chos sgo grangs med kun gyi mthar thug gi //
NK132(no)004:4361: zab gnad mthong phyir kun gyi rtse mor mthong //
NK132(no)004:4362: legs par bsam na snga 'gyur dus kyi ni //
NK132(no)004:4363: bstan 'dzin rnams kyi bka' drin 'gran bral zhing //
NK132(no)004:4364: bstan pa rgya mtsho bsil ldan ljongs su khyab //
NK132(no)004:4365: bstan zhugs kun kyang de yi drin la brten //
NK132(no)004:4366: de lta mod kyi sde snod gsum gyi chos //
NK132(no)004:4367: snga 'gyur yin yang 'di la rtsod pa med //
NK132(no)004:4368: chos zab rdo rje theg pa nang rgyud gsum //
NK132(no)004:4369: 'phags yul phal la'ang yongs su ma grags mod //
NK132(no)004:4370: rgyal ba nyid dang mtshungs pa'i pan grub kyi //
NK132(no)004:4371: drin las gangs ljongs skal bar bzhag na yang //
NK132(no)004:4372: zab gnad mi shes phyogs re'i mig can gyis //
NK132(no)004:4373: 'di dag rnying ma'i chos zhes the tshom gyi //
NK132(no)004:4374: gzhi byas phrag dog tshig ngan bdud kyis bsgrags //
NK132(no)004:4375: nor bu'i gter chen rnying ma'i sger skal gyur //
NK132(no)004:4376: rdo rje theg pa'i dgongs don ches zab pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4377: dgongs pa dmar 'byin man ngag snying po'i gzhung //
NK132(no)004:4378: 'di rnams yin kyang skal pas ma chun pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4379: sngags 'dzin rnams la sa 'og gter bzhin gyur //
NK132(no)004:4380: yang dag lam bzang mthong ba'i shes rab can //
NK132(no)004:4381: yod na gsar rgyud rnams kyi dgongs pa'i mtha' //
NK132(no)004:4382: ji bzhin nges pa 'di la rag las te //
NK132(no)004:4383: rgyud las rgyud kyi man ngag lta bu yin //
NK132(no)004:4384: 'di dag so skye mkhas pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK132(no)004:4385: dpyad pas gsar du rnyed pa'i bstan bcos dang //
NK132(no)004:4386: rtog ge'i rang bzos bcos pa ma yin te //
NK132(no)004:4387: rgyal ba nyid kyis rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud //
NK132(no)004:4388: gzhan du sbas pa 'dir ni mngon bstan phyir //
NK132(no)004:4389: snyed daka'i chos mchog 'di rnams legs bzung na //
NK132(no)004:4390: zab cing rtogs par dka' ba yin mod kyis //
NK132(no)004:4391: rtogs na don che 'di dang mtshungs gzhan med //
NK132(no)004:4393: rtogs sla yin yin 'dra yang phug brtag na //
NK132(no)004:4394: byis pa mgu bar byed pa'i ngang tshul las //
NK132(no)004:4395: rigs khur mi bzod bye ma'i chang bu 'dra //
NK132(no)004:4396: mthar thug dpyod pa'i rigs pas grub pa yi //
NK132(no)004:4397: zab don rdo rje'i gsang gnad 'di dag la //
NK132(no)004:4398: nges pa skye na nam mkha' ji srid du //
NK132(no)004:4399: pha rol rgol bas nam yang bskyod mi nus //
NK132(no)004:4400: snga 'gyur chos mdzod nor bu'i gling skyes kyang //
NK132(no)004:4401: nor skal chad 'ga' gzhan zer 'ching bu len //
NK132(no)004:4402: rang gi chos la the tshom za byed pa //
NK132(no)004:4403: lha skal chad pas 'byung po sgrub dang mtshungs //
NK132(no)004:4404: kun rtog 'phel ba'i sna mang mi 'tshol zhing //
NK132(no)004:4405: brgyud pa'i man ngag bdud rtsi'i bcud mchog la //
NK132(no)004:4406: rang nus ji bzhin spyod pas ngom par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:4407: de ltar brjod pa 'di la gzhan dag gis //
NK132(no)004:4408: rang zhen rang bstod che ba yin snyam na //
NK132(no)004:4409: rton pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK132(no)004:4410: lta ba'i gnad dang nyams len man ngag gzhung //
NK132(no)004:4411: chos kyi chings dang bslu med rigs pa'i lam //
NK132(no)004:4412: thams cad ring mo zhig tu rtogs bgyis na //
NK132(no)004:4413: de nas the tshom mun pa dwangs pa yi //
NK132(no)004:4414: nges shes nyin mor byed pa bzhin du 'char //
NK132(no)004:4415: de ltar mthong nas snyigs ma lnga bdo'i dus //
NK132(no)004:4416: bstan zhabs skyes pa'i chos smra'i khur 'dzin bdag /
NK132(no)004:4417: rnam byang phyogs kyi yon tan ches phra zhing //
NK132(no)004:4418: las nyon sdug bsngal brgya yis mnar mod kyi //
NK132(no)004:4419: bstan pa 'di la gus pa rtse gcig pas //
NK132(no)004:4420: nam nam zhor zhor ji ltar 'bad pa yis //
NK132(no)004:4421: snga 'gyur bstan la ji phan brjod par byas //
NK132(no)004:4422: de dag pha yi kha phor gtsang zhen ltar //
NK132(no)004:4423: zhes pas ma yin nges pa skyes las yin //
NK132(no)004:4424: grub mtha' mi mthun gzhan la sdang ba yis //
NK132(no)004:4425: sun 'byin ma yin theg don gsal byed yin //
NK132(no)004:4426: de ltar rgyal ba nyid dang rgyal ba'i sras //
NK132(no)004:4427: dngos byon snga 'gyur dam pa mchog rnams la //
NK132(no)004:4428: bka' drin byas pa legs par gzo ba dang //
NK132(no)004:4429: theg mchog chos la gus ba bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)004:4430: chal chol smra ba'i nges pas tshe rabs brgyar //
NK132(no)004:4431: ro 'dzin ral gris 'thag pa'i las ngan khur //
NK132(no)004:4432: mi len chos mchog smra ba pad+ma'i ljags //
NK132(no)004:4433: skye ba kun thob snyam du spro ba skyes //
NK132(no)004:4434: 'on kyang bdag 'dra so skye dman pa yi //
NK132(no)004:4435: blo yi nus pas zab don ma rtogs nas //
NK132(no)004:4436: cung zad nyes par bshad pa mchis srid na //
NK132(no)004:4437: rtsa gsum lha dang srung ma'i tshogs la bshags //
NK132(no)004:4438: dad pa'i sems dang brgyud pa'i man ngag mthus //
NK132(no)004:4439: ma nor legs par bshad pa'i cha gang mchis //
NK132(no)004:4440: de yi dge bas skye ba thams cad kun //
NK132(no)004:4441: zab don rdo rje'i gsungs la dad gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:4442: ma 'ongs snga 'gyur bstan zhabs skye rnams kyang //
NK132(no)004:4443: brgyud pa'i man ngag ldan byas rang lugs kyi //
NK132(no)004:4444: khas len rnams las cung zad mi 'da' bar //
NK132(no)004:4445: dad cing spro ba'i sems kyis bzung byas na //
NK132(no)004:4446: dam pa rnams kyi thugs rjes yongs 'dzin zhing //
NK132(no)004:4447: tshe rabs kun tu theg mchog chos kyis 'byor //
NK132(no)004:4448: smra ba rab yangs pad+ma'i ljags thob nas //
NK132(no)004:4449: rgyal ba'i chos mdzod smra ba'i dbang por 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:4450: zhes tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs dang bcas te smras so ////
NK132(no)004:4451: de rnams kyis rtsa ba'i dang po spyi don gyi lus rnam par bzhag pa song nas /
NK132(no)004:4452: gnyis pa tshig don dngos bshad pa la /
NK132(no)004:4453: klad gzhung mjug gi don gsum las /
NK132(no)004:4456: dgos pa brjod nas smon lam ji ltar gdab pa'i tshul lo //
NK132(no)004:4458: snga 'gyur bstan pa rgyas pa'i sogs te /
NK132(no)004:4459: de yang bstan bcos kyi dbur mtshan btags pa'i dgos pa sogs spyi ltar nges par byas nas /
NK132(no)004:4460: bye brag tshig don dngos la /
NK132(no)004:4461: gsang chen bla na med pa snga 'gyura rdo rje
NK132(no)004:4462: theg pa zab mo nang rgyud sde gsum gtso bor
NK132(no)004:4463: gyur pa'i mdo sngags kyi bstan pa rin po che
NK132(no)004:4464: gong nas gong du 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i thabs su
NK132(no)004:4465: g.yo zol med pa'i lhag pa'i bsam pas smon lam
NK132(no)004:4466: du bgyis pa / brjod pa'i don phun sum tshogs
NK132(no)004:4467: pa chosa kyi rgyal po mkhan slob chos gsum sprul
NK132(no)004:4468: pa'i lo pan sogs sras bcas rgyal ba dgyes pa'i
NK132(no)004:4469: zhala lunga dri ma med pa nyid 'dir sgro skur
NK132(no)004:4470: dang bral bar bsdebs pas na de skad zhesa bya
NK132(no)004:4471: du bgyis pa / ba'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK132(no)004:4472: de yang dus kyi sog ste /
NK132(no)004:4473: de yanga skal bzang rnams kyi snying la brnag par
NK132(no)004:4474: bya ba ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po
NK132(no)004:4476: snyigs ma lnga bdo ba'i dus kyi tha mara dam
NK132(no)004:4477: pa'i chos rab tu 'jig pa la phyogs pa'i skabs
NK132(no)004:4478: 'dir rang stobs kyis brtson pas 'dzin pa'am /
NK132(no)004:4479: min kyang rtsa gsum rab 'byams lhag pa'i lha'i thugsa dam gyi rgyud bskul nasa /
NK132(no)004:4480: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i snying po dus gsum du
NK132(no)004:4481: 'byung bar dka' ba yid bzhin gyi nor bu riina
NK132(no)004:4483: phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du dar zhing rgyas
NK132(no)004:4484: la yun du gnas para gyur ciga snyam du dus
NK132(no)004:4485: lan gciga tsam du mosa pa skye na yanga /
NK132(no)004:4486: bsoda namas tshad med pa dang ldan zhing rgyal ba'i sras kyi smon lam gyi gtso bo ni /
NK132(no)004:4487: zhing kun tu sangs rgyas kyi chos 'dzin pa dang
NK132(no)004:4488: de gzhan la ston pa'i sgo nas sems can rgya
NK132(no)004:4489: mtsho yongs su smin par byed pa nyid yin na
NK132(no)004:4491: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rab 'byams rnams su skye ba
NK132(no)004:4492: 'dzin zhing tshe rabs kun tu bdud bzhi'i dgra las
NK132(no)004:4493: rgyal ba'i sangs rgyas kyi chosa ji snyed pa dang
NK132(no)004:4494: / khyad par chosa kyi snying poo nges don zab mo'i thega pa rnams dang 'phrada nasa /
NK132(no)004:4495: don la mi 'jigs pa'i spobs pa thob ste /
NK132(no)004:4496: 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum gyi sgo nas 'dzin skyong speela basa sangs rgyas kyi chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4497: des sems can rgya mtsho yongs su smin par byas nas /
NK132(no)004:4498: dus ring por mi thogs par myur du sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:4499: kyi rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shesa la
NK132(no)004:4500: rega para 'gyur ba'i dgosa pa yoda de /
NK132(no)004:4501: 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnams grangs las /
NK132(no)004:4503: theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pas /
NK132(no)004:4504: 'di lta bu'i mi bzad pa dang mi basngagasa pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4505: dam pa'i chos rab tu 'jig pa mthong nas brtson 'grus chen po'i shugs rab tu bskyed de /
NK132(no)004:4507: 'di lta bu'i mdo sde byang chub sems dpa'i sde
NK132(no)004:4508: snod kyi chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rab tu mnyan
NK132(no)004:4510: yi ger bris nas bcang bar bya /
NK132(no)004:4511: gzhan la yang go bar bya /
NK132(no)004:4512: rgya cher yang dag par rab tu bstan par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:4513: des kyang 'du shes bzhi bzhi bskyed par bya ste /
NK132(no)004:4515: bdag gi pha yi nor gyi phung po 'di rab tu 'jig par 'gyur te /
NK132(no)004:4516: gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
NK132(no)004:4517: dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:4518: sh+aakya thub pa des bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig
NK132(no)004:4519: brgya stong dpag tu med pa nas bzung ste dka'
NK132(no)004:4521: de'i phyir rab tu 'jig par mi 'gyur bar bzung bar bya /
NK132(no)004:4523: bzung bar bya ste chud mi za bar bya'o //
NK132(no)004:4527: skyes bu zhig la bu gcig yod de /
NK132(no)004:4528: byams sdug yid du 'ong zhing mi mthun pa med
NK132(no)004:4529: par snang ba de g.yang sa chen por zhugs pa
NK132(no)004:4530: na / des de lag gis bzung ste sems can
NK132(no)004:4531: dmyal ba'i g.yang sa 'dir lhung bar ma gyur cig
NK132(no)004:4532: ces gces 'dzin rab tu 'dzin pa de bzhin du
NK132(no)004:4534: gang skyes bu dam pa de dag nga la dad
NK132(no)004:4535: cing dkon mchog bla na med pa 'di yang yongs
NK132(no)004:4537: mya ngan las 'das pa la yang re bar 'gyur
NK132(no)004:4538: ba de dag de'i dus na dam pa'i chos yongs
NK132(no)004:4540: ngas de dag la byang chub mchog 'di gtad par bya'o //
NK132(no)004:4541: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4542: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:4543: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa //
NK132(no)004:4544: de ni de bzhin gshegs la byas gzo yin //
NK132(no)004:4545: rgyal ba rnams kyi mdzod 'dzin yid brtan zhing //
NK132(no)004:4546: phyogs bcu rnams su sangs rgyas mchod pa yin //
NK132(no)004:4547: sangs rgyas spyan gyis gzigs pa'i zhing mang po //
NK132(no)004:4548: rin chen bkang ste de bzhin gshegs la phul //
NK132(no)004:4549: zad pa'i dus ni ji ltar chos 'dzin ltar //
NK132(no)004:4550: bsod nams phung po de tsam 'phel ma yin //
NK132(no)004:4552: nam mkha' mdzod kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)004:4553: ji ltar bskal pa bye ba stong brjod kyang //
NK132(no)004:4554: sangs rgyas ye shes mtha' yod ma yin ltar //
NK132(no)004:4555: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4556: bsod nams de yang tshad yod ma yin no //
NK132(no)004:4559: rgyal ba rnams kyis dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK132(no)004:4560: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK132(no)004:4561: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyong ba yang //
NK132(no)004:4562: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par bgyi //
NK132(no)004:4564: lan gcig tsam yang dad pa skyed pa na /
NK132(no)004:4565: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)004:4567: bdag legs su 'dod pa'i skala bazanga rnamas kyis rgyu
NK132(no)004:4568: mtshan shes pa'i sgo nas dus dang dus min rtag
NK132(no)004:4570: khyad para tshogas manga gi skabas sogs su stobs che
NK132(no)004:4571: bas tshig 'di ltar smon lam du gadba para bya
NK132(no)004:4573: gnyis pa gzhung don dngos 'chad pa la /
NK132(no)004:4574: dkon mchog rtsa gsum gyi thugs rgyud bskul ba'i smon lam dang /
NK132(no)004:4575: bstan pa'i che ba brjod pa'i smom lam gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:4581: phyogs bcu'i sogs tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK132(no)004:4582: de la na mo ni phyag 'tshal ba ste /
NK132(no)004:4583: gang na 'chad 'gyur ltar bla ma rgyal ba sras bcas rtsa gsum gyi lha la /
NK132(no)004:4584: gang gis na thog mar gzhung rtsom pa po dang /
NK132(no)004:4585: skabs thob smon lam 'debs po rang gis /
NK132(no)004:4586: tshul ji ltar na rang rang gi blo tshod dang mthun pas te /
NK132(no)004:4587: thun mong du sgo gsum gus pas so //
NK132(no)004:4588: de ltar phyag 'tshal bas bsod nams kyi tshogs 'phel
NK132(no)004:4589: bas ji ltar smon pa sogs bsam pa thams cad
NK132(no)004:4592: bsod nams ldan pa'i mi yi bsam pa rnams kyang 'grub //
NK132(no)004:4594: dgos pa de ldan gyi phyag 'tshal ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK132(no)004:4595: steng 'og la sogs pa'i phyogsa bcu'i zhing rab 'byams
NK132(no)004:4596: na bzhugs pa'i don gnyis mthar phyin pa'i sar bde
NK132(no)004:4597: bar gshegas pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das dang /
NK132(no)004:4598: sras byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa nyan thos dang
NK132(no)004:4599: rang sangs rgyas bden tshig grub pa'i drang srong rig
NK132(no)004:4600: pa 'dzin pa'i tshogas dang bacasa pa rnams dang /
NK132(no)004:4601: khyad para du snyigs ma'i 'gro la thugs bskyed pad
NK132(no)004:4602: dkar ltar basngagasa pa mnyam med sh+aakya'i rgyal po dang
NK132(no)004:4603: / des bstan pa gang la gtad pa'i 'jam dpal
NK132(no)004:4604: dang spyan ras gzigs sogs rgyal srasa chen po brgyad
NK132(no)004:4605: dang sprul pa'i nyan thos chen po yan lag 'byung
NK132(no)004:4606: ba sogs gansa brtan chen po bcu drug 'khor dgra
NK132(no)004:4608: tshangs pa dang brgya byin rgyal po chen po bzhi
NK132(no)004:4609: la sogs dkar phyogs skyong ba'i dge bsnyen chen po
NK132(no)004:4610: rnams dang / gzhan yang mkhyen brtse'i badga nyid 'gro
NK132(no)004:4611: ba skyob pa'i mgon dang dpung gnyen mchoga tu gyur
NK132(no)004:4612: pa rnams deng 'dir thugs brtse bas dgongas su gsola
NK132(no)004:4613: rnams dang / / de ltar dgongs gsol brjod pas
NK132(no)004:4614: dngos su byon nas bzhugs shing ji ltar smon pa'i
NK132(no)004:4616: 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan bkod pa las /
NK132(no)004:4617: chos rnams thams cad rkyen bzhin te //
NK132(no)004:4618: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK132(no)004:4619: gang gis smon lam ci btab pa //
NK132(no)004:4621: gang zhig sangs rgyas yid byed pa //
NK132(no)004:4622: de yi mdun na de bzhugs te //
NK132(no)004:4623: rtag par byin gyis rlob byed cing //
NK132(no)004:4624: nyes pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK132(no)004:4626: tshul khrims ldan pas smon pa 'grub //
NK132(no)004:4628: de ltar mkhyen par gsol nas /
NK132(no)004:4629: gang smon lam du bya ba /
NK132(no)004:4630: rang gzhan gyi gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phana
NK132(no)004:4631: bde'i 'byunga gnas gcig pur gyur pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)004:4632: bstan pa rina po che ste /
NK132(no)004:4633: mdo sde rnams nas rgya cher gsungs pa bzhin sngon
NK132(no)004:4634: slob lam du ston pa mchog dang rgyal sras byang
NK132(no)004:4635: chub semas dapa'a 'aphagas pa mchoga gzhan rnams kyis kyang
NK132(no)004:4636: sku srog phang med du btang nas yanga dang yanga
NK132(no)004:4637: du daka'a basa batsala zhing thugs la brnag pa'i dona
NK132(no)004:4638: / 'chad 'gyur ltar mdo sngags kyi lus rdzogs shing che yon dpag med dang ldan pa /
NK132(no)004:4639: rang byung sprul sku 'chi med rdo rje'i sku brnyes
NK132(no)004:4640: pa mtsho skyes rgyal ba gnyis pa'i bstan pa snga
NK132(no)004:4641: 'gyur gyi ring lugs 'khrul pa'i dri ma dang bral
NK132(no)004:4642: ba nyid phyogs dus gnas skabs kun tu dar zhing
NK132(no)004:4643: rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4644: de de bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu
NK132(no)004:4645: gsol snyam du snying thag pa nas smon pa ste
NK132(no)004:4646: / tshig 'og ma'i don phyi ma kun la sbyor bar bya'o //
NK132(no)004:4648: mkhan slob chos rgyal sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK132(no)004:4649: de yang sngon gyi thugs bskyed kyi rgyu las gangs
NK132(no)004:4650: can pa rnams la sangs rgyas las kyang bka' drin
NK132(no)004:4651: che ba makhana sloba cho rgyal bi ma bee ro
NK132(no)004:4652: sogs sprul pa'i lo pan gyis tshogs rnams dang /
NK132(no)004:4653: brgyud pa gsum mam drug dang ldan pa'i bka'a gtera
NK132(no)004:4654: gyi riga 'dzina brgyud pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams
NK132(no)004:4655: dang yi dama rgyud sde bzhi drug gi lha tshogs
NK132(no)004:4656: gnas gsum gyi dpa' bo dang mkha' 'gro /
NK132(no)004:4657: ma mgona gaza'a rdor sogs ye shes dbyings kyi dal mthong zhing /
NK132(no)004:4658: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srung bar zhal gyis bzhes
NK132(no)004:4659: pa'i rgyud gsuma dam can dregas pa'i sde tshogas dang
NK132(no)004:4660: bcas pa ste / snga 'gyur rtsa ba gsuma gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogas rnams dgongas su gsola /
NK132(no)004:4661: thuba pa'i bstan pa mdo sde snod gsum dang sngagas
NK132(no)004:4662: rgyud sde bzhi sogs kyi theg pa rim dgu'i chos
NK132(no)004:4663: tshul matha'a daga / thugs bskyed brtson pa chen pos
NK132(no)004:4664: gangas can gyi ljongsa su thugs brtse basa drangas zin
NK132(no)004:4666: chesa chera spel ba'i rdo rje'i dama tshig gnyan po rjes su dgongas nasa /
NK132(no)004:4667: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas par mdzod cig pa'am gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4668: gnyis pa bstan pa'i che ba brjod pa la /
NK132(no)004:4669: nyams su len bya bstan pa dam chos kyi che ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4670: ji ltar nyams su len cing 'dzin tshul gyi che ba gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:4672: sgyur byed lo pan gyi che ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4673: bsgyur bya chos kyi che ba gnyis /
NK132(no)004:4675: phyogs dus rgyal ba'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK132(no)004:4676: de yang phyogsa bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i sku gsunga thugsa rdo rje yi rang gzugs /
NK132(no)004:4677: rgyal sras 'phags pa rigas gsuma semas dpa'i sgyu 'phrula rdo rje'i rola mo'am rol gar te /
NK132(no)004:4680: 'jam dpal sprul pa'i chos rgyal chen po yisa /
NK132(no)004:4681: sngon gyi thugs bskyed btsan po gser gyi shing rtas /
NK132(no)004:4682: bod gangas can pa'i gdul bya'i bsod nams kyi mkha' la /
NK132(no)004:4683: phana bde'i 'od zer stong phrag 'phro ba'i rgyal bstan
NK132(no)004:4684: gyi nyi ma gasla bar 'dren par madzada pa yi
NK132(no)004:4685: / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:4686: de bzhin du sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad sogs
NK132(no)004:4687: rgyal dang rgyal sras 'aphagas pa chen poo'i tshogas rnams
NK132(no)004:4688: kyang / bod yul du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa spel ba'i phyir bsam bzhin du /
NK132(no)004:4689: bee ro ska cog nam snying sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4690: 'phags yul gyi pan grub chen po rnams kyi zlos gara te skye srid nye bar bzunga nasa /
NK132(no)004:4691: nyes skyon gyi dri mas bslad pa meda pa'i rgyal
NK132(no)004:4692: bstan lung rtogs bshad sgrub kyi nora bu'i rgyal matshana
NK132(no)004:4694: srid zhi'i dbul ba sel zhing don gnyis kyi 'dod
NK132(no)004:4695: rgu'i char gdul bya'i skal ba dang 'tshams par 'bab
NK132(no)004:4696: pa yi / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4697: de yang thun monga ba sgra tshad bzo gso sogs rig pa'i gnas dang /
NK132(no)004:4698: thun mina gsung rab mdo sde snod gsum /
NK132(no)004:4699: sngags rgyud sde drug sogs mtha' drug dang tshul bzhis bcing ba /
NK132(no)004:4700: grub pa thob pa dang 'phags pa'i spyod yul la /
NK132(no)004:4701: so skye'i blos phigs par dka' ba'i gzhunga dang man ngag zab mo kuna kyang /
NK132(no)004:4702: sangs rgyas dngos dang 'dra ba'i sprul pa'i lo pan rnams zhal 'dzom pas /
NK132(no)004:4703: de dag nges pa'i tshig dang /
NK132(no)004:4704: brjod bya'i don sogs so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi la dbang 'byor ba'i stobs kyis /
NK132(no)004:4705: gzhan la ltos pa med par ranga dabnga gisa /
NK132(no)004:4706: tshig don gnyis ka ma nora ba ste tshig la lhag chad dang /
NK132(no)004:4707: don la nor 'khrul med pa thog mar bsgyur /
NK132(no)004:4708: bar du skad gsar bcad sogs kyis bcos shing zhus te le'u dang bam po tshun gyi tshad bzung /
NK132(no)004:4709: mthar nyan bshad dang sgom sgrub kyis gtan la phabas pa yisa /
NK132(no)004:4710: bod gangas can gyi ljongsa su dam pa'i chos kyi
NK132(no)004:4711: snang ba'i sgo chena po thoga mara phyes pa yi
NK132(no)004:4712: / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che de nyid rgyas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4713: gnyis pa bsgyur bya chos kyi che ba la /
NK132(no)004:4714: rgya che ba bstan pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i che ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4715: zab pa bstan pa'i snying po dang ldan pa'i che ba gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:4717: gzhung bka' dang dgongs 'grel tshang ba'i che ba /
NK132(no)004:4718: bka' gter mdo sngags zung 'brel gyi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4719: lta spyod rmad byung zung 'brel gyi che ba'o //
NK132(no)004:4721: skal bzang gdul byas sogs te /
NK132(no)004:4722: de yang sngon bsags kyi skal pa bazanga po dang
NK132(no)004:4723: ldan pa'i rjes 'jug gi gdula byas rang rang gi
NK132(no)004:4724: skal ba dang 'tshams par theg pa che chung gi
NK132(no)004:4725: mdo dang 'bras bu sngagsa kyi tshul phyi nang rnams
NK132(no)004:4726: / rang rang gang 'dod pa de nyid nyamsa su
NK132(no)004:4727: leen pa la gazhana gyi dringa la mi 'joga pa
NK132(no)004:4728: ste gzhan la ltos mi dgos para /
NK132(no)004:4729: legs par gsungs pa'i bka'a dang /
NK132(no)004:4730: de'i dgongas pa shing rta chen po rnams kyis ji
NK132(no)004:4731: ltar bkral ba'am 'grela pa'i gzhunga gdams ngag zab mo
NK132(no)004:4732: dang bcas pa kun te lam gyi lus yongs su
NK132(no)004:4733: rdzogsa pa / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4735: bden gsungs bka' yi sogs te /
NK132(no)004:4736: gnyis su med par bdena par gsungsa pa ni sangs
NK132(no)004:4737: rgyas nyid yin pas des gsungs pa'i bka'a yi rgya
NK132(no)004:4738: mtsho chen po zab cing gting dpag dka' ba'i ring
NK132(no)004:4739: brgyud kyi chu bo ma chad pa la /
NK132(no)004:4740: dam nyams dang rtog ges bslad gzhug tu med par /
NK132(no)004:4743: dbyings kyi mkha' 'gros rgyas btab pa /
NK132(no)004:4744: dus su bab pa na gdul bya'i snod dang 'tshams
NK132(no)004:4745: par 'byung bas byin rlabs kyi tshan kha gzhan las
NK132(no)004:4746: myur ba'i nye rgyud zaba mo'i chosa gtera yid bzhin
NK132(no)004:4747: gyi nora busa mngona para mdzesa shing /
NK132(no)004:4748: rgyu phar phyin sogs mtshan nyid theg pa'i mdo dang /
NK132(no)004:4749: 'bras bu gsang chen nges pa sngagas kyi lam srol bazanga po gnyis /
NK132(no)004:4750: gang zag gcig sangs rgyas pa'i lam gyi cha rkyen
NK132(no)004:4751: du khyer shes pas de gnyis 'gal med zunga du
NK132(no)004:4753: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4755: rmad byung za hor sogs te /
NK132(no)004:4756: de yang rmad byung za hor makhana po'i spyod pa
NK132(no)004:4757: ni nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde pa bzhi'i nang nas
NK132(no)004:4758: / gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i lugs ltar
NK132(no)004:4759: phyi 'dul ba so thar gyi lag len dang kun
NK132(no)004:4760: spyod rnam par dag pa'i ngang /
NK132(no)004:4761: nang byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas /
NK132(no)004:4762: spyod pa pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang 'brel ba ste /
NK132(no)004:4763: de dang sangs rgyas kyis lung bstan pa'i skyes chen
NK132(no)004:4764: mtshungsa pa meda pa dapala ldan klu yi lta ba
NK132(no)004:4765: ste gnyis po / lta spyod zunga du 'brela dgos
NK132(no)004:4766: par brgyud pa'i bka'a srol 'di nyid du bka' gtsigs
NK132(no)004:4767: kyi phyag rgyas bataba pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:4768: de'ang ha shang sun phyung ba'i rjes su rgyal po'i bkas bcad de /
NK132(no)004:4769: lta ba klu sgrub kyi lugs /
NK132(no)004:4771: nyams len rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la brten par gnang /
NK132(no)004:4772: bla med kyi rgyud rnams ches gnyan zhing gsang ba
NK132(no)004:4773: srung ba la thugs goms pas de dus khyab brdal
NK132(no)004:4774: du spyod du med pas dngos su ma gsungs par
NK132(no)004:4776: de yang dpal ldan klu'i lta ba ni /
NK132(no)004:4777: bdag nyid chen po 'di nyid kyis bka' 'khor gsum gyi dgongs 'grel du /
NK132(no)004:4780: bstod tshogs te tshogs gsum mdzad pa las /
NK132(no)004:4781: phyi ma gnyis kyi nges don zab gnad gcig par
NK132(no)004:4782: snang stong gang gi'ang phyogs su ma lhung ba'i zung
NK132(no)004:4784: ye nas dag pa'i chos nyid spros mtha' kun bral /
NK132(no)004:4785: sgro 'dogs som nyi dang bral ba'i chos kyi dbyings /
NK132(no)004:4786: srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa /
NK132(no)004:4787: ngo bo rnam thar gsum ldan /
NK132(no)004:4788: stong cha nas chos sku dang snang cha nas gzugs
NK132(no)004:4789: sku sogs zag med dbyings kyi yon tan rnams dang
NK132(no)004:4791: smra bsam brjod med blo 'das kyi ye shes /
NK132(no)004:4792: 'phags pa rnams kyi so so rang rig pa'i spyod
NK132(no)004:4793: yul du gyur pa'i theg mchog 'bras bu'i dbu ma
NK132(no)004:4794: chen po'i don nyid rtogs na rtag chad sogs mthar
NK132(no)004:4795: 'dzin gyi 'ching ba thams cad gcod nus pas na
NK132(no)004:4797: de las gzhan du de gnyis 'gal bar bzung nas /
NK132(no)004:4798: snang stong gang rung re'i mtha' la zhen nas /
NK132(no)004:4799: rang rang gi zhe 'dod dang mthun par dgag sgrub
NK132(no)004:4800: kyi ca co sgrog pa ni dbu ma'i lam ma
NK132(no)004:4801: yin te / de tsam gyis spros pa'i mtha' kun
NK132(no)004:4802: khegs mi nus shing byis pa rtog ge'i las kyang
NK132(no)004:4804: des na bden pa gnyis kyang /
NK132(no)004:4805: shes bya yul gyi sgo nas snang stong ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad dang /
NK132(no)004:4806: shes byed yul can gyi mthong tshul la rtog tshul
NK132(no)004:4807: nas gcig pa bkag pa'i tha dad lta bur don
NK132(no)004:4808: gyis 'gyur na'ang / mthar thug don dam pa'i ngos
NK132(no)004:4809: na de gnyis ka'ang dbye gzhi zad pa'i dbyer med
NK132(no)004:4810: rnam dag chen por shes dgos te /
NK132(no)004:4811: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK132(no)004:4812: kun rdzob rnam chad rnam dbye'i yul 'das pas //
NK132(no)004:4813: btags pa'i bden gnyis 'das phyir spros kun zhi //
NK132(no)004:4814: bden pa dbyer med grub dang ma grub med //
NK132(no)004:4815: dbyings la snang stong rang bzhin gnyis med pas //
NK132(no)004:4816: bden pa de yang dbyer med ces brjod do //
NK132(no)004:4818: tha snyad du dag ma dag gnyis chos 'gal bas 'drer med pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:4819: ma 'dres pa la dbyer med pas kyang rang bzhin rnam dag tu grub pa yin no //
NK132(no)004:4820: de ltar bshad na rgyud bla sogs byams gzhung dang /
NK132(no)004:4821: shing rta chen po thogs med kyi bzhed pa'ang 'di
NK132(no)004:4822: dang phan tshun sbrang rtsi'i ro gzugs bzhin 'gal med
NK132(no)004:4823: du 'gyur bas don chen po dang ldan pa yin
NK132(no)004:4824: te / rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang pos mdzad
NK132(no)004:4825: pa'i theg pa'i rnam dbye gsal bar byed pa'i gtam
NK132(no)004:4826: te / las / dpal ldan n+aa gardzu na yis //
NK132(no)004:4827: thal 'gyur grub matha'i rgyal rnga che //
NK132(no)004:4828: srid rtse'i bar du brdung ba las //
NK132(no)004:4829: bden pa gnyis kyi rnam bzhag kyang //
NK132(no)004:4830: 'phags dang so skye'i ngo skal te //
NK132(no)004:4831: dper na gnyis kyi mthus bskyed pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4832: rmi lam sad tshe med bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:4833: sngar smos gtan tshig de rnams kyis //
NK132(no)004:4834: gzhan sel skye ba med sgrub kyang //
NK132(no)004:4835: don du de yang sgyu ma bzhin //
NK132(no)004:4836: bden zhen nyid du khas ma blang //
NK132(no)004:4837: de phyir khas len bral ba ni //
NK132(no)004:4838: lta ba'i mthar thug nyid du 'jog /
NK132(no)004:4839: gzhan yang rigs gzhung cher smra dang //
NK132(no)004:4840: gzhan gyi rtsod ngor basngagasa pa ni //
NK132(no)004:4841: thal 'gyur nyid do rtse gcig tu //
NK132(no)004:4842: mnyam par bzhag pa'i rnal 'byor don //
NK132(no)004:4843: phra ba nang gi dbu ma'ang bstan //
NK132(no)004:4844: de yi chos rnams kun brtags dang //
NK132(no)004:4845: gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum du bstan //
NK132(no)004:4846: so sor gnyis re dbye bas drug /
NK132(no)004:4847: sbyong gzhi bde gshegs snying po ni //
NK132(no)004:4848: snang chas gzugs sku stong cha yis //
NK132(no)004:4849: chos sku'i yon tan lhun gyis grub //
NK132(no)004:4850: de la kun tu brtags pa dang //
NK132(no)004:4851: gzhan dbang rim gyis sbyangs pa las //
NK132(no)004:4852: mthar thug gzhi nyid mngon gyur par //
NK132(no)004:4853: sems can byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK132(no)004:4854: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes su 'dod //
NK132(no)004:4855: gter dang 'bras bu'i shing bzhin du //
NK132(no)004:4856: gnas lugs nyid dang rgyas 'gyur gyi //
NK132(no)004:4857: rigs de rnams gnyis rdzogs pa'i mod //
NK132(no)004:4858: bla med snying por gshegs par nges //
NK132(no)004:4859: 'di ni sa bcu'i dbang phyug mchog /
NK132(no)004:4860: rgyal tshab ma pham pa yis bzhed //
NK132(no)004:4861: tshul der phyogs snga smra ba rnams //
NK132(no)004:4862: yid srubs mthu yis sgrib par nges //
NK132(no)004:4863: ci phyir shing rta chen po gnyis //
NK132(no)004:4864: dgongs don mthar thug gcig bsdus gang //
NK132(no)004:4865: 'phags bod mkhas pa'i rnam dpyod kyis //
NK132(no)004:4866: 'chad rtsod rtsom pas gsal mdzad cing //
NK132(no)004:4867: nang gi rnal 'byor che brnyes pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4868: grub mchog kun kyang 'di bzhed do //
NK132(no)004:4869: gzhan yang 'khor lo dang po yis //
NK132(no)004:4870: bsod nams ma yin las ldog pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4871: gtam gyis nyan rang theg pa bstan //
NK132(no)004:4872: bar pas bdag las ldog byas te //
NK132(no)004:4873: bdag med dbu ma'i lam bzang 'chad //
NK132(no)004:4874: tha mas lta gzhi kun spangs nas //
NK132(no)004:4875: nges don snying po'i sgra chen bsgrags //
NK132(no)004:4877: der ma zad 'di nyid gzhir bzhag gis sngags kyi gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud du bzhag pa'i skabs su'ang /
NK132(no)004:4878: ngo bo'i gzhi dang btags pa'i gzhi gnyis su dbye ba dang /
NK132(no)004:4879: gzhan yang bya spyod kyi de kho na nyid sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:4882: a ti'i rang byung ye shes /
NK132(no)004:4883: mthar phyin rdzogs chen gyi gzhi ka dag lhun grub
NK132(no)004:4884: zung 'jug sogs kyang 'di las gzhan du ma gyur
NK132(no)004:4885: ba'i phyir / mdo sngags kyi zab gnad thams cad
NK132(no)004:4886: bsdus nas nyams su len shes pa sogs dgos pa
NK132(no)004:4888: mdor na sngags kyi lta ba mthar thug snang srid
NK132(no)004:4889: ye sangs rgyas pa'i don gyi gnad kyang 'di la
NK132(no)004:4891: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK132(no)004:4892: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK132(no)004:4895: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK132(no)004:4896: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa //
NK132(no)004:4898: pad+ma'i lam rim chen mo las /
NK132(no)004:4899: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i gnas lugs ni rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK132(no)004:4900: gnyis chos 'khrul pa sangs la gnyis med ye shes rgyas pas sangs rgyas so //
NK132(no)004:4901: de yang 'khrul pa yod pa gcig med par sangs
NK132(no)004:4902: nas gnyis med ye shes med pa gcig yod par
NK132(no)004:4904: gshis la 'khrul pa ma grub cing ngo bo gnyis
NK132(no)004:4905: med ye shes su rgyas pas ye nas sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:4906: pa yin te / rang bzhin stong pa chos sku /
NK132(no)004:4907: rang mdangs gsal ba longs sku /
NK132(no)004:4908: gsal stong gnyis med sprul sku /
NK132(no)004:4909: rang bzhin stong pa ji lta ba /
NK132(no)004:4910: rang mdangs gsal ba ji snyed pa /
NK132(no)004:4911: gsal stong gnyis med dam dbyer med de mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK132(no)004:4912: gshis la 'khrul pa med pas spangs pa phun tshogs /
NK132(no)004:4913: ngo bo gnyis med yod pa rtogs pa phun tshogs /
NK132(no)004:4914: de ltar ye nas sangs rgyas ma yin na bsgoms kyang sangs rgyas su mi 'gyur te /
NK132(no)004:4915: sa le sbram ye nas gser ma yin na byas kyang gser du mi 'gro ba bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:4916: zhes gsungs pa sogs bstod tshogs kyi dgongs pa dang sgra ji bzhin par 'byor ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:4917: snga 'gyur gyi lo pan skyes mchog rnams dang /
NK132(no)004:4918: phyis dus kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK132(no)004:4919: rje smin gling pa sku mched /
NK132(no)004:4920: chos rje kahthoga pa yab sras brgyud par bcas pas
NK132(no)004:4921: mtshon snga 'gyur zol med kyi ring lugs 'dzin pa
NK132(no)004:4922: kun gyis grub matha'i zhal bzhes 'di bzhin mdzad pa
NK132(no)004:4923: 'ba' zhig ste so so'i gsung rab kyis dbang por
NK132(no)004:4925: zhib par rang lugs kyi grub matha'i khas len dang
NK132(no)004:4926: lung rigs kyi rtsod spong sogs ni kun mkhyen bla
NK132(no)004:4927: ma 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i gsung rab las shes par
NK132(no)004:4929: 'di dang mnyam pa ni rang gzhan gyi phyogs gang na'ang mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)004:4930: de lta bu'i lta spyod ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i /
NK132(no)004:4931: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4932: gnyis pa zab pa bstan pa'i snying po dang ldan pa'i che ba la /
NK132(no)004:4936: nyams su blang bya chos kyi che ba /
NK132(no)004:4937: de la bslad ma zhugs pa'i che ba /
NK132(no)004:4938: zab mo de lta bu gzhan med pa'i che ba bstan pa gsum /
NK132(no)004:4940: rgya che ba rgyud sde dbang du byas pa dang /
NK132(no)004:4941: zab mo sgrub sde'i dbang du byas pa gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:4943: zab mo nang rgyud sogs te /
NK132(no)004:4944: de yang thog ma'i 'jug sgo dbang thob cing dam tshig la gnas pa gal che bas /
NK132(no)004:4945: lta dgongs dang ldan pa'i bla mas snod ldan gyi
NK132(no)004:4946: slob bu'i rgyud kyi rtsa rlung thig le sems dang
NK132(no)004:4947: bcas pa ste / gnyug ma'i sgo gsum ye nas
NK132(no)004:4948: rdo rje'i bzhi'i ngo bor sgrub gzhir gnas pa nyid
NK132(no)004:4949: bcas pa ste / / thabs zab mo dbang bzhis sad par byas te /
NK132(no)004:4950: 'bras bu sku bzhir smin rung gi nus pa khyad par can du byas nas /
NK132(no)004:4951: dbang srog dam tshig la gnas pa'i sgrub pa pos /
NK132(no)004:4952: gang nyams su blang bya'i chos zaba mo mthar thug
NK132(no)004:4953: pa ni thun min nanga rgyud sde gsuma yin te
NK132(no)004:4954: / rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long gi rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:4955: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni chos thams cad kyi gzhi lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:4956: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni chos thams cad kyi lam lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:4957: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga ni chos thams cad kyi 'bras bu lta bu'o //
NK132(no)004:4960: ma h+aas chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer
NK132(no)004:4961: med kyi cho 'phrul du rtogs pas thabs bskyed pa'i
NK132(no)004:4963: a nus dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK132(no)004:4964: bde ba chen po'i rtsal las rang shar bar rtogs
NK132(no)004:4965: nas shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gtso bor
NK132(no)004:4966: rton / a tis ye nas skye 'gag med pa'i
NK132(no)004:4967: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid ma 'gags
NK132(no)004:4968: par rang shar bar shes nas gang la'ang ched 'dzin
NK132(no)004:4969: dang spang blang med par zung 'jug 'od gsal gyi
NK132(no)004:4970: lam la gtso bor byed pa ste /
NK132(no)004:4971: 'di gsum yang gdul bya zhe sdang can /
NK132(no)004:4976: bya rtsol lhod pa gsum dang /
NK132(no)004:4977: dbang po dman 'bring mchog gi gdul bya la dgongs nas gsungs so //
NK132(no)004:4978: de gsum gyi dgongas pa'i bcuda thun mina mana ngaga
NK132(no)004:4979: sde gsang ba snying thig 'di dgongs pa gzhi ka
NK132(no)004:4980: dag gi gnas lugs gtan la phab nas khregs chod
NK132(no)004:4981: cog bzhag bzhi'i sgo nas nyams su len pa dang
NK132(no)004:4982: / lam lhun grub thod rgal gyi nyams len gnad
NK132(no)004:4983: chen po gsum gyi sgrom du bcug nas 'od gsal
NK132(no)004:4984: gyi rtags tshad snang ba bzhis gtan la phabs te
NK132(no)004:4985: mngon sum lam du byed pa'i ye shes gasnga ba'i
NK132(no)004:4987: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu lam gyur gyi rig 'dzin bzhi'am lnga sogs dang /
NK132(no)004:4988: mthar thug gi 'bras bu snyigs dus kyi tshe thung gcig la /
NK132(no)004:4989: 'gyur bcas rlung sems kyi 'pho ba'i cha rnams /
NK132(no)004:4990: 'gyur med lhan skyes bde ba chen po'i dbyings su thim nas /
NK132(no)004:4991: nang dbyings ka dag gi grol sar /
NK132(no)004:4993: sems chosa skur grol te gdod ma'i rgyal sar gshegas
NK132(no)004:4994: pa'i mngon rtags deng sang gi bar 'byin nus pa'i
NK132(no)004:4995: ngo matshara gyi snang ba 'abra ba can /
NK132(no)004:4996: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:4999: gang zhig bsgrub bya'i lha raba 'byamsa rtsa gsum zhi
NK132(no)004:5000: khro'i khyab badga ste 'phro gazhi'am rtsa bar gyur pa
NK132(no)004:5002: pad+ma gsung sogs sgrub sde chen po brgyad po /
NK132(no)004:5003: rang rang gi bka'a babsa kyi riga 'dzina 'jam dpal bshes gnyen /
NK132(no)004:5007: pra b+ha hasti sogs rig 'dzin brgyad so so'i dgongas pa'i bcud /
NK132(no)004:5008: 'jam dpal sku 'khor lo bzhi la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK132(no)004:5010: pad+ma gsung rta skad theng gsum /
NK132(no)004:5011: yang dag thugs ru lu 'bru brgyad /
NK132(no)004:5012: bdud rtsi yon tan snang srid bdud rtsi rnam dag /
NK132(no)004:5013: phur pa phrin las thal 'byin rnam pa bzhi /
NK132(no)004:5014: rbod gtong ma mo rtsa rlung byang sems /
NK132(no)004:5015: 'jig rten mchod bstod mchod bstod brten gsum /
NK132(no)004:5016: dmod pa drag sngags 'bod rbad bsad gsum mam rdzong 'phrang srog gsum gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5017: zhar byung bla ma rig 'dzin bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i sgo
NK132(no)004:5018: nas sgrub pa sogs spyi bye brag gi sgrub bka'
NK132(no)004:5019: de thams cad kun 'dusa pa pad+ma'i bka'a srol bde
NK132(no)004:5020: gshegs 'dus pa tshom bu gcig tu sgrub pa dang
NK132(no)004:5021: / gzhan yang dpal bka' 'dus chos kyi rgya mtsho
NK132(no)004:5022: tshom bu nyer gcig tu sgrub pa sogs rtsa gsum
NK132(no)004:5023: lhag pa'i lha rab 'byams spyi dang bye brag gi
NK132(no)004:5024: sgrub bka' mtha' dag gciga tu 'khyil ba'am 'dus pa'i
NK132(no)004:5025: / mtsho chen po / las dang grub pa sogs
NK132(no)004:5026: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub gang ci 'dod
NK132(no)004:5027: pa sgrub pa la dka' ba med pa'i ngo mtshar
NK132(no)004:5028: dang che yon zab khyad rmad du byung ba'i /
NK132(no)004:5029: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5030: gnyis pa de la bslad ma bzhugs pa'i che ba la /
NK132(no)004:5031: tshig la bslad med pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5032: don la bslad med tshul gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:5035: de yang he ru ka gal po las /
NK132(no)004:5036: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa yis //
NK132(no)004:5037: sems nyid sangs rgyas rgyu ru 'dod /
NK132(no)004:5038: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa yis //
NK132(no)004:5039: sems nyid sangs rgyas nyid du bsgom //
NK132(no)004:5040: rgyu dang 'bras bu gang yin pa'i //
NK132(no)004:5041: phyogs kyang rab tu shes par bya //
NK132(no)004:5042: zhes gsungs pa ltar sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu tsam du shes nas /
NK132(no)004:5043: sems bskyed dang phyin drug sogs lam tshogs gnyis la
NK132(no)004:5044: bskal pa grangs med gsum sogs su brtson pa'i mthar
NK132(no)004:5045: / 'bras bu sangs rgyas nyid gzod thob par 'dod pa mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5046: sems nyid da lta nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin
NK132(no)004:5047: dbyings dang ye shes dang 'bras bu'i don dam ste
NK132(no)004:5048: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur grub pa lhag pa'i
NK132(no)004:5049: don dam dang / de las shar ba'i phung khams
NK132(no)004:5050: sogs rtog tshogs kyi chos kun sku dang ye shes
NK132(no)004:5051: su rnam par dag pa lhag pa'i kun rdzob ste
NK132(no)004:5052: don dam dang / / de lta bu'i bden pa
NK132(no)004:5053: gnyis kyang ye nas dbyer med par lhag pa'i chos
NK132(no)004:5054: sku chen por 'khor 'das kyi chos kun dbye bsal
NK132(no)004:5055: med par sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin snang srid dag
NK132(no)004:5057: gzhi rgyud rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du lta bas gtan la phab cing /
NK132(no)004:5058: sgom spyod 'bras bu'i chos kun kyang de'i ngang du la bzlas pas /
NK132(no)004:5059: 'bras bu phyi dus la mi re bar da lta
NK132(no)004:5060: nas sangs rgyas par 'dod pa thun min rdo rje
NK132(no)004:5061: theg pa sngags bla med kyi grub mtha' ste /
NK132(no)004:5063: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi dpal gsang ba snying po las /
NK132(no)004:5064: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK132(no)004:5065: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK132(no)004:5066: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK132(no)004:5067: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK132(no)004:5069: gzhal bya 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi gnas lugs la /
NK132(no)004:5070: don dam bden pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du
NK132(no)004:5071: ye nas lhun gyis grub par rang chas su yod
NK132(no)004:5072: kyang rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pas nges
NK132(no)004:5073: pa'i shes pa ma skyes pas ye nas gsang /
NK132(no)004:5074: kun rdzob bden pa sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK132(no)004:5075: 'khor du rang bzhin gyis gnas kyang rkyen kun tu
NK132(no)004:5076: brtags pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo ma shes te
NK132(no)004:5077: rang snang la mtshan mar bzung bas rang bzhin gyis
NK132(no)004:5078: gsang / bden gnyis dbyer med pa'i gnas lugs lhag
NK132(no)004:5079: pa'i chos sku chen por ye nas gnas kyang de
NK132(no)004:5080: ltar ma shes pas snang stong tha dad du bzung
NK132(no)004:5081: bas ngo bo nyid kyis gsang /
NK132(no)004:5082: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'i don de ye
NK132(no)004:5083: nas rang chas su yod kyang yul yul can tha
NK132(no)004:5084: dad du bzung bas shin tu gsang ba ste dmus
NK132(no)004:5085: long la gzugs gab pa bzhin du gnas pa /
NK132(no)004:5086: yang dag pa'i lung rigs man ngag gis mngon du 'byin nas ston par byed pa la /
NK132(no)004:5087: tha snyad kyi rtog ge'i rig pa ltar snang tsam gyis gtan la mi pheb pas /
NK132(no)004:5090: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul /
NK132(no)004:5091: byin gyis brlab dang mngon sum pa //
NK132(no)004:5092: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK132(no)004:5093: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK132(no)004:5096: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams chos can /
NK132(no)004:5097: don dam dbyings ye zung 'jug rang byung gi ye shes su rgyu'am tshul gcig pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:5098: chos thams cad de'i ngang tshul las ma 'das pa'i phyir yig 'bru'i tshul /
NK132(no)004:5099: dbyings las shar ba'i snang ba rnams chos can /
NK132(no)004:5100: dpe yig 'bru'i tshul gyis kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su snang ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:5101: dbyings kyi rang bzhin las ma 'da' pa'i snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:5102: byin gyis brlab pa kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis chos can /
NK132(no)004:5103: phan tshun gcig gis gcig byin gyis brlabs shing dbyer med pa yin te /
NK132(no)004:5104: ngo bo tha dad du ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)004:5105: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs dbyer med pa'i gnas lugs chos can /
NK132(no)004:5106: blos spyod yul thams cad dang bral ba yin te /
NK132(no)004:5107: tha snyad kyi blos bsam gyis mi khyab pa so
NK132(no)004:5108: so rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul yin
NK132(no)004:5109: pa'i phyir ro // de ltar de bzhis legs par
NK132(no)004:5110: gtan la phabs pas dbang rnon cig car ba'i rigs
NK132(no)004:5111: pa'i phyir ro // can gyis / snang lugs nas du mar snang ba'i 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams /
NK132(no)004:5112: gnas lugs bdag nyid chen por rang byung gi ye shes gcig tu rtogs pa ni /
NK132(no)004:5114: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK132(no)004:5116: 'di la bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs ces bya /
NK132(no)004:5117: de lta bu'i don la thag chod kyi myong ba
NK132(no)004:5118: khyad par can skyes pa'i skad cig ma gcig la
NK132(no)004:5119: gong gi bzhi po ldog pas tha dad du dbye
NK132(no)004:5120: ba tsam mo // de ltar rtogs na gong 'og
NK132(no)004:5121: gi theg pa dang grub mtha' kun gyi dgongs pa
NK132(no)004:5124: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK132(no)004:5125: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK132(no)004:5126: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK132(no)004:5127: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'du //
NK132(no)004:5129: gang zag rim gyis pa rnams kyis de ltar rtogs mi nus pas /
NK132(no)004:5130: gtan tshig snga ma snga ma rnams kyis don /
NK132(no)004:5132: rol pa 'gag med sogs gtan la phab nas /
NK132(no)004:5135: phyag rgya phra rags sogs la rim gyis bslabs te goms par byas pas /
NK132(no)004:5136: mthar mngon du byed pa yin la /
NK132(no)004:5137: gzhan yang thabs lam la brten nas nang gi rtsa
NK132(no)004:5138: mdud grol stobs kyis rim gyis dpe don gyi ye
NK132(no)004:5140: shin tu dbang rtul kha cig bsags sbyang la rgyun
NK132(no)004:5141: ring 'bad stobs kyis brgyud nas rtogs pa'ang yod de
NK132(no)004:5142: / lam pa'i gang zag gi skal pa'i khyad par
NK132(no)004:5143: gyis mtha' gcig tu nges pa ni ma yin no
NK132(no)004:5144: / // mdor na grol lam bla ma'i man ngag
NK132(no)004:5145: gis rang sems chos skur ngo sprad pa'i gdams pa
NK132(no)004:5146: zab mo la ma brten par /
NK132(no)004:5147: thabs lam rang mtshan par zhen pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5148: 'khrigs sred la med dgag gis rgyas btab pa sogs
NK132(no)004:5149: ni rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi gzugs brnyan du
NK132(no)004:5150: 'gyur te / zhib par gzhan du bshad zin pas 'dir ma spros so //
NK132(no)004:5151: de lta bu'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5152: 'brasa bu gasnga sngagas rdo rje theg pa che yon
NK132(no)004:5153: rmad du byung ba can de gnyis ka'i gzhung dang
NK132(no)004:5154: gdams pa kun tshang la ma nora bar /
NK132(no)004:5155: mdo phyogs rnams shing rta chen po mkhan chen zhi ba 'tsho dang dzi d+aan gnyis sogs kyis /
NK132(no)004:5156: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po mi brjed pa'i
NK132(no)004:5157: gzungs dang ldan pa ska cog sogs la brgyud pa
NK132(no)004:5163: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje sogs riga 'dzina brgyud pa'i zhal gyi lung /
NK132(no)004:5164: ye shes dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bzung zhing skal med kyis bslad du med pas /
NK132(no)004:5165: d+aa ki'i zhala gyi drod rlangsa tho le ba rnams /
NK132(no)004:5166: sangs rgyas dngos lta bu'i grub pa'i rig 'dzin pad
NK132(no)004:5167: 'byung bi ma sangs rgyas gsang ba sogs kyis spyan
NK132(no)004:5168: drangs te / bka' babs las can snying gi bu
NK132(no)004:5169: dagu'am nyer gcig sogs rje 'bangs rig 'dzin 'dus pa'i
NK132(no)004:5171: phal cher ma 'ongs snyigs dus kyi gdul bya la
NK132(no)004:5172: dgongs nas zab mo'i gter du rgyas btab pa dus
NK132(no)004:5173: dang 'tshams par / gter ston sprul pa'i sku mchog
NK132(no)004:5174: gnyis gling pa brgyad sogs rim par byon pas spyan
NK132(no)004:5175: drangs nas snod ldan gyi gang zag lung zin chos
NK132(no)004:5176: kyi bdag po rnams la spel ba yin pas /
NK132(no)004:5177: tha na cho ga'i yan lag ngag 'don phra mo
NK132(no)004:5178: tsam la'ang so skye phal gyi tshig gis bslad ma
NK132(no)004:5179: zhugs par / rgyud dang rgyud kyi dgongs pa gu
NK132(no)004:5180: ru rin po che sogs kyi lung du bsdebs pa'i
NK132(no)004:5181: rdo rje'i tshig 'ba' zhig yin pas gzhan las khyad
NK132(no)004:5183: de lta bu'i mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5186: ston pa kun tu bzang po dang rigs drug pa
NK132(no)004:5187: rdo rje 'chang gi dgongas dona zab mo bduda rtsi'i
NK132(no)004:5188: yang bcud de seng ge'i 'o ma lta bu /
NK132(no)004:5189: dbang bzhi'i lam khyer thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5190: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa mtshan bcas mtshan med kun gyi zab pa'i gnad spyi dang /
NK132(no)004:5191: khyad par dbang bzhi pa'i lam rdzogs pa chen po
NK132(no)004:5192: mngon sum ngo sprod kyi man ngag gzhan la med
NK132(no)004:5194: snod bzang po gser snod dang 'dra ba'i makhasa grub rig 'dzin bye ba'i thugs nas thugs su byon /
NK132(no)004:5195: zhal nasa snyan du brgyud pa zam ma chad pas /
NK132(no)004:5196: sngon gyi dus su rje 'bangs nyer lnga /
NK132(no)004:5198: spang mi pham mgon po bdun brgyud /
NK132(no)004:5199: nyang dang lce btsun sogs zag zad 'od skur gshegs pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5200: 'byung bzhi la rang dbang sgyur zhing bsad pa gso nus pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5201: lus de nyid kyis mkha' spyod du gshegs pa sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa byon cing /
NK132(no)004:5202: deng sang gi dus su'ang gang zag skal ba can
NK132(no)004:5203: rnams la nyams myong byin rlabs kyi bka' ma chad
NK132(no)004:5204: par bzhugs pas / brgyud pa rin po che la
NK132(no)004:5205: dam nyams dang 'dres khyer gyi bslad ma zhugs shing
NK132(no)004:5206: par bzhugs pas / / brgyud pa'i man ngag dang
NK132(no)004:5207: bral ba'i rtog ge ngana pasa ranga bzosa ma bslad
NK132(no)004:5208: pa zab don gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i
NK132(no)004:5209: par bzhugs pas / / / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5210: gsum pa de lta bu gzhan la med pa'i tshul ni /
NK132(no)004:5211: gser zhing nor bus sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5212: rin po che gsera las grub pa'i stong gsum sogs zhing mang po /
NK132(no)004:5213: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi nora bus spras
NK132(no)004:5214: pa'am phyur bor bkang pa'i yona gyis kyang cha tsam
NK132(no)004:5215: yang mi 'gugsa pa dbyingsa kyi mkha'a 'groo'i thugsa mdzoda
NK132(no)004:5216: na gnas pa'i chos zab mo rnams /
NK132(no)004:5218: grub pa'i gnas lha klu sogs gnas tha dad pa na bzhugs pa rnams /
NK132(no)004:5219: grub pa'i slob dpon chen po pad 'byung dang /
NK132(no)004:5220: bi ma la la sogs pas rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pas spyan drangs nas /
NK132(no)004:5221: zang zing gi yon la blta ba med par thugs
NK132(no)004:5222: brtse basa dgongs te ma 'ongs rjesa 'juga gi gdul
NK132(no)004:5223: bya'i skal pa kho nara bkrama pa 'di lta bu
NK132(no)004:5224: gsar phyogs kyi grub mtha' gzhan la med de zhib
NK132(no)004:5225: par gong du bstan pa bzhin /
NK132(no)004:5226: de lta bu'i mtsho skyesa rgyal pa'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5227: gnyis pa bye brag tu rdzogs pa chen po'i che ba bshad pa la gsum /
NK132(no)004:5228: gzhi gtan la phab tshul gyi che ba /
NK132(no)004:5229: lam nyams su len tshul gyi che ba /
NK132(no)004:5230: 'bras bu zad sar skyel tshul gyi che ba bstan pa'o //
NK132(no)004:5232: ngo bo ka nas sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5233: rang byung gdod ma'i gshis lugs ye nas 'ching grol
NK132(no)004:5234: las 'das pa'i chos nyid mnyam pa chen po ni
NK132(no)004:5235: rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral bas nam mkha' dwangs
NK132(no)004:5237: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'char gzhi ma 'gags pa /
NK132(no)004:5238: ngo bo yod med snang stong sogs spros pa'i mtha'
NK132(no)004:5239: kun dang bral bas ka nasa daga pa'i rang byung
NK132(no)004:5241: sku dang ye shes sogs zag med 'bras bu'i yon
NK132(no)004:5242: tan gyi chos kun nyi ma dang 'od zer bzhin
NK132(no)004:5243: du ye nas 'du 'bral spang ba'i ranga bzhina lhun
NK132(no)004:5245: thugs rje'i rig pa'i rtsal 'gags pa med par phyogs med kun khyab tu shara basa /
NK132(no)004:5246: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa nyid ye nas rag la rang chas su gnas pas /
NK132(no)004:5247: de ngos zin phyin chad blun sgom yid dpyod kyi
NK132(no)004:5248: sems 'dzin sogs kyi rtsol ba la rag ma lus
NK132(no)004:5249: par / semas sems byung sogs kun gzhi tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa dbyings su thim pa'am 'gags nas /
NK132(no)004:5250: rnam shes lasa 'adsa pa'i rang byung gi ye shes thig le nyag gcig gi klong du /
NK132(no)004:5251: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma btsal ba ye nas rdzogs pas rdzogas pa /
NK132(no)004:5252: de'i gong na rtogs bya lta ba'i gzhi dang lam
NK132(no)004:5253: dang 'bras bu'i chos gzhan med pas na che ba'am
NK132(no)004:5254: chen po ste / theg pa 'og ma'i lam dang
NK132(no)004:5255: 'bras bu'i chos kun gyi mthar thug gi dgongs pa'i
NK132(no)004:5256: chen po ste / skyel so / 'di nyid rtogs
NK132(no)004:5257: na blos byas kyi grub matha'i 'ching ba brgya phrag
NK132(no)004:5259: de lta bu'i rtsol bral theg pa'i rgyal po mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstana pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5261: yod med phyogs rer sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5262: smos ma thag pa ltar skyon yon grub bsal las
NK132(no)004:5263: 'das pa'i rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK132(no)004:5264: po nyid lam gyi skabs su bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK132(no)004:5265: 'pho ba'i stobs kyis mngon sum rang thog tu ngo
NK132(no)004:5266: 'phrod pa'i tshe / 'khrul pa shes bya la mi srid pa'i gding chos te /
NK132(no)004:5267: yin min yoda meda sogs phyogsa rer zhena pa'i yid
NK132(no)004:5268: dpyod grub matha'i dmigas gtad kyi zhen 'dzin mtha' dag
NK132(no)004:5270: rtag chad sogs mathara 'dzina gyi lta ba ngan pa'i 'dzin stangsa mtha' dag drunga nasa phyungsa te /
NK132(no)004:5271: gzhi'i skabs su ka dag lhun grub zung 'jug tu gtan la phab /
NK132(no)004:5272: lam gyi dus su khregs chod dang thod rgal zung 'jug tu nyams su blangs pas /
NK132(no)004:5273: 'bras bu'i skabs su dbyings dang ye shes zung du
NK132(no)004:5274: 'jug pa'i nang gsal sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK132(no)004:5275: don nyid mngon du byed pas na /
NK132(no)004:5276: gzhi lam 'brasa bu'i chos kun snang stong zunga du
NK132(no)004:5277: 'juga pa'i lam zab mo gzhan la med pa'i khyad
NK132(no)004:5278: chos can mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyasa gyur
NK132(no)004:5280: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5281: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i skyel so dus gsuma gyi rgyal ba'i dgongas pa mathara thug pa'i dona /
NK132(no)004:5283: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK132(no)004:5284: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gi rnyed //
NK132(no)004:5285: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK132(no)004:5286: mi smra nags kyi nang na gnas pa snyams //
NK132(no)004:5287: tshig bral ngag gi lam gyis mi mtshon pa //
NK132(no)004:5288: de bzhin nyid chos rang bzhin nam mkha' 'dra //
NK132(no)004:5289: sems dang yid kyi rgyu ba kun spangs pa //
NK132(no)004:5290: mchog rab ngo mtshar che ba dam pa shes //
NK132(no)004:5292: mtshan 'dzin gyi spros pa'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i zaba pa /
NK132(no)004:5293: sems sems byung gi rgyu ba 'gags pas zhi ba /
NK132(no)004:5294: 'di zhes mtshan mar mi dmigs pas sprosa pa dang bral ba'i ye shes rang 'od gsal ba /
NK132(no)004:5295: rgyu rkyen gyi rtsol sgrub kyis ma bskyed pa'i zag med 'dusa ma byas chen po /
NK132(no)004:5296: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par riga stong
NK132(no)004:5297: zung du 'jug pa'i mi shigas rdo rje grub pa'i
NK132(no)004:5298: matha'a chen po de'i ngang du lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK132(no)004:5299: chos kun zad sar skyol bas na /
NK132(no)004:5300: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa zab mo la sgra ji bzhin par da lta nas 'jug nus pa'i /
NK132(no)004:5301: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5302: gnyis pa ji ltar nyams su len cing 'dzin pa'i tshul la smon pa la gsum /
NK132(no)004:5303: rang gis lung rtogs kyi bstan pa 'dzin pa /
NK132(no)004:5304: gzhan la de ltar spel ba'i tshul /
NK132(no)004:5305: de 'dra'i bstan 'dzin mang du 'byung bar smon pa'o //
NK132(no)004:5307: lung gi bstan pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5308: rtogs pa'i bstan pa 'dzin tshul la smon pa gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:5310: mang du thos pa sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5311: yongs 'dzin mkhas pa la brten nas thun mong dang
NK132(no)004:5312: thun mong ma yin pa'i mdo rgyud dgongs 'grel yan
NK132(no)004:5313: lag dang bcas pa manga du thosa pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5314: de'i don la rton pa bzhi dang ma 'gal bar
NK132(no)004:5315: rigs pa yang dag pas brtags shing dpyod pa las
NK132(no)004:5316: byung ba'i bsam byung gi shes rab dri ma med
NK132(no)004:5317: pas yid ches kyi gding rnyed nas /
NK132(no)004:5318: dpyad gsum rnam par dag pa'i lung gi sprin chen po 'khrigas shinga /
NK132(no)004:5319: pha rol gyi rgol ba ngan pa'i tshogs rnams dus
NK132(no)004:5320: cig car du 'jomas nus pa'i riga pa'i 'brug sgra
NK132(no)004:5321: bzang po phyogs kun tu sgrogs pa'i rnam dpyod kyi
NK132(no)004:5323: snyan brgyud zab mo man ngaga gi ganda kyi bduda
NK132(no)004:5324: rtsi 'chi gsos kyi sman dang 'dra ba rnams snying
NK132(no)004:5325: la sim pas yon tan gyi lus zung rgyas shing
NK132(no)004:5326: / de'i mthus 'chad rtsod rtsom pa la thogs pa
NK132(no)004:5327: med pa'i rnam dpyod kyi mthu chen po grub ste
NK132(no)004:5328: / / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po
NK132(no)004:5329: che 'dzin zhing bsrung ba dang spel bas phyogs kun
NK132(no)004:5332: rmad byung a ti sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5333: zab khyad dang che yon rmad du byung ba can
NK132(no)004:5334: gyi rtsol bral a ti yo ga'i gasnga ba zab
NK132(no)004:5335: mos lam nas / ma lusa rgyal ba kun gyi ye shesa kyi sku /
NK132(no)004:5336: khyab badga 'ajama dapala ye shes sems dpa' ste /
NK132(no)004:5337: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas /
NK132(no)004:5338: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu /
NK132(no)004:5339: lung la ma brten pa'i man ngag zab mo gzhan
NK132(no)004:5340: la med pa'i khyad chos nyid khong nas rang shar
NK132(no)004:5341: ba'i tshul gyis / rigs kun bdag po rdo rje
NK132(no)004:5342: sems dpa' nyid du raba tu bsgrubsa pa'am rtogs pa
NK132(no)004:5344: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i don brgyud snying po'i bstan pa
NK132(no)004:5345: rin po che 'dzin zhing spel bas dus kyi mthar
NK132(no)004:5346: yang mi nyams par rgyas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5348: lung gi chos spel ba dang /
NK132(no)004:5349: rtogs pa'i chos spel ba gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:5351: yang dag tshad ma sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5352: de yang thun mong ba mngon rjes lung gi tshad ma gsum sogs spyir grags pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5353: thun min gzhal bya bden gsum dbyer med pa'i don la /
NK132(no)004:5354: gzhal byed yang dag pa'i tshad ma /
NK132(no)004:5356: lung dang rig pa man ngag gi //
NK132(no)004:5357: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal bas //
NK132(no)004:5358: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:5361: thugs kyi sgron ma gsang ba'i 'grel pa 'di //
NK132(no)004:5362: lung dang man ngag rig pas gtan la dbab //
NK132(no)004:5364: lung rig man ngag gsuma gyi nga ro ste 'jigs
NK132(no)004:5365: pa med par skad gsang mthon por bsgrags pa yis
NK132(no)004:5366: / rtag chad kyi gnas la zhen pa'i lta damna
NK132(no)004:5367: gyi ri dwagsa wa skyes lta bu'i tshogas rnams spobs
NK132(no)004:5368: pa bcoms nas skrag par madzada pa yi /
NK132(no)004:5369: rim dgu'i theg pa'i rtse rgyal mchoga a ti yo
NK132(no)004:5370: ga'i rang skad rgyu 'bras bya rtsol las 'das pa'i
NK132(no)004:5371: seng ge'i sgra dbyangs chen po sa gsuma na khyab
NK132(no)004:5372: par bsgrags pas / dman lam yid dpyod kyi lta sgom grub matha'i bslad pa dang bral ba'i /
NK132(no)004:5373: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5375: rgyal bstan yongs su sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5376: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid can gyi rgyal bstan
NK132(no)004:5377: bshad sgrub snying po'i lung yongas su rdzogsa pa'i lha'i
NK132(no)004:5378: gosa bazanga po'i dar shams kyi rtser /
NK132(no)004:5379: grol ba drug dang ldan pa'i 'od gasla rdo rje
NK132(no)004:5380: snying po'i dgos 'byung nor bu'i tog gis mngon par
NK132(no)004:5381: mdzesa pa yis / phas kyi brgol ba ngan pa
NK132(no)004:5382: sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogsa kun lasa rnam para rgyal
NK132(no)004:5383: zhing don gnyis kyi 'dod pa yid bzhin du 'jo
NK132(no)004:5384: ba'i dga' ston gyi rgyal mtshan srid zhi'i bla na
NK132(no)004:5386: snyan ngag khyad par gyi gzugs can gyi rgyan du bkod pa ste /
NK132(no)004:5387: don la lha dbang g.yul las rgyal ba'i ru mtshon bzhin du dus nam yang g.yo ba med par /
NK132(no)004:5388: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas shing yun du brtan par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5390: rang gi 'dzin par smon pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5391: gzhan gyis 'dzin par smon pa gnyis /
NK132(no)004:5393: bdag sogs deng nas sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5394: ji ltar smon lam 'debs pa po badga rang nyid
NK132(no)004:5395: dang sogas khong nas brgyud 'dzin slob mar bcas pas
NK132(no)004:5396: mtshon kun kyang / dus denga nasa bzung ste 'gro
NK132(no)004:5397: ba sems can gyi khams ji srida gnas kyi bar
NK132(no)004:5398: mtshon kun kyang / de srid du / ngan 'gro log par ltung ba'i gnas su mi skye zhing /
NK132(no)004:5399: mtho ris kyi yon tan bdun dang lam gyi gzhi rten 'khor lo chen po bzhis 'byor te /
NK132(no)004:5400: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che sde snod gsum rgyud sde bzhi spyi dang /
NK132(no)004:5401: khyad par bstan pa'i snying po zab mo nang rgyud
NK132(no)004:5402: sde gsum gyi lam gyi lus yongs su rdzogs pa
NK132(no)004:5404: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa'i mkha'a khyab sangs rgyas
NK132(no)004:5405: kyi zhing rab 'byams kun tu rgyal ba'i sras kyi
NK132(no)004:5406: mchog /'jam pa'i dbyangs dang kun tu bzang po /
NK132(no)004:5407: gsang ba'i bdag po sogs kyi rnam thar ji lta
NK132(no)004:5408: ba bzhin du 'dzin skyong sprel ba'i dam baca'i go
NK132(no)004:5410: mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che rgyas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5412: dam pa rnams kyi rang gi ngang tshul bstan pa ste /
NK132(no)004:5413: snga 'gyur pun+da ri ka'i rgyud las /
NK132(no)004:5414: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK132(no)004:5415: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK132(no)004:5418: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK132(no)004:5419: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK132(no)004:5422: mdor na mkhas btsun sogs tshigs bcad phyi ma gnyis te /
NK132(no)004:5423: gong smos smon lam kun gyi don mdora bsdu na /
NK132(no)004:5424: mkhyen brtse nus gsum dang makhasa btsun bzang gsum sogs
NK132(no)004:5425: mkhas pa dang grub pa'i yon tan gyis mngon par
NK132(no)004:5426: mtho ba'i rnam thara gyis te /
NK132(no)004:5427: rang don du gsan bsam bsgom gsum mthar phyin zhing /
NK132(no)004:5428: gzhan don du 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum dang /
NK132(no)004:5429: gnyis don du bshad sgrub las gsum ste mkhas tshul dagu'am dam pa'i tshul dgu'i sgo nas /
NK132(no)004:5430: rgyal bstan nges gsang snying po'i ring lugs nyid phyogs
NK132(no)004:5431: mthar spel ba'i phrin lasa nam mkha'a ltar kun la
NK132(no)004:5432: khyab pa'i / bstan 'dzina gyi skyes bu dama pasa
NK132(no)004:5433: sa yi steng thams cad yongas su khyab pa'am ganga
NK132(no)004:5434: khyab pa'i / nasa / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5435: khyad par du'ang don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i dapala
NK132(no)004:5436: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i mtshungs med bla
NK132(no)004:5437: ma'i sku tshe rdo rje ltar gzhom gzhig dang bral
NK132(no)004:5438: bar raba tu brtan cinga thugs kyi bzhed don mtha'
NK132(no)004:5439: dag gegs med du 'grub pa dang /
NK132(no)004:5440: bstan la mchod pa'i sbyin badga rgyal blon khyim bdag
NK132(no)004:5441: sogs kyang chos bzhin du 'tsho ba'i mang'a thang dara
NK132(no)004:5442: zhing sde bzhi'i 'byor ba rgyas pa yisa /
NK132(no)004:5443: chos dang srid kyi dpal 'byor nam yang mi nuba par /
NK132(no)004:5444: gtsug lag khang dang spong klog gi sde 'phel zhing /
NK132(no)004:5445: rnyed sogs kyis nam yang mi brel ba dang /
NK132(no)004:5446: rtag par dge 'dun rnams lta spyod mthun zhing /
NK132(no)004:5447: chos spyod bcu sogs bsam rgu yid bzhin du 'grub
NK132(no)004:5448: pa'i nora bu'i rgyal mtshan rtag par bsgrengsa pa yis
NK132(no)004:5449: / mtsho skyes rgyal ba'i bstan pa snga 'gyur yo
NK132(no)004:5450: ga sde gsum gtso bor gyur pa'i ring lugs dri
NK132(no)004:5451: ma med pa nyid phyogs kun tu dar zhing rgyas
NK132(no)004:5452: la yun ring du gnas par gyur ciga /
NK132(no)004:5453: de ltar grub pa'ang bla ma rgyal ba sras dang bcas pas byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK132(no)004:5454: zhes rang 'dod dang bral bar rtsa gsum lha'i thugs
NK132(no)004:5455: rgyud bskul te lhag pa'i bsam pa yang dag pas
NK132(no)004:5457: rtsa ba'i gsum pa mjug gi don la /
NK132(no)004:5458: rgyu mtshan dang bcas te gzhan la bskul ba dang /
NK132(no)004:5459: dgos pa brjod de mdzad byang smos pa gnyis las /
NK132(no)004:5461: zhes rgyal ba thams cad sogs te /
NK132(no)004:5462: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi ngo bo
NK132(no)004:5463: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs nas lung bstan
NK132(no)004:5464: pa'i dapala ldan sangsa rgyas pad+ma skyes 'chi meda rdo
NK132(no)004:5465: rje sku brnyes shing lho nub 'o ma can gyi
NK132(no)004:5466: rgya mtshor 'khrungas pa'i rgyal ba gnyis pa'i bstan pa
NK132(no)004:5467: gsang chen snga 'gyur rnying ma zhesa gragas pa 'di
NK132(no)004:5468: ni / rgyal bstan yongas su rdzogas pa'i phyi mo'am 'byung khungs yiin cinga /
NK132(no)004:5469: gong du smos pa ltar gyi zaba gnad kyi che ba du ma'i khyad chosa dang /
NK132(no)004:5470: lta sgoma spyod gsum rnam para daga pasa rgyal ba
NK132(no)004:5471: dgyes pa'i lam bazanga tshang la ma nora ba'i mchog
NK132(no)004:5472: yina pasa 'di ltar ngo shesa nas /
NK132(no)004:5473: 'jig rten na ded dpon mkhas pas yid bzhin gyi
NK132(no)004:5474: nora bu rina po che yongs su brtags nas byi
NK132(no)004:5475: dora byasa te rgyal mtshan gyi rtse la mchoda pas
NK132(no)004:5476: rang gzhan gyi 'dod pa 'byung ba bzhina du /
NK132(no)004:5477: ganga zaga skala ba dang ldana pa shes rab dang brtson 'grus mi dman pa rnamas kyis /
NK132(no)004:5478: rang lugs kyi grub matha'i rkang bzung ste /
NK132(no)004:5479: gzhan gyi zer sgros kyis bslad ma zhugs par 'achada
NK132(no)004:5480: pa dang rtsod pa dang rtsom pa gsuma gyi phrina
NK132(no)004:5481: lasa rlabas po chesa phyogsa dus gnas skabs thams cad
NK132(no)004:5482: du dara zhing rgyas para madzada pa'i thugsa 'khura bzhesa
NK132(no)004:5483: pa dang / zhes thugs brtse bas gzhan bskul 'debs
NK132(no)004:5484: pa ste blo ldan rnams kyis phan pa'i gdams ngag
NK132(no)004:5485: spyi bos len zhing snying la bcang dgos pa kho
NK132(no)004:5486: pa dang / na ste / rgyal sras zhi ba lhas /
NK132(no)004:5487: gzhan la gzhan bskul 'debs mkhas shing //
NK132(no)004:5488: ma bcol phan par byed pa'i ngag /
NK132(no)004:5489: gus pas spyi bor blang gis te //
NK132(no)004:5490: rtag tu kun gyi slob mar 'gyur //
NK132(no)004:5491: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)004:5494: smos ma thag pa de lta bu'i tshul gyis bstan
NK132(no)004:5495: la dgongs pa'i dam pa rnams kyi thugs kyi bzheda
NK132(no)004:5496: pa ji bzhina du 'gruba pa'i rten cing 'brela 'byung
NK132(no)004:5497: bzang po'i smon tshiga tu gsang chen rnying ma'i bstan
NK132(no)004:5498: pa la g.yo zol med pa'i lhag pa'i bsam pa
NK132(no)004:5499: yar ngo'i zla ba ltar rnam para dakara ba can
NK132(no)004:5502: rnam dag rigs pa'i lam gsum gyi shing rta chen por grub cing /
NK132(no)004:5503: legs bshad kyi snang ba rgya mtsho'i gos can yongs la khyab pa ste /
NK132(no)004:5504: don gyi rgyu mtshan bzhi dang 'brel ba'i sgo nas /
NK132(no)004:5505: rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i zhabs kyis gsol ba'i mtshan /
NK132(no)004:5506: mi phama 'ajama dbyangs rnama rgyal rgya mtshosa gansa dusa
NK132(no)004:5507: ston 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'i rten 'brela shin tu
NK132(no)004:5508: dge bar nyin gunga gi thun gcig la thugs thog
NK132(no)004:5510: dge legas kyi snang bas phyogs dus 'jig rten kun
NK132(no)004:5511: khyab cing don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal yon
NK132(no)004:5512: gong nas gong du 'pheel ba'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:5514: des gzhung gi tshig don mdo tsam 'grel zin nas /
NK132(no)004:5516: srid dang zhi ba'i phun tshogs 'dod rgu'i char //
NK132(no)004:5517: ci dgar sbyin mdzad rgyal bstan yid bzhin dbang //
NK132(no)004:5518: sher brtson rgyal mtshan rtse mor mchod mkhas pa'i //
NK132(no)004:5519: ded dpon mchog rnams thub la byas gzo nyid //
NK132(no)004:5520: skyob pa mchog des grangs med bskal pa ru //
NK132(no)004:5521: sku srog bye ba btang nas btsal ba'i nor //
NK132(no)004:5522: dam chos rin chen mdzod khang rjes 'jug la //
NK132(no)004:5523: gtad pa'i don go de lags gzhan du ci //
NK132(no)004:5524: thub mchog zhabs kyis bcags min ljongs 'di ru //
NK132(no)004:5525: snang ba'i sgo chen snga 'gyur pa yis phyes //
NK132(no)004:5526: de la brten nas gsar 'gyur dag kyang byung //
NK132(no)004:5527: kun kyang rnam grol lam las nyams pa med //
NK132(no)004:5528: 'on kyang dus dang gdul bya'i khyad par gyis //
NK132(no)004:5529: zab gnad khyad 'phags snga 'gyur pa la yod //
NK132(no)004:5530: de tshul rigs pa'i lam nas tshad ma ru //
NK132(no)004:5531: sgrub la bsnyengs bral 'jam mgon bla ma tsam //
NK132(no)004:5532: tshigs re tsam gyis the tshom d+r+wa ba 'bum //
NK132(no)004:5533: chod ces 'jam dpal phyag gi ral gri gang //
NK132(no)004:5534: yang yang khyed la gtad pa'i rnam spyod dpal //
NK132(no)004:5535: 'di 'dra sngon dus 'phags pa'i yul na'ang dkon //
NK132(no)004:5536: mgon po gang gi legs bshad nor bu'i gter //
NK132(no)004:5537: ci dgar 'byed pa'i dus ston deng lags na //
NK132(no)004:5538: gzhan zer rjes brjod 'ching bus tshim min par //
NK132(no)004:5539: skal mchog ldan rnams 'di sbyin ci dgar rol //
NK132(no)004:5540: de slad bdag blo sbyang brtson zhan na yang //
NK132(no)004:5541: dam pas bskul dang bstan la gus pa'i blos //
NK132(no)004:5542: phyogs tsam bkral 'dir rmongs blos nyes pa'i cha //
NK132(no)004:5543: gang mchis 'phags dang mkhas pa'i spyan sngar bshags //
NK132(no)004:5544: de las byung ba'i rab dge dri med kyis //
NK132(no)004:5545: skye dang skye bar rgyal ba'i chos mdzod 'dzin //
NK132(no)004:5546: mkha' khyab dam chos sgron ma rnam bkod nas //
NK132(no)004:5547: don gnyis lhun grub chos kyi rgyal por shog /
NK132(no)004:5548: phan bde'i 'byung gnas rgyal bstan yun du gnas //
NK132(no)004:5549: de 'dzin zhabs brtan bshad sgrub mnga' thang dar //
NK132(no)004:5550: rtag par dge 'dun lta spyod don mthun pas //
NK132(no)004:5551: sde gsum snying po'i ring lugs rgyas gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:5552: lha klu dga' bas dus bzhir shis pa sgrubs //
NK132(no)004:5553: mi rnams bde skyid dge bcu'i khrims kyis 'tsho //
NK132(no)004:5554: nad mug mtshon sogs mi shis ming mi grags //
NK132(no)004:5555: rdzogs ldan dang po'i dus ston 'phel gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:5556: bkra shis gang zhig lhan skyes bde ba che //
NK132(no)004:5557: rang byung don gyi mtsho skyes pad+ma rgyal //
NK132(no)004:5558: 'gro ba kun gyi snying la rtag bzhugs pa'i //
NK132(no)004:5559: bden pa de yis dus kun shis gyur cig /
NK132(no)004:5560: ces pa'ang lung rtogs yon tan gyi gter mnga' rdzogs
NK132(no)004:5561: chen mkhan rin po che bsod chos nas gsung bskul
NK132(no)004:5562: gnang zhing / rang lugs kyi lta grub la gzhan
NK132(no)004:5563: dring mi 'jog pa'i rnam dpyod can mkhan kun dpal
NK132(no)004:5564: dang bla ma dam pa chos dbyings 'od gsal nas
NK132(no)004:5566: rigs brgya'i khyab bdag zur mang drung rin po ches
NK132(no)004:5567: kyang bka'i rjes su gnang ba thob pa la brten
NK132(no)004:5569: 'byung 'khrugs nad kyi mnar ba'i gzhan dbang du gyur nas rim lus su gyur pa la /
NK132(no)004:5570: slar rab tshes shing glang zla ba lnga pa'i tshe
NK132(no)004:5571: bzhi res gza' lha'i bla ma rgyal sar phebs pa'i
NK132(no)004:5572: 'phrod sbyor dang rten 'byung shin tu dge ba'i nyin
NK132(no)004:5573: glo bur du bri 'dod byung ba dang /
NK132(no)004:5574: mchog gi sprul pa'i sku pad+ma dri med legs pa'i
NK132(no)004:5575: blo gros dang dge slong 'phags mchog gnyis nas kyang
NK132(no)004:5576: legs so'i tshig gis bskul ba la brten /
NK132(no)004:5577: nad las rnam par rgyal ba'i brtson pa'i go cha bskyed de /
NK132(no)004:5578: rje nyid kyi mdzad pa'i sa bcad dang gsung sgros 'bel gtam rnams gtso bor bzung /
NK132(no)004:5579: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK132(no)004:5580: mkhas mchog blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK132(no)004:5581: zhe chen ma h+aa pan+di ta sogs sngon byon dam
NK132(no)004:5582: pa rnams kyi gsung gi sgron me la brten nas
NK132(no)004:5583: / 'jam mgon rdo rje 'chang rnam gsum gyi zhabs rdul la spyi bos reg cing /
NK132(no)004:5584: khyab bdag zhe chen rab 'byams lnga pa'i bka' 'bangs
NK132(no)004:5585: su gtogs pa'i ban rgan 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya
NK132(no)004:5586: mtsho'i sgra dbyangs sam rdo rje dbang mchog dgyes pa
NK132(no)004:5588: tshes de nyid la dbu btsugs nas zla ba de'i
NK132(no)004:5589: tshes bcu gsum la grub par rang gnas bde mchog
NK132(no)004:5590: bkra shis dge 'phel gyi dben spyil du bris pa
NK132(no)004:5591: 'di la / rang blo dman zhing rgyun ring nad kyis mnar bas shes pa mi gsal ba dang /
NK132(no)004:5592: sam tra sogs la brten pa'i nyis bris sogs kyang ma grub stabs /
NK132(no)004:5593: tshig don gyi cha la 'gal 'khrul gang mchis snying nas bshags shing /
NK132(no)004:5594: dge bas nges gsang snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i
NK132(no)004:5595: bstan pa rin po che phyogs dus gnas skabs kun
NK132(no)004:5596: tu dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa'i
NK132(no)004:5598: gangs can mtha' khob mun gling khrod 'dir rmad byung thugs bskyed skya rengs gsar pas yongs bskul te //
NK132(no)004:5599: rgyal bstan rin chen mdo sngags chos tshul 'od stong can de 'bad brtson shing rta bdun shugs kyis //
NK132(no)004:5600: thogs med drangs las chos tshigs yul dbus 'phags yul gnyis pa skal pa bzang por bsgrubs pa'i gtam //
NK132(no)004:5601: snga 'gyur pa zhes yongs su grags 'di gang 'dul bka' bab rgyal bstan yongs kyi phyi mo'ang yin //
NK132(no)004:5602: de slad bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam drang srong mi pham gsung gi dgongs 'grel legs bshad mchog //
NK132(no)004:5603: mkhyen rab dbang phyug rgyal tshab 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya mtsho'i sgra dbyangs sgrogs des brtsams mdzad pa //
NK132(no)004:5604: 'di ko snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos mdzod yan lag mtha' rgyas khongs su bsdus shing spel bar byas //
NK132(no)004:5605: bsod nams gang des skabs don smon pa'i gnas kun gegs med yongs 'grub bkra shis dpal 'bar shog /
